Ukwanda okusheshayo kokuvela kwesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom, kusukela ngoJanuwari 1 kuya ku-March 15, 2020
Izigameko ezihlangene zesifo se-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) zibonisa ukuthambekela okufanayo emazweni e-European Union / European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom okuqinisekisa ukuthi, ngenkathi esezingeni elihlukile kuye ngezwe, ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha kuwo wonke amazwe.
Ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho okuvela e-Italy, amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kufanele akhulise ukulungela kwabo ukwanda kweziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezizodinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okujulile.
NgoDisemba 31, 2019, kwabikelwa ngeqembu lamacala omdlavuza wamaphaphu we-aetiology engaziwa eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
NgoJanuwari 9, 2020, iChina Center for Disease Control and Prevention yabika ukuthi i-agent ebangela lesi sifo yi-coronavirus entsha manje ebizwa ngokuthi i-coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kusukela lapho, lesi sifo esibangelwa ukutheleleka yi-SARS-CoV-2 sesibizwa ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubufakazi kuze kube manje ukuthi cishe abantu abangama-80% abane-COVID-19 banesifo esibuthakathaka, okungukuthi, isifo sokuphefumula esinesifo samaphaphu noma esingabuthakathaka, futhi iningi labo liyaphila.
Ezimweni ezingaba ngu-14% iziguli, i-COVID-19 iba yisifo esibi kakhulu esidinga ukufakwa esibhedlela kanti izinga eliphakeme lama-6% lazo zigula kakhulu ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile.
Izinga lokufa kwabagulayo ababhekene ne-COVID-19 licishe libe ngama-4%.
Kulesi sifundo, sihlola izitayela zokugcwala kwe-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye le-European Union / European Economic Area (EU / EEA) nase-United Kingdom (UK) bese siziqhathanisa naleso seSifundazwe saseHubei, eChina.
Siphinde siqhathanise inani lamanje lamacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU / EEA nase-UK nalawo ase-Italy phakathi kuka-31 Januwari15 Mashi 2020.
Izigameko ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Ngemuva kweChina, i-COVID-19 yaqhubeka nokusabalala endaweni futhi amandla obhubhane lwe-COVID-19 ezweni lonke njengamanje alandela lawo aleli zwe.
NgoMashi 11, 2020, uMqondisi-Jikelele weNhlangano Yezwe Yezempilo (i-WHO) wamemezela i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Ephephandabeni lika-5 Mashi le-Eurosurveillance 2020, uSpiteri et al. babike ngamacala okuqala e-COVID-19 aseYurophu aqinisekisiwe ngokwencazelo yecala le-WHO.
E-EU/EEA, amacala amathathu okuqala aqinisekisiwe abikwe yiFrance ngoJanuwari 24, 2020 kubantu ababuya eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Kusukela ngoMashi 15, 2020, amacala e-COVID-19 ayebonwe kuwo wonke amazwe angama-30 e-EU / EEA nase-United Kingdom (UK), lapho phakathi kukaDisemba 31, 2019 nalolo suku, kwabikwa amacala angama-39,768 nokufa okuyi-1,727 , kanti amacala angama-17,750 nokufa okuyi-1441 kwavela e-Italy kuphela.
Ukuthola inani elihlangene kanye nokutheleleka okuhlangene kweziguli ze-COVID-19
ESikhungweni SaseYurophu Sokuvimbela Nokulawula Izifo (ECDC), izibalo zamacala e-COVID-19 azisiwe ezweni ngalinye emhlabeni wonke, ezitholakala kuphela emithonjeni esemthethweni njengamazwe UMnyango Wezempilo, iziphathimandla zezempilo zikazwelonke nezesifunda kanye ne-WHO, ziyabuyekezwa nsuku zonke ngo-8: 00 ekuseni.
Le datha yasetshenziselwa ukuhlola izitayela ze-COVID-19 e-EU / EEA nase-UK, futhi yaziqhathanisa nalezo e-Italy.
Njengomthengisi wokwanda kwamacala asebenzayo e-COVID-19, sibalile izinsuku eziyi-14 zokwehla kwamacala e-COVID-19, ngaleyo ndlela sicabangela inkambo yemvelo ye-COVID-19, ezweni ngalinye le-EU / EEA nase-UK, phakathi nenkathi kaJanuwari 115 Mashi 2020.
Siphinde saveza inani elihlangene lamacala azethunyelwe ezweni ngalinye ngo-15 Mashi 2020 ngo-8:00 ekuseni uma kuqhathaniswa ne-Italy esikhathini esingu-31 Januwari15 Mashi 2020.
Izitayela ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Izitayela ezinsukwini eziyi-14 zokwehliswa kwecala le-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU / EEA nase-UK ngokuvamile zilandela lezo zeSifundazwe saseHubei (eChina) (Umdwebo 1).
E-EU/EEA nase-UK iyonke, izigameko ezihlangene ze-COVID-19 zaqala ukukhuphuka cishe ngoFebhuwari 21 bese zikhuphuka kakhulu ngoFebhuwari 28, 2020 (Izinto ezingeziwe).
Lokhu kwakubangelwa ikakhulu ukwanda okusheshayo kwenani lamacala abikiwe avela e-Italy, kepha wonke amanye amazwe e-EU / EEA ne-UK akhombise ukuthambekela okufanayo okwandayo kokutheleleka okuhlangene kwe-COVID-19 (Izinto ezingeziwe).
Umdwebo 2 ubonisa inani lamacala e-COVID-19, emazweni e-EU / EEA nase-UK uma kuqhathaniswa ne-Italy esikhathini esiphakathi kuka-31 Januwari15 Mashi 2020.
Ugcizelela ukuthi ngoMashi 15 ngo-8:00 ekuseni, amanye amazwe ayi-15 e-EU/EEA ne-UK asebike inani eliphelele lamacala eliqhathaniswa nelase-Italy amasonto amathathu nje ngaphambili noma ngaphansi.
Imiphumela yethu ibonisa ukuthi inani lamacala e-COVID-19 abikiwe landa ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Izitayela ezibonwayo zokugcwala kwe-COVID-19 zikhombisa ukuthi ubhadane luqhubeka ngesivinini esifanayo kuwo wonke amazwe.
Lokhu kungakhathaliseki ukuthi amazwe asezingeni elihlukile, ukuhlukahluka kwezimpendulo zezempilo zomphakathi ezizwe, futhi mhlawumbe nezincazelo ezahlukene zamacala emazweni kanye nezinqubo ezahlukene zokukhetha iziguli okufanele zihlolwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe i-COVID-19, kuhlanganise nokuhlolwa okuqhubekayo.
Ekuqaleni kukaMashi 2020, odokotela ezifundeni ezithintekile zase-Italy bachaze isimo lapho cishe iziguli eziyi-10% ezine-COVID-19 zidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile futhi imithombo yezindaba yabika ukuthi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kulezi zindawo asevele efinyelele umthamo wabo ophakeme.
Idatha yokwamukelwa kwamacala e-COVID-19 esibhedlela kanye/noma eyunithi yokunakekelwa okujulile iyatholakala njengamanje ezingeni le-EU/EEA kumacala angu-6% no-1% kuphela, ngokulandelana (idatha ayibonisiwe).
Nokho, kufanele ziqoqwe ngendlela ehlelekile ukuze zengeze idatha yamanje yokubhekwa egxile enanini lamacala abikiwe nasenani labantu abafa.
Ucwaningo olwenziwe ngo-2010-11 lwabonisa ukuhluka okukhulu kokutholakala kwemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile nemibhede yokunakekelwa okuphakathi eYurophu, isukela kuma-29,2 eJalimane kuya kuma-4,2 emibhedeni kubantu abangu-100,000 ePortugal.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi amazwe angase abe nezinsizakusebenza eziningi noma ezimbalwa kune-Italy (12.5 imibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile nemibhede yokunakekelwa okuphakathi kubantu abangu-100,000 ngo-201011).
Izimo zokulingisa ezihlobene nokugcwala kwamandla ezempilo, ngokulinganiselwa kwezwe ngalinye le-EU / EEA ne-UK kokwanda kwamacala e-COVID-19 asezibhedlela ahlobene nengozi engama-90% yokudlula umthamo wemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile, zinikezwa ku-ECDC yesithupha yokubuyekezwa kokuhlolwa kwengozi okusheshayo kwe-COVID-19.
Njengoba iziguli ziye zahlanganiswa ezindaweni ezithile emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile ngokuvamile akhonza abantu abahleliwe besifunda, kufanele kube lula ukwenza ulwazi mayelana neziguli nemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile kutholakale ku-Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Okuhlangenwe nakho okuvela e-Italy kanye nezimo zamanje kwamanye amazwe kubonisa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha e-EU / EEA nase-UK.
Ngakho-ke, amazwe, izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kufanele azilungiselele isimo sokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nokwanda kwenani leziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okujulile, njengalowo okwenzeka ezifundeni ezithintekile zase-Italy.
Njengoba kukhonjisiwe ekuhlolweni kwengozi okusheshayo kwe-ECDC, indlela esheshayo, esebenzayo nebanzi ibalulekile ukubambezela ukusabalala kwe-SARS-COV-2, ngokuguqulwa kusuka ekuvimbeleni kuya ekuvimbeleni, njengoba ukwanda okusheshayo okulindelekile kwenani lamacala kunganikeza abenzi bezinqumo nezibhedlela isikhathi esanele sokuqonda, ukwamukela nokulungisa impendulo yabo ngokufanele uma ingasetshenziswa kusenesikhathi.
Ukuhlolwa kwengozi okusheshayo kuhlanganisa nezinhlelo zezempilo yomphakathi zokunciphisa umthelela wobhadane.
Kunomkhawulo omfushane wamathuba lapho amazwe enethuba lokukhulisa imizamo yawo yokulawula ukuze anciphise ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV-2 futhi anciphise ingcindezi enikezwa ukunakekelwa kwezempilo.
Uma lokhu kungenzeki, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlelo zezempilo kwamanye amazwe e-EU/EEA zizobhekana nokwanda kweziguli ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile ezinsukwini noma emasontweni azayo.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo seCoronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), okubangelwa yi-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kuze kube manje sekubulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 000 futhi kuthinteke abangaphezu kuka-80 000 eChina nakwezinye izindawo emhlabeni, okuholele enhlekeleleni kubantu.
Ngokufana negciwane elifanayo, i-SARS-CoV, elabangela i-SARS ezinkulungwaneni zabantu ngo-2003, i-SARS-CoV-2 nayo ingadluliselwa kusuka emagqabini futhi ibangele izimpawu ezifanayo ngomshini ofanayo.
Kodwa-ke, i-COVID-19 inezinga eliphansi lobunzima nokufa kunesifo se-SARS kodwa iyadlulisela kakhulu futhi ithinta abantu abadala abaningi kunentsha namadoda amaningi kunabesifazane.
Ngenxa yenani elikhulayo lezincwadi eziphathelene nalesi sifo esivelayo, lesi sihloko sizama ukunikeza ukubuyekezwa okufika ngesikhathi nokujulile kwendaba yocwaningo ekhula ngokushesha.
Sizoxoxa ngezinto eziyisisekelo mayelana nobugebengu, ubugebengu, amagciwane, ukuxilongwa, ukwelashwa, ukuqagela, nokuvimbela lesi sifo.
Nakuba kusadingeka izimpendulo zemibuzo eminingi, siyethemba ukuthi lokhu kubuyekezwa kuyosiza ekuqondeni nasekucineni lesi sifo esisongelayo.
Umkhosi Wentwasahlobo ngoJanuwari 25, 2020 ube yinkumbulo engakaze ibonwe futhi engasoze yakhunjulwa kubo bonke abaseChina ababecelwa ukuba bahlale endlini yabo kulo lonke leli holide futhi amasonto amaningi ngemuva kwalokho ngenxa yokuqubuka kwesifo esisha esibangelwa amagciwane.
Leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-coronavirus (CoV) eyabangela ukuqubuka kwe-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) ngo-2003; ngakho-ke, yaqanjwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yi-World Health Organization (WHO) ngoFebhuwari 11, 2020, kanti isifo esihambisanayo saqanjwa ngokuthi i-COV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Lesi sifo saqala eWuhan, eChina, futhi ngokushesha sasakazeka kulo lonke izwe safinyelela cishe kwamanye angu-50 emhlabeni wonke.
Kusukela ngoMashi 2, 2020, leli gciwane seliholele ezigulini ezingaphezu kuka-80,000 eziqinisekisiwe ze-COVID-19, iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-40,000 zikhululwe futhi iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-3,000 zifile.
I-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi i-COVID-19 iyisitha somphakathi esiyinhloko futhi singase sibe namandla kakhulu kunobuphekula.
Ngokusho kwePubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), esikhathini esingaphansi kwezinyanga ezimbili, sekushicilelwe amaphepha angaphezu kuka-200 nge-COVID-19 kufaka phakathi i-virology, epidemiology, etiology, ukuxilongwa, kanye nokwelashwa kwayo kusukela kumbiko wokuqala ngoJanuwari 7, 2020 owamisa ukulandelana kwegciwane elihlukaniswe ezigulini eziningi.
Lokhu kubuyekezwa kuzama ukufingqa inqubekela phambili yocwaningo emkhakheni omusha futhi othuthuka ngokushesha.
Noma nini lapho kungenzeka, sizozama ukuqhathanisa i-COVID-19 ne-SARS kanye nolunye uhlobo lwesifo esibangelwa i-COV, i-Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, ukuqubuka ngo-2012).
Sizoxoxa nangalokho esikufundile kuze kube manje ngokuphathelene nokuvimbela nokubona lesi sifo, kanye neminye imibuzo esekhona kodwa ephuthumayo.
Ama-COV aye abhekwa njengezifo ezingabulali abantu, ikakhulukazi okubangela cishe u-15% wamathumbu avamile 4.
Kodwa-ke, kuleli khulu leminyaka, sihlangane nama-CoV abantu anobuthi kakhulu kabili, okungukuthi, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, okwabangela ukuqubuka ekuqaleni eChina ngo-2003 naseSaudi Arabia ngo-2012, futhi ngokushesha kwasakazekela kwamanye amazwe amaningi anobhubhane nokufa okubi.
Ngakho-ke, i-COVID-19 yamanje iqala ukuqubuka okwesithathu kwe-COV emlandweni womuntu.
Njengoba kuboniswe ku-Fig. Fig.1,1, amaqembu omdlavuza omzimba owawuvela eWuhan abikwa okokuqala ngo-December 31, 2019 eChina National Health Commission.
