NgoJanuwari 15, 2020 kwabikwa icala lokuqala elibulalayo eWuhan.
Phakathi naleso sikhathi, lesi sifo sasakazekela ngokushesha emadolobheni, ezifundazweni nakwamanye amazwe angomakhelwane.
Ngo-January 20, kwabikwa ukuthi abantu abahlinzeka ngemisebenzi yezempilo banesifo, okusikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi abantu batheleleke.
NgoJanuwari 23, idolobha laseWuhan lavalwa futhi konke ukuhamba komphakathi kwavalwa.
NgoJanuwari 24 ucwaningo lokuqala lwezokwelapha ngalolu bhubhane lwabika ukuthi, ezigulini ezingu-41 ezinezifo eziqinisekisiwe, ezingu-21 kuphela ezazithola ukuxhumana okuqondile nemakethe ye-Wuhan yezimpahla zasolwandle eyayibhekwa njengendawo yokuqala yokutheleleka emthonjeni wezilwane ongaziwa.
NgoJanuwari 30, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi lolu bhubhane luyisimo esibucayi empilweni yomhlaba wonke.
