Ezimweni ezinzima, iziguli zaqala ngokushesha ukuba nesifo sokuphefumula esibucayi, ukushaywa isifuba, i-acidosis yemetabolism, ne-coagulopathy.
Iziguli ezinomkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula kanye nomkhuhlane osheshayo, ngisho nangaphandle kokuphazamiseka kokubukwa kwemithambo yemiphunga, kufanele zihlolwe ukuze zithole ukuthi igciwane liyagonywa yini.
Ucwaningo lwezenhlalakahle ngasekupheleni kukaDisemba ka-2019 lwabonisa ukuthi amaphesenti eziphawu ayingu-98% ngenxa yomkhuhlane, 76% ngenxa yekhotha elomile, 55% ngenxa yokushaya umoya, no-3% ngenxa yesisu; amaphesenti angu-8 eziguli adinga ukusekelwa komoya.
Ukuthola okufanayo kwabikwa ezifundweni ezimbili zakamuva zeqembu lomndeni neqembu elibangelwa ukudluliselwa komuntu ongenayo imizwa.
Ngokufanayo, ucwaningo lwezenhlalakahle ngo-2012 lwabonisa ukuthi iziguli ze-MERS-CoV nazo zazinomkhuhlane (98%), ukukhwehlela okomile (47%), kanye ne-dyspnea (55%) njengezimpawu zazo eziyinhloko.
Kodwa-ke, ama-80% abo adinga ukusekelwa komoya, okuphezulu kakhulu kunokugula nge-COVID-19 futhi okuhambisana nokufa okuphezulu kwe-MERS kunokwe-COVID-19.
Iziguli ze-MERS nazo zaphawula ukuhlanza (26%) nokuhlushwa kwamakhala (21%).
Ezigulini ze-SARS, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi imfiva (99%-100%), ukukhwehlela okomile (29%-75%), ukuphefumula (-40%-42%), isifo sohudo (20-25%) kanye nobuhlungu bomphimbo (13-25%) kwakuyizimpawu ezinkulu futhi ukusekelwa komoya kwakudingeka cishe ku-14%-20% weziguli.
