Amagciwane angathinta umuntu nangamehlo.
NgoJanuwari 22, 2020, udokotela watheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 yize egqoke imaski ye-N95; leli gciwane kungenzeka lingene emzimbeni wakhe ngamehlo akhe okuvuvukala.
Ngakho, abahlinzeka ngemisebenzi yezempilo kufanele bagqoke izivikelo zobuso noma izibuko ezicacile lapho besebenza neziguli.
Umphakathi obanzi ezindaweni ezithintekile noma ezingathinteka, kunconywa kakhulu ukuthi wonke umuntu ageze izandla zakhe ngensipho yokubulala amagciwane kaningi kunokujwayelekile, azame ukuhlala endlini ukuze azihlukanise futhi anciphise ukuxhumana nabantu abangase babe neziguli.
Amamitha amathathu abhekwa njengebanga elifanele abantu abahlala kude nesiguli.
Lezi zinyathelo ziyizindlela ezisebenzayo zokunciphisa ingozi yokutheleleka kanye nokuvimbela ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Yize i-SARS-CoV-2 yafika njengegciwane elisha emhlabeni womuntu, ukufana kwayo okuphezulu ne-SARS-CoV njengoba kubikwe ngoJanuwari 7, 2020 bekufanele kube yimbangela yokuqapha okukhulu eChina ngokusekelwe enkumbulweni yayo ejulile yokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-2003.
Kodwa-ke, kwaze kwaba ngu-19 kuJanuwari 2020 lapho umqondisi weZikhungo Zokulawulwa Kwezifo eWuhan eduduza izakhamizi ngokuthi leli gciwane elisha linokutheleleka okuphansi futhi linokuzala okulinganiselwe kusuka kumuntu kuya kumuntu nokuthi akuyona inkinga ukuvimbela nokuvimbela lesi sifo.
Lo mlayezo wehlisa kakhulu ukuphazamiseka komphakathi, ikakhulukazi lapho izwe lonke belungiselela uMkhosi Wentwasahlobo, futhi isikhathi esibucayi saphuthelwa ukuvimbela lesi sifo ngezinga elincane eWuhan.
Izinhlangano zokulawula izifo eChina zingase zithathe lesi sifundo esinzima futhi zenze intuthuko ebalulekile esikhathini esizayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, lezi zinhlangano kufanele (1) ziqaphele ngokwengeziwe lapho zenza izimemezelo zomphakathi njengoba wonke amazwi ebalulekile ezakhamuzi futhi angashintsha isimo sabo sengqondo nezinqumo zabo; (2) zivumelane futhi ziphenduke kakhulu nemininingwane engavamile evela emitholampilo kunokuba zilinde imibiko esemthethweni evela ko dokotela noma ezikhundleni; (3) zivimbele kakhulu ukuvimbela ubhadane olungaba khona esigabeni salo sokuqala kunokuba zizame ukududuza umphakathi; futhi (4) zivame kakhulu ukukhipha izivivinyo ezihlosiwe nezisebenzayo zokwandisa ulwazi lomphakathi ngezifo eziwubhadane nokuhlola nokuthuthukisa uhlelo lokuphendula lomphakathi ngezikhathi ezithile.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 okubangelwa yigciwane elisha i-SARS-CoV-2 kwaqala ekupheleni kukaDisemba 2019.
Ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezingu-2 sesiye sasakazeka kulo lonke elaseChina nakwamanye amazwe angaba ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke ngesikhathi kubhala lesi sihloko.
Njengoba leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV futhi izimpawu zifana phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kudale umuzwa wokuthi i-SARS iyaphindaphindeka.
Kodwa-ke, kuneminye imiehluko ephawulekayo phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni lolu bhubhane nasekwelapheni iziguli.
I-COVID-19 ithinta abantu abadala abaningi kunentsha namadoda amaningi kunabesifazane, futhi ubukhulu nokufa nabo kukhulu kubantu abadala kunentsha.
I-SARS inezifo eziphakeme kune-COVID-19 (10.91% uma iqhathaniswa no-1.44%).
Iziguli ze-COVID-19 zidlulisa leli gciwane noma zingenazo izimpawu kanti iziguli ze-SARS zivame ukulidlulisa lapho zigula kakhulu, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu kakhulu ekuvimbeleni ukusabalala kwe-COVID-19 kunese-SARS.
Lokhu kuchaza ngokwengxenye ukuthi kungani i-SARS-CoV-2 isakazeka ngokushesha futhi kabanzi kuneyase-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlolwa okujwayelekile kwe-RNA kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungaba nemiphumela engemihle kwezinye iziguli ze-COVID-19.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iziguli eziphulukisiwe zingaba ne-virus futhi.
Lezi zithombe zandisa kakhulu ingozi yokusabalala kwegciwane.
Njengoba kunenqubekela phambili esheshayo ocwaningweni lwe-COVID-19, kusadingeka ukuxazulula izinkinga eziningana ezibalulekile, njengokulandelayo:
I-SARS-CoV-2 yavelaphi?
Yize kutholakale i-96% ye-homolog yezakhi zofuzo phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-COV amabili afana ne-SARS embathi, asikwazanga ukuphetha ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela embathini.
Yisiphi isilwane esiphakathi nesidlulisela leli gciwane kumuntu owasisebenzisela lona, njengokungathi izintethe?
Ngaphandle kokwazi izimpendulo zemibuzo engu-1 no-2, asikwazi ukuvimba ukuhanjiswa kahle, futhi ukuqubuka kungaphinde kwenzeke nganoma isiphi isikhathi.
Nakuba ukuhlola okwenziwa ngamamolekyuli nokuhlolwa kwamakhemikhali okuphilayo kufakazele ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibopha ku-ACE2, igciwane lingena kanjani ngqo kumaseli emigwaqo yokuphefumula futhi libangele izinguquko ezihambisana nalezi zimo?
Ingabe leli gciwane libopha namaseli abonisa i-ACE2 kwezinye izitho?
Ngaphandle kwezimpendulo ezicacile zale mibuzo, ngeke sikwazi ukuthola isifo esisheshayo nesiqondile nokwelashwa ngendlela ephumelelayo.
Lolu bhubhane luyohlala isikhathi esingakanani?
Igciwane livela kanjani ngokofuzo lapho lidluliselwa kubantu?
Ingabe kuyoba ubhadane emhlabeni wonke, kufe njenge-SARS noma kubuye kube khona njalo njengomkhuhlane?
Kubalulekile kodwa kungase kuthathe isikhathi ukufuna izimpendulo zale mibuzo engenhla neminye eminingi.
Nokho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kudinga izindleko ezingakanani, asinayo enye indlela ngaphandle kokuqeda lolu bhubhane ngokushesha ngangokunokwenzeka futhi sibuyele ekuphileni okuvamile.
Imvelaphi ye-coronavirus yabantu ngezilwane
Ukuguquguquka nokuzivumelanisa nezimo kuye kwaholela ekuguquguqukeni kwe-coronavirus (i-CoVs) kanye namagciwane ayo, kuhlanganise nabantu, izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Ngaphambi kuka-2003, kwakwaziwa ukuthi ama-CoV amabili abantu (ama-HCoV) abangela izifo ezincane, njengokubanda okuvamile.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula esibucayi (SARS) kanye nesifo sokuphefumula saseMpumalanga Ephakathi (MERS) kuye kwaveza ukuthi ukutheleleka kwe-HCoV kungaba yingozi kanjani futhi kusongela ukuphila.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 enkabeni yeChina ekupheleni kuka-2019 kuphinde kwafaka ama-COV emgqeni futhi kwasimangaza ngokudluliselwa kwawo okuphezulu kepha kunciphise ukubangela izifo uma kuqhathaniswa nodadewabo i-SARS-CoV.
Ukutheleleka nge-HCoV kuyisifo sezilwane futhi ukuqonda imvelaphi ye-HCoVs ngezilwane kuyosisiza.
Ama-HCoV amaningi avela emibhoshongweni lapho engenawo ama-pathogenic.
Ama-host reservoir aphakathi kwamanye ama-HCoV ayaziwa.
Ukuhlonza izilwane ezibambele kunemiphumela eqondile ekuvimbeleni izifo zabantu.
Ukucwaninga ngokuxhumana kwe- CoV- host ezilwaneni nakho kungathola ukuqonda okubalulekile nge- CoV pathogenesis kubantu.
Kulesi sibuyekezo, sinikeza umbono jikelele wolwazi olukhona mayelana nama-HCoV ayisikhombisa, ngokugxila emlandweni wokutholakala kwawo kanye nemvelaphi yawo ye-zoonotic nokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo.
Okubalulekile ukuthi siqhathanisa futhi siqhathanise ama-HCoV ahlukene ngokombono wokuvela kwegciwane kanye nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-genome.
Kulokhu kuxoxwa ngobhadane lwamanje lwe-COV 2019 (i-COVID-19)
Ngaphezu kwalokho, kugcizelelwa nezidingo zokuqedwa komgcini ophumelelayo kanye nemiphumela yokuvela kwegciwane ebuhlungwini besifo.
Ama-Coronaviruses (i-CoVs) angomndeni weCoronaviridae, ohlanganisa iqembu lama-RNA ama-virus ahlanganisiwe, anemizwa emihle, anezinhlamvu eyodwa.
Lawa magciwane aqukethe i-genome enkulu kunazo zonke engama-26 kuya kuma-32 kilobases phakathi kwama-RNA amagciwane abizwa ngokuthi ama-CoVs ngenxa ye-morphology yawo efana nomqhele ngaphansi kwe-electron microscope.
Ngokwesakhiwo, ama-COV anezinhlanga ezingahlukanisiwe ze-genome ezabelane ngenhlangano efanayo.
Cishe izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu ze-genome ziqukethe ama-frame amabili amakhulu avulekile afundwayo (ORF1a ne-ORF1b), ahunyushelwa kuma-p1a ne-pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Amaphrotheni amaningi aqhubeka ecutshungulwa ukuze akhiqize amaprotheni ayi-16 angeyona eyakhiwe, abhalwe ngokuthi i-nsp1 ~ 16.
Ingxenye esele ye-genome iqukethe ama-ORF wamaprotheni ezakhiwo, kuhlanganise ne-spike (S), i-envelope (E), i-membrane (M) ne-nucleoprotein (N).
Amaprotheni amaningi okuhambisana nezinhlanga nawo abhalwe ngezinhlanga ezahlukene ze-COV.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlukeni kwamasekhondi wamaprotheni, ama-CoV ahlukaniswa abe izinhlobo ezine (i-alpha-CoV, i-beta-CoV, i-gamma-CoV ne-delta-CoV), phakathi kwazo izihlobo ze-beta-CoV ziqukethe ama-HCoV amaningi futhi zihlukaniswe zibe izizukulwane ezine (A, B, C no-D).
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic buveze ukuthi izintethe nezimpethu zisebenza njengomthombo wezakhi zofuzo zama-alpha-CoVs amaningi nama-beta-CoVs, kuyilapho izinyoni ziyisikhungo esiyinhloko sama-gamma-CoVs nama-delta-CoVs.
Sekuyizinkulungwane zeminyaka ama-COV eqhubeka ewela imingcele yezinhlobo futhi amanye aye abonakala njengezifo ezibalulekile zabantu.
Kuze kube manje, ama-CoV abantu ayisikhombisa (ama-HCoVs) ayaziwa.
Phakathi kwazo i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-NL63 yi-alpha-CoVs.
Amanye ama-beta-CoV amahlanu afaka i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1, i-coronavirus ye-acute respiratory syndrome (SARS-CoV), i-coronavirus ye-Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS-CoV) ne-SARS-CoV-2.
I-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63 ngokuvamile zibangela izimpawu ezincane, njengokubanda okuvamile kanye / noma isifo sohudo.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 esanda kutholakala inobuthi obukhulu, ibangela ukutheleleka okubucayi komgwaqo wokuphefumula ongaphansi ezigulini eziningi kakhulu ezinethuba eliphakeme lokuthuthukisa isifo sokucindezeleka kokuphefumula okubucayi (ARDS) kanye nezimpawu ezingaphandle kwamaphaphu.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E, i-B814, lwahlukaniswa ekudlulisweni kwemithambo yemihlathi yabagulayo abanomkhuhlane ovamile maphakathi nawo-1960.
Kusukela lapho, ulwazi olwengeziwe lwaqoqwa ngezifundo ezibanzi ze-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, zombili ezibangela izimpawu ezizivimbelayo.
Ngempela, umqondo wawusamukelwa kabanzi wokuthi ukutheleleka ngama-HCoVs ngokuvamile akulimazi kuze kube ukuqubuka kwe-SARS.
Ukuqubuka kwe-SARS okwaqala ngo-2003 kungenye yezingozi kakhulu emlandweni wamanje, kuthinta abantu abangaphezu kuka-8.000 ngesilinganiso sokufa esingamaphesenti angaba ngu-10 sezigameko ezingavamile.
Ngemva kweminyaka eyishumi, ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula saseMpumalanga Ephakathi (MERS) kwaholela esifweni esiqhubekayo eNhlonhlweni Yase-Arabhiya, esisakazeka kancane kancane emhlabeni wonke.
I-HCoV entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV), kamuva eyabizwa ngokuthi yi-SARS-CoV-2, iyimbangela yokuqubuka kwesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19), esibulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3 120 futhi sabulala abantu abangaphezu kuka-91 000 ngoMashi 3, 2020.
Isimemezelo sesishaye indiva futhi umhlaba kufanele ulungiselele ubhadane oluzayo lwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Zonke izinhlobo eziyisikhombisa ze-HCoVs zinomsuka we-zoonotic kusuka kumagundane, amagundane noma izilwane zasendlini.
Imigqa eminingi yobufakazi isekela imvelaphi yokuziphendukela kwemvelo yazo zonke i-HCoVs kusuka kumagundane, lapho amagciwane ahlangabezana kahle futhi engekho-pathogenic kodwa ekhombisa ukwehluka okukhulu kofuzo.
Ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luye lwaletha izinselelo ezinkulu kwezokwelapha, ezesayensi, ezenhlalo nezokuziphatha eChina nasemhlabeni wonke.
Ukulandelela imvelaphi ye-zoonotic ye-HCoVs kunikeza uhlaka lokuqonda umlando wemvelo, amandla ashukumisayo kanye nezakhi zokuvimbela izinhlobo zokugxuma.
Lokhu kungaqondisa noma kusize ukucinga indawo yokugcina izilwane, eziphakathi nezisebenzayo ze-SARS-CoV-2, okuzoba nemiphumela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni ukuchitheka kwesikhathi esizayo.
Kulesi sibuyekezo sinikeza umbono jikelele ngemvelaphi ye-zoonotic, ukudluliselwa kwezinhlobo kanye ne-pathogenesis ye-HCoVs.
Ikakhulukazi, sigcizelela futhi sixoxe ngendaba ejwayelekile yokuthi amagciwane omzali we-HCoVs ngokuvamile awabangelwa yi-pathogenic kumagumbi awo emvelo kodwa aba yi-pathogenic ngemuva kokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo kuya kumgcini omusha.
Siphinde sibuyekeze ukuthambekela kokuvela kwe-HCoV lapho ukwanda kokudluliselwa kuvame ukuza nokwehla kokubangela izifo.
Umphumela wokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okuqhubekayo nawo uxoxwa ngawo kulo mongo.
Ama-CoV ezilwane aye aziwa kusukela ngasekupheleni kwawo-1930.
Ngaphambi kokuhlukaniswa kokuqala kohlobo lwe-HCoV-229E B814 kusuka ekukhishwe kwemihlathi yeziguli ezazithole umkhuhlane ovamile, ama-COV ahlukahlukene ayehlukaniswe ezilwaneni ezahlukahlukene ezithathelwe igciwane, kufaka phakathi inkukhu, igundane, inkomo, ingulube, ikati nenja.
Emashumini eminyaka adlule, kuye kwahlolwa ama-HCoV ayisikhombisa.
Ukufingqa kafushane umlando wokutholakala kwe-HCoV ngokulandelana kwesikhathi (ithebula 1) kungaba okufundisayo nokufundisayo.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E lwahlukaniswa emigwaqweni yokuphefumula yabagulayo abanesifo semigwaqo yokuphefumula engenhla ngonyaka ka-1966, futhi kamuva lwavumelaniswa nokukhula emigqeni yamaseli wamaphaphu e-WI-38.
Iziguli ezithathwe yi-HCoV-229E zabonisa izimpawu ezivamile zokubanda, ezihlanganisa ikhanda elibuhlungu, ukuqhuma, ukuphazamiseka kanye nokuthukwa, kanti ukushisa nokukhwehlela kwabonakala kumacala angu-10~20%.
Kamuva ngo-1967, i-HCoV-OC43 yahlukaniswa ne-organ culture futhi kamuva yadlula ebuchosheni bamagundane ancelisayo.
Izici zomtholampilo zokutheleleka kwe-HCoV-OC43 zibonakala zifana nalezo ezibangelwa yi-HCoV-229E, ezingahlukaniseki ngezibonakaliso kusuka ekutheleleni nezinye izifo zokuphefumula ezifana namagciwane omkhuhlane A namagciwane e-rhinoviruses.
Kokubili i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43 zisakazwa emhlabeni wonke, futhi zivame ukudluliselwa kakhulu ngesikhathi sasebusika esimweni sezulu esimnene.
Ngokuvamile, isikhathi sokuvundiswa kwalezi zinambuzane ezimbili singakapheli isonto elilodwa, silandelwe isifo esingamasonto amabili.
Ngokwezifundo zabantu abavolontiya, abantu abaphilile abane-HCoV-229E bathola umkhuhlane omncane.
Iziguli ezimbalwa kuphela ezazinesifo sokuzivikela emagxeni zazithola zinezifo eziyingozi zendlela yokuphefumula.
I-SARS, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-atypical pneumonia, yayiwumqedazwe wokuqala obhalwe kahle obangelwe yi-HCoV emlandweni wesintu futhi i-agent ye-etiological yi-SARS-CoV, i-HCoV yesithathu etholakele.
Icala lokuqala le-SARS lingalandelwa emuva ekupheleni kuka-2002 esifundazweni saseGuangdong eChina.
Ubhadane lwe-SARS lwaholela ezigulini ezingu-8 096 ezibikiwe neziguli ezingu-774, zasakazeka emazweni amaningi namazwekazi.
Ngaphandle kwabasakazekayo, kulinganiselwa ukuthi icala ngalinye lingabangela izigameko ezimbili eziphindwe kabili, ngenkathi yokufudumala yezinsuku ezi-4 kuye kwezi-7 futhi isiqongo somthwalo we-viral sibonakala ngosuku lwe-10 lokugula.
Iziguli ezithathwe yi-SARS-CoV ekuqaleni zine-myalgia, ikhanda elibuhlungu, umkhuhlane, ukuwohloka komzimba kanye nokuthuthumela, kulandele ukuphazamiseka komoya, ukukhwehlela nokucindezeleka kokuphefumula njengezimpawu zokugcina.
I-Lymphopenia, ukuhlolwa kwesibindi okungasebenzi kahle, kanye nokwenyuka kwe-creatine kinase kuyiziphazamiso ezivamile ze-SARS.
Ukulimala kwe-alveolar okuhlakazekile, ukwanda kwamangqamuzana e-epithelial nokwanda kwama-macrophages nakho kuye kwabonwa ezigulini ze-SARS.
Cishe ama-20-3% eziguli adinga ukunakekelwa okujulile nokuthuthwa komoya.
Ngaphezu kwezitho zokuphefumula ezingezansi, izitho eziningi kuhlanganise nomzila wesisu, isibindi nezinso nazo zingase zitheleleke kulezi zimo ezinzima, ngokuvamile zihambisana nesiphepho se- cytokine, esingabulala ikakhulukazi ezigulini ezinesifo sokuzivikela.
Leli gciwane laqala ukuhlukaniswa ekuhlolweni komzimba komzimba womuntu owayehlobene nesiguli esihluphekile esiye eHong Kong sisuka eGuangzhou.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, kuye kwenziwa imizamo emikhulu ocwaningweni lwe-HCoV.
I-HCoV-NL63 yahlukaniswa nengane enezinyanga ezingu-7 yaseNetherlands ngasekupheleni kuka-2004.
Ekuqaleni kwabonwa ukuthi kuyanda ezinganeni ezincane, kubantu abadala kanye neziguli ezinesifo sokuphefumula.
Ukuvezwa kwe-coryza, i-conjunctivitis, umkhuhlane, ne-bronchiolitis kuvamile kulesi sifo esibangelwa yi-HCoV-NL63.
Olunye ucwaningo olungazimele lwachaza ukuhlukaniswa kwegciwane elifanayo nesampula lephunga kumfana oneminyaka engu-8 ubudala onesifo samaphaphu eNetherlands.
Nakuba yahlonza eNetherlands, empeleni isakazwa emhlabeni wonke.
Kulinganiselwa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 ihlanganisa cishe ama-4.7% ezifo ezivamile zokuphefumula, futhi ukuvela kwayo okuphezulu kwenzeka ekuqaleni kwehlobo, entwasahlobo nasebusika.
I-HCoV-NL63 ihlobene ne-laryngitis evimbelayo, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-croup.
Ngonyaka ofanayo, i-HCoV-HKU1 yahlukaniswa nendoda eneminyaka engu-71 ubudala eyayiboshwe esibhedlela ngenxa yokuphefumula ne-bronchiolitis eHong Kong.
Ngaphandle kokungenwa isifo samaphaphu nesifo se-bronchiolitis emphakathini, i-HCoV-HKU1 ibike ukuthi ihlobene nokuqina komoya okubucayi.
Ngokufana ne-HCoV-NL63, i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 itholakale emhlabeni wonke, ibangela izifo zokuphefumula ezilula.
Zonke lezi zinhlobo ezine ze-HCoV ezitholakala emphakathini ziye zavumelaniswa kahle nabantu futhi ngokuvamile azivamile ukuguquka zibangele izifo ezibangelwa izifo, yize izingozi zenzeka ngezizathu ezingaziwa njengasesimweni esingavamile sohlobo oluthile lwe-HCoV-NL63, olwabikwa muva nje ukuthi lubangela ukutheleleka okunzima komgwaqo wokuphefumula ongaphansi eChina.
Ngokuvamile, lapho lezi zingane ze-HCoV zithola ikhono lokudlulisela kahle futhi zizigcine zingapheli ngaphakathi kwabantu, nazo ziba nzima kakhulu noma zingabangela izifo.
I-MERS-CoV yahlukaniswa okokuqala ngo-2012 emaphashini esiguli esineminyaka engama-60 ubudala esathuthuka isifo samaphaphu esibucayi kanye nokwehluleka kwezinso eSaudi Arabia.
Nakuba iningi lamacala aqinisekiswe ngelabhorethri evela eMpumalanga Ephakathi, kuye kwabikwa amacala angenisiwe anezinkinga ezihambisana nokuxhumana okuqondile emazweni ahlukahlukene aseYurophu naseTunisia.
Kwavela esinye isifo esiyingqayizivele eNingizimu Korea ngo-2015 lapho kwaqinisekiswa khona iziguli ezingu-186.
Izimpawu zokwelashwa kwe-MERS zifana nezase-SARS, ezibonakala ngokuqhubeka komdlavuza womoya osheshayo.
Ngokungafani ne-SARS, iziguli eziningi ezine-MERS nazo zaqala ukwehluleka kwezinso okubucayi, okuyinto kuze kube manje eyingqayizivele ye-MERS phakathi kwezifo ezibangelwa i-HCoV.
Iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-30% zinezimpawu zesisu, njengokukhwehlela nokuhlanza.
Kusukela ngoFebhuwari 14, 2020, kwabikwa amacala angaphezu kuka-2500 aqinisekisiwe e laboratory ngenani eliphakeme lamacala okufa angama-34.4%, okwenza i-MERS-CoV ibe enye yamagciwane abhubhisayo kakhulu aziwa ngabantu.
Phakathi noDisemba 2019 kuya ngasekupheleni, kwabonwa amaqembu eziguli ezinesifo samaphaphu ezaziwa emuva emuva ukuthi zihlobene nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
I-World Health Organization imemezele ukuqubuka okuqhubekayo kwesifo sokutheleleka komzila wokuphefumula ongaphansi okubangelwa yi-SARS-CoV-2 njenge-Public Health Emergency of International Concern futhi yabiza lesi sifo ngokuthi i-COVID-19.
Kusukela ngoMashi 3, 2020, amacala angama-90,053 aqinisekisiwe emhlabeni wonke, kanti ukufa kwabantu abangelayo ngamacala angama-3.4%.
Ngokuphawulekayo, inani labantu abafa e-Hubei, eChina, lingamaphesenti angu-4,2 kanti elingaphandle kwalo lingamaphesenti angu-1,2%.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ibangela ukutheleleka komoya okunzima njenge-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, okukhishwa njengokushisa, ukukhwehlela kanye ne-dyspnea.
Ukudla kwamanzi nakho kubonakala kwezinye iziguli.
Isifo samaphaphu singesinye sezimpawu ezinzima kakhulu futhi singasheshe siphenduke isifo sokuphefumula esibucayi.
Yize i-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zifana kakhulu ngenxa ye-homology ephezulu ye-nucleotide sequence engu-82%, ziqoqa zibe amagatsha ahlukene esihlahleni se-phylogenetic.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusobala ayiyona i-pathogenic kodwa iyadluliselwa kakhulu uma iqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Kubikwe ukuthi kunabantu abangenazo izimpawu ababhekene ne-SARS-CoV-2 futhi bangabangela ukuthi isakazeke ngokushesha emhlabeni wonke.
Ukuqhathanisa nokuqhathanisa i-SARS-CoV-2 namanye ama-HCoV ayisithupha kuveza ukufana nokwehluka okuthakazelisa kakhulu.
Okokuqala, isikhathi sokuvundiswa nesikhathi sokuhamba kwesifo se-HCoV sifana kakhulu.
Kulokhu, i-SARS-CoV-2 ilandela ukuthambekela okujwayelekile kwamanye ama-HCoV ayisithupha.
Okwesibili, ubukhulu bezimpawu ze-COVID-19 buphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV nama-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini (isb. i-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63).
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubonisa izici ezivame kakhulu ukubonakala ngesikhathi sokutheleleka ngama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini, kufaka phakathi ukubonakaliswa kwezimpawu ezingekho, ezincane noma ezingenayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, kunesabelo esincane samacala aqine e-COVID-19 futhi esingabonakala njengasesenzweni sokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV, yize isilinganiso siphansi kancane.
Okwesithathu, ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubonisa futhi amaphethini athakazelisayo ahlobene nama-HCoVs atholakala emphakathini kanye ne-SARS-CoV.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okungenani kuphakeme njengaleyo ye-HCoVs etholakala emphakathini.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, kusamele kuqinisekiswe ukuthi ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kwehla yini ngemuva kokudlula kubantu njengoba kunjalo ngamacala e-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Ekugcineni, njengezinye i-HCoVs, i-SARS-CoV-2 ingatholakala kumasampula we-fecal.
Ukuthi ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngomlomo nge-fecal kudlala indima ebalulekile njengase-SARS-CoV okungenani ngaphansi kwezimo ezithile kusamele kucaciswe yizifundo zesikhathi esizayo.
Kuyathakazelisa kakhulu futhi ukubona ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ingabonisa yini ukuthi inkathi njengoba kunjalo ngama-HCoV atholakala emphakathini.
Noma kunjalo, izici ze-SARS-CoV-2 kufaka phakathi ukutheleleka kwayo, ubuthi kanye nokusabalala okuqhubekayo ngemuva kokudlula kubantu kuzoba nethonya elikhulu ekuqhamukeleni kokuphela kokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19.
Zonke izimpawu ezine ze-HCoV ezitholakala emphakathini ezibangela izimpawu ezincane ziye zavumelaniswa kahle nabantu.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, kungase kube yiqiniso nokuthi abantu baye bavumelanisa kahle nalezi zinhlobo ezine ze-HCoVs.
Ngamanye amazwi, bobabili bangase babe abasindile ezifweni zasendulo ze-HCoV.
Ama-HCoV abangela izifo ezinzima kubantu nakubantu ababenesifo esinzima se-HCoV asuswe.
Ukuze lokhu kwenzeke, ama-HCoVs kufanele aphindeke kubantu ngezinga elanele ukuvumela ukuqoqwa kwezimpawu zokuguquguquka ezivumelanayo eziphikisana nezici zokunciphisa izivakashi.
Ngale ndlela, isikhathi eside ukuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kuqhubeka futhi abantu abaningi abathintekayo, amathuba okuba ukuthi izovumelana ngokuphelele nabantu ayanda.
Uma ilungiswa kahle, ukudluliselwa kwayo kubantu kungaba nzima ukuvimbela ngokukhishwa kwabantu noma ezinye izindlela zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Sekuyiminyaka eminingi, ama-COV amane atholakala emphakathini ehlakazeka kubantu, okwenza abantu abanomzimba ongenawo amakhemikhali babe nomkhuhlane.
La magciwane awadingi indawo yokugcina izilwane.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV ezibangela izifo eziphezulu azivumelananga kahle nabantu futhi ukudluliselwa kwazo kubantu akunakusekelwa.
Kumelwe zigcine futhi zande ezindaweni zazo zokugcina izilwane futhi zifune ithuba lokufinyelela emizimbeni yabantu, mhlawumbe nge-host eyodwa noma eziningi eziphakathi nezinkulu.
I-SARS-CoV-2 inezici ezifana ne-SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV kanye ne-HCoVs ezine ezitholakala emphakathini.
I-HCoV ithinteka kakhulu njenge-HCoVs etholakala emphakathini, okungenani okwamanje.
Kodwa-ke, i-HCoVs etholakala emphakathini i-pathogenic kakhulu futhi i-HCoVs engaphansi kwe-SARS-CoV noma i-MERS-CoV.
Kusamele kubonwe ukuthi izovumelana ngokuphelele nabantu futhi izungeze abantu ngaphandle kwesikhwama noma isilwane esiphakathi.
Ngaphambi kokuxoxa ngemvelaphi yezilwane ze-HCoVs, kuzosisiza kakhulu ukuxoxa ngezincazelo nezici zezinsiza eziphendukelayo, zemvelo, ezisesidlekeni, eziphakathi nezisebenzayo ze-HCoVs.
Isilwane sisebenza njengendawo yokwamukela i-HCoV uma sihlala nomkhulu oxhumene kakhulu ohlanganyela i-homology ephezulu ezingeni lokulandelana kwama-nucleotide.
Igciwane lokhokho ngokuvamile lizivumelanisa kahle futhi alizihluphi kule ndawo.
Ngokufanayo, indawo yokugcina amanzi ihlala i-HCoV ngokuqhubekayo nangesikhathi eside.
Kuzo zombili lezi zimo, izibukeli zitheleleke ngokwemvelo futhi ziyizibukeli zemvelo ze-HCoV noma igciwane lomzali walo.
Ngokuphambene nalokho, uma i-HCoV isanda kwethulwa kumgcini ophakathi ngaphambi noma nxazonke zokwethula kwayo kubantu, ayizivumelanisi kahle nomgcini omusha futhi ivame ukuba ne-pathogenic.
Lo mgcini ophakathi angenza umsebenzi wokuba umthombo we-zoonotic wokutheleleka komuntu futhi adlale indima yomgcini wokuthuthukisa ngokuvumela igciwane ukuba liziphindaphinde okwesikhashana bese lilidlulisela kubantu ukuze likhulise isikali sokutheleleka komuntu.
I-HCoV ingabhekana nokutheleleka okungenakuqedwa uma ingakwazi ukuqhubeka nokudluliselwa kwayo ngaphakathi komsingathi ophakathi.
Ngokuphambene nalokho, ama-HCoVs nawo angakwazi ukuzivumelanisa nomgcini ophakathi futhi ngisho nokufakazela ukuthi anobhubhane isikhathi eside.
Kulokhu, umninikhaya ophakathi uba umninikhaya wemvelo.
Idatha ye-epidemiological iveze emuva kwesikhathi ukuthi icala le-SARS lalinomlando wokuxhumana nezilwane zasendle.
Ucwaningo olwalwenziwe kamuva lwe-seroprevalence lwabonisa ukuthi abathengisi bezilwane babenesilinganiso esiphakeme se-IgG e-anti-SARS-CoV uma kuqhathaniswa nesabantu abavamile.
Izimpukane zesundu ezifihlakeleyo (Paguma larvata) nenja ye-racoon ezimakethe zezilwane eziphilayo zaqala ukubonwa njengezithwele amagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV afana ne-SARS-CoV.
Lokhu kwaxhaswa ngokungaqondile iqiniso lokuthi akukho okunye ukuxilongwa kwe-SARS okwaboniswa ngemuva kokubulala wonke ama-civet ezimakethe.
Kodwa-ke, kubikwe ukuthi ama-palm civets amasha avela endle noma emapulazini ngaphandle kokubekwa ezimakethe zezilwane eziphilayo ayebonakala engakhi kakhulu ku-SARS-CoV, okusikisela ukuthi ama-palm civets amasha angase asebenze kuphela njengendawo yokugcina i-amplifying kodwa hhayi indawo yokugcina yemvelo ye-SARS-CoV.
Okuphawulekayo ukuthi njengoba izilwane ezahlukahlukene ezimakethe eGuangzhou zine-antibodies ye-SARS-CoV, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlobo eziningi zezilwane ezincanyana nazo zingase zisebenze njengezivakashi eziphakathi eziqinisa i-SARS-CoV azikwazi ukuvinjelwa.
Zonke lezi zibonakala ziyizindwendwe ezifiphele ze-SARS-CoV.
Ukuphenywa okulandelayo kwesilwane esingokwemvelo esibambele i-SARS-CoV kuveze i-COV yezinambuzane ezihlobene eduze, ebizwa nge-SARS-related Rhinolophus bat CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), ekhona ezinambuzane zaseChina ezikhwebheni.
Lezi zimvemvane zinemiphumela emihle ye-anti-SARS-CoV antibodies kanye nokulandelana kwe-genome ye-SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Leyo kanye nezinye i-COVs zamaphaphu zihlanganisa i-88-92% ye-nucleotide sequence homology ne-SARS-CoV.
Lezi zifundo ziye zabekela isisekelo somqondo omusha wokuthi izimpungushe zibamba izifo ezibangelwa ukuvuvukala kwabantu.
Ama-COV amaningana afana ne-SARS (SL-CoVs) nawo abonwe emibhedeni, kepha akekho ngaphandle kwe-WIV1 eyodwa ekhonjwe engahlukaniswa njengegciwane eliphilayo.
I-enzyme 2 eguqula i-angiotensin yabantu (ACE2) yaziwa ukuthi iyamukela i-SARS-CoV.
I-WIV1 etholakala esampula le-fecal le-bat yayisetshenziswa njengendlela yokungenisa amaseli.
Okuhlaba umxhwele ukuthi amasera eziguli eziphila nge-SARS akwazi ukuvimbela i-WIV1.
Kuze kube manje, i-WIV1 imele ukhokho oxhumene kakhulu we-SARS-CoV emibhedeni, ehlanganyela i-95% ye-nucleotide sequence homology.
Yize ukufana okuphezulu phakathi kwalezi zinambuzane ezimbili, ngokuvamile kukholakala ukuthi i-WIV1 akuyona igciwane lomzali osheshayo we-SARS-CoV futhi izintethe aziyona indawo yokugcina impahla osheshayo we-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kuhlanganisa i-MERS-CoV eqenjini elifanayo ne-bat CoV-HKU4 ne-bat CoV-HKU5.
I-Bat CoV-HKU4 ne-MERS-CoV zisebenzisa i-host receptor efanayo, i-dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), yokungena kwegciwane.
Ukulandelana kwe-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase ye-MERS-CoV kusondele kakhulu ku-phylogenetically kumlingani we-bat beta-CoVs atholakala eYurophu nase-Afrika.
Kuze kube manje, akukho MERS-CoV ephilayo etholakala emibhedeni yasendle.
I-MERS-CoV ne-Cov-HKU25 yomkhonto wayo osondelene kakhulu bane-87% kuphela yokufana kwe-nucleotide sequence.
Ngakho, izintuthwane kungenzeka zingabi isivakashi esiseduze se-MERS-CoV.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ucwaningo eMpumalanga Ephakathi luye lwabonisa ukuthi amakamela angama-dromedary ane-seropositive for MERS-CoV-specific neutralizing antibodies, afana namakamela avela eMpumalanga Ephakathi avela emazweni amaningi ase-Afrika.
I-MERS-CoV ephilayo efana negciwane elitholakala kubantu yahlukaniswa kusuka kuma-swabs asemvelweni wamakamela angama-dromedary, okukhombisa ukuthi amakamela asebenza njengendawo yokugcina impahla ye-MERS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka nokuthi ngokuvamile izimpawu ezincane kodwa ukuvuza okukhulu kwegciwane kwabonwa kumakamela atheleleke ngokuhlolwa nge-MERS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi amakamela atheleleke awachithi amagciwane kuphela ngendlela yokuphefumula kodwa nangendlela yokuchitheka yomlomo, okubuye kube yindlela eyinhloko yokukhishwa kwegciwane emagundwini.
Kodwa-ke, kusekhona imibuzo ngoba amacala amaningi aqinisekisiwe e-MERS awanawo umlando wokuxhumana namakamela ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu, okucatshangwa ukuthi kungenxa yokudluliselwa komuntu kumuntu noma izindlela zokudlulisa ezingaziwa ezibandakanya izinhlobo zezilwane ezingaziwa ezihlala ku-MERS-CoV.
I-SARS-CoV-2 yabelana nge-96.2% ye-nucleotide homology ne-bat CoV RaTG13 ehlukaniswe kusuka ku-Rhinolophus affinis bats.
Njengasezimweni ze-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, ukwehluka kokulandelelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RATG13 kukhulu kakhulu ukuthi kungabelwana ngobudlelwano babazali.
Okusho ukuthi, izintuthwane kungenzeka zingabi yizivakashi eziseduze ze-SARS-CoV-2 ngaphandle kokuthi kutholakale ama-COV ezifana kakhulu esikhathini esizayo.
Cishe, izilwane eziphakathi nezilwane ze-SARS-CoV-2 kufanele zibe phakathi kwezinhlobo zezilwane zasendle ezithengiswa futhi zibulawa eHuanan Seafood Wholesale Market, lapho amacala amaningi okuqala e-COVID-19 ahlobene khona, okukhombisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi kudluliselwe izilwane kubantu.
Ucwaningo lwamuva olwenziwe ngokulandelana kwe-metagenomic lubonise ukuthi iqembu lezilwane ezincane ezisengozini yokuqothulwa ezaziwa ngokuthi ama-pangolins (Manis javanica) nazo zingaba ne-beta-CoVs yasendulo ehlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lawa ma-genome amasha e-pangolin CoV ahlanganyela i-85%-92% ye-nucleotide sequence homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, zihlobene eduze ne-RaTG13 nge-90% yokufana ezingeni lokulandelana kwama-nucleotide.
Zihlanganiswa zibe yizinhlobo ezimbili ze-SARS-CoV-2-like viruses esihlahleni se-phylogenetic, enye yazo ehlanganyela i-receptor binding domain (RBD) efana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2, enobunikazi besizinda se-amino acid esingu-97.4%.
Ngokuphambene, ama-RBD e-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahlukahlukene, yize ephakeme kakhulu ekuhambisaneni kwe-homology ye-sequence ku-genome yonke.
Ucwaningo olwedlule kuma-pangolin agulayo lubike nokuthi kutholakale ama-contigs omdlavuza kumasampula emiphungushe, okubonakala ukuthi ahlobene ngokufanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lolu cwaningo lwamukela izindlela ezahlukene zokuhlanganisa nokugcinwa ngesandla ukuze kukhiqizwe ukulandelana kwe-genome okuyingxenye okuhlanganisa cishe u-86.3% we-genome ye-viral yesikhathi esigcwele.
Asikwazi ukukhipha ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi i-pangolin ingenye yezilwane eziphakathi ezibambele i-SARS-CoV-2.
Kodwa-ke, okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obusekela imvelaphi eqondile ye-pangolin ye-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokuhlukahluka kokulandelelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ehlobene ne-beta-CoVs.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ibanga eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 lifushane ngisho nangaphezu kwebanga eliphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ehlobene ne-beta-CoVs.
Indlela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-SARS-CoV-2 emagundane, ama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo isazosungulwa.
Ngenkathi i-homology yokulandelelana ephezulu itholakale kuma-RBD phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin, ama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, i-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RATG13 ahlanganyela i-homology yokulandelelana ephezulu kakhulu ye-genome-wide.
Kucatshangwa kakhulu ukuthi ukufana okuphezulu phakathi kwama-RBD e-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ahlobene nama-beta-CoVs ne-SARS-CoV-2 kubangelwa ukuguquguquka okuhambisana nokukhetha.
Iphikisana nesiphakamiso sokusebenzisana kabusha phakathi kwe-pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoV ne-RaTG13 kuhlobo lwesithathu lwezilwane zasendle.
Njengamandla ashukumisayo ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kusakazeke kakhulu phakathi kwama-beta-CoVs.
Ijaji lisalokhu lingaqiniseki ngemvelaphi eqondile ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngaphandle kwama-HCoVs anobuthi obuphezulu, kufundwe nangomthombo we-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-HKU1.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic buveze ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-229E kungenzeka ukuthi zavela kuma-CoV ezimpungushe, kanti amagciwane omzali we-HCoV-OC43 ne-HCoV-HKU1 atholakala ezigqonyeni.
Kubikwe ukuthi i-bat CoV ebizwa nge-ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) etholwe embathini omnyama onemibala emithathu waseNyakatho Melika ibonise ubudlelwane obuseduze ne-HCoV-NL63.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-HCoV-229E yayihlobene ngokofuzo nenye i-Cov bat, ebizwa ngeHipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, etholwe eGhana, kanti kusolwa ukuthi ama-camellids nawo angumbungazi wayo ophakathi.
Ukuze kucace, ulwazi lwamanje ngemvelaphi yezilwane yama-HCoV aziwayo lufingqiwe kumfanekiso 1 nakwethebula 2.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kunikeze ubufakazi bezenzakalo zokudluliselwa kwe-HCoVs phakathi kwezinhlobo emlandweni.
Lapho i-HCoV-OC43 iwela izinhlobo ukuze itheleleke kubantu abavela emfuyweni yasekhaya cishe ngo-1890, kwaqoshwa ubhadane lokutheleleka komoya.
Umlando wokudluliselwa kwe-HCoV-229E phakathi kwezinhlobo awucaci kangako.
Kuye kwatholakala ukuthi ama-alpha-CoVs ombathe ahlobene kakhulu ne-HCoV-229E.
Phakathi kwazo kukhona i-alpaca alpha-CoV.
Kunobufakazi obuningi obusekela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane kusuka emagundane kuya kubantu ngokuqondile.
Okokuqala, abantu, kodwa hhayi ama-alpaca, bangase babe nokuxhumana nezimpungushe endaweni ehlangene yezemvelo.
Kunalokho, abantu basondelana kakhulu nama-alpaca.
Okwesibili, ama-alpha-CoVs ezinhlansi ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E ahlukahlukene futhi awabangelwa yizifo ezinhlansi, kanti i-alpaca alpha-CoV ibangele ukuqubuka kwezifo zokuphefumula ezilwaneni ezithathelwanayo.
Ekugcineni, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ayitholakalanga ezilwaneni zasendle.
Ngakho-ke, kungenzeka ukuthi ama-alpacas athole i-alpha-CoV ehlobene ne-HCoV-229E kubantu ayikwazi ukukhanselwa.
Empeleni, izintuthwane zingumthombo oqondile wamagciwane abangela izifo kubantu kuhlanganise negciwane le-rabies, igciwane le-Ebola, igciwane le-Nipah ne-Hendra.
Ngakho-ke akumangazi ukuthi izintethe zingadlulisela i-HCoV-229E ngqo kubantu.
Ngenye indlela, kuyilapho ama-alpha-CoVs ombathe esebenza njenge-gen pool ye-HCoV-229E, ama-alpacas namakamela e-dromedary angasebenza njengezindwendwe eziphakathi ezidlulisela amagciwane kubantu, njengoba kunjalo nange-MERS-CoV.
I-MERS-CoV isebenza njengesibonelo esihle sokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo kusuka emagundane kuya kumakamela angama-dromedary kanye namakamela angama-dromedary kuya kubantu.
Imvelaphi yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-MERS-CoV evela emagundane yaziwa lapho ihlolwa kuqala futhi iye yaqiniswa futhi okutholakele kamuva.
Kuyacaca ukuthi izintuthwane zinikeza inqwaba yezinhlobo zamagciwane ukuze kushintshwe izingcezu zofuzo phakathi kwezinhlobo nokudluliselwa kwazo.
Ukuphila isikhathi eside, izindawo ezihlala abantu abaningi, ukusebenzisana kwabantu eduze nekhono lokundiza eliqinile kuyindlela enhle yokuba izimpungushe zibe 'umchithi we-virus' ongcono.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV iye yaziswa kumakamela angama-dromedary amashumi eminyaka.
Ivumelana kahle nalezi zingamela eziye zaphenduka isizinda esiphakathi zaba isizinda esizinzile nesingokwemvelo.
I-MERS-CoV ibangela isifo esibuthaka kakhulu futhi igcina izinga lokuguquka eliphansi kulezi zilwane.
Ukudluliselwa kwayo kwabantu ngezikhathi ezithile kuyingozi futhi abantu bahlala bengenawo amandla okuthumela i-MERS-CoV njengoba ukudluliselwa kwayo kungeke kuqhubeke.
Ngokuphambene nendima yamakamela ekudluliseni i-MERS-CoV, indima yama-pangolin, uma ikhona, ekudluliseni i-SARS-CoV-2 ihlukile.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-pangolin beta-CoVs anobuthi obukhulu kuma-pangolin.
Bangase babe yizivakashi ezingapheli zama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, afana nama-civet esimweni se-SARS-CoV.
Izindlela eziningana zokudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 eziphakathi kwezinhlobo kusuka ezilwaneni ziye kubantu kufanele zikhishwe noma zikhishwe ezifundweni ezizayo.
Okokuqala, izintuthwane zingaba iziboshwa zesikhwama se-SARS-CoV-2 esihlobene negciwane elifana ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bangase bahlanganyele imvelo nezimpungushe ngokubulala noma ngokumba amalahle.
Okwesibili, ama-pangolin angaba enye yezinsiza eziphakathi eziqinisa lapho i-SARS-CoV-2-virus ehlobene nayo isanda kwethulwa.
Abantu bathola leli gciwane ngokubulala nangokudla inyama yezilwane zasendle.
Kungenzeka ukuthi izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya zivame ukutheleleka yi-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuhlolwa kwezilwane zasendle nezasendle ukuze kutholakale izidumbu kuyadingeka.
Okwesithathu, njengoba kushiwo ngenhla, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha nokuguqulwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungenzeka kwenzeke ohlotsheni lwesithathu oluxhumana nezinambuzane nama-pangolin.
Ukufuna imvelaphi yezilwane ze-SARS-CoV-2 kusasebenza.
Ngaphandle kwezinhlobo ezahlukene zezilwane ezibambele, izici ezintathu ezinkulu ohlangothini lwegciwane nazo zibalulekile ekuthuthukiseni ama-COVs ukuba adlule izithiyo zezinhlobo.
Okokuqala, izinga labo lokuguquka eliphezulu kakhulu ekuphindaphindeni i-RNA.
Uma kuqhathaniswa namanye amagciwane e-RNA anemichilo eyodwa, izinga lokuguquka elilinganiselwe lama-COV lingabhekwa njenge- kulinganisela kuya ku-kulinganisela ngenani eliphakathi lokuthintela elilinganiselwa ku-10-4 ngonyaka ngesayithi 2, kuye ngokuthi isigaba sokuzivumelanisa kwe-COV nezingosi ezintsha.
Ama-COV ane-exoribonuclease eqondiswayo, ukususwa kwawo okuholela ekuguqulweni okukhulu kakhulu nasekunciphiseni noma ngisho nasekungasebenzisekeni.
Kuyathakazelisa ukuthi i- nucleotide analogue Remdesivir yaziwa ukuthi ivimbela ukuphindiswa kwe- CoV ngokuvimbela lokhu kuvinjelwa kwe- exoribonuclease kanye ne- RNA- polymerase ehlobene ne- RNA.
I-Remdesivir ingenye yezithunywa ezithembisayo kakhulu zokulwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ezizohlolwa ezivivinyweni zemitholampilo.
Noma kunjalo, izinga lokuguquka kwama-COV liphakeme ngokuphindwe ngesigidi kunelabanikazi bawo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga lokuguquka ngokuvamile liphakeme lapho ama-COV engavumelani kahle nomgcini.
Uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV enesilinganiso esiphakeme sokuguquka, izinga lokuguquka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusobala liphansi, okusikisela izinga eliphakeme lokuzivumelanisa nabantu.
Cishe, isivele ilungiswe komunye umkhaya oseduze nabantu.
Ngaphezu kwe-SARS-CoV-2, lokhu kusebenza nase-MERS-CoV, evumelana kahle namakamela angama-dromedary.
Ngokwesayensi, akunakwenzeka ukuthi ukuzulazula kwezakhi zofuzo kuzokwenza imithi yokugoma kanye nemithi elwa namagciwane e-SARS-CoV-2 ingasebenzi ngokushesha.
Okwesibili, i-RNA enkulu ye-CoVs inobungako obengeziwe ekuguqulweni kwe-genome ukuze ibe nezinguquko nokuhlanganiswa kabusha, ngaleyo ndlela kukhulise amathuba okuvela ndawonye kwezinhlobo, okuyinto ezuzisayo ekubukeni kwama-CoV amasha lapho izimo zifaneleka.
Lokhu kusekelwa yizinhlaka eziningi ezivulekile zokufunda kanye nemisebenzi yamaprotheni efakwe ngekhodi ngasekupheleni kwe-3′ kwe-genome.
Okwesithathu, ama-COV ashintsha izifanekiso ngokungahleliwe futhi kaningi ngesikhathi sokuphindaphinda i-RNA ngokusebenzisa indlela eyingqayizivele yokukhetha ukukopisha.
Kumgcini wezinsiza ezisebenza njengesitsha sokuxuba, ukushintshaniswa kwezintambo kwenzeka kaningi ngesikhathi sokubhalwa kwe-RNA ye-COV.
Ama-RNA ahlobene kakhulu nobude obuphelele kanye nama-RNA angase ahlanganiswe kabusha ukuze akhiqize ama-COV amasha.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bokubambisana kabusha kwemvelo butholakale kokubili ku-HCoV-HKU1 naku-HCoV-OC43, kanye nama-CoV ezilwane njenge-bat SL-CoV ne-batCoV-HKU9.
Ukuxhumana kwegciwane nomgcini wezinambuzane maqondana nokudluliselwa
Ngaphandle kwezinto ezintathu ezibangelwa amagciwane ezichazwe ngenhla, ukusebenzisana kwegciwane ne-host receptor kungenye into ebalulekile ethinta ukudluliselwa kwezinhlobo.
Lapha, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-SARS-CoV kuthathwa njengesibonelo esijwayelekile, esibonisa nobufakazi bokukhethwa okuhle ngesikhathi sezenzakalo zokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlaziyweni okuqhathanisiwe phakathi kwe-SARS-CoVs yabantu kanye ne-civet, kucatshangwa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV iyazivumelanisa ngokushesha kumagumbi ahlukene, ikakhulukazi ngokuvela kwe-RBD ye-S protein.
Ngokuvamile, i- RBD eprotheni le- S le- CoV ixhumana ne- cellular receptor futhi ikhethwa ngokuqinile impendulo ye- host antibody.
Ku-SARS-CoV, i-RBD ise-318th kuya ku-510th amino acid ku-S1 fragment, ebopha ku-ACE2 yomuntu kanye nama-coreceptors ayo okufaka igciwane.
I-RBD ye-SARS-CoV iyakwazi ukubona ama-ACE2 receptors ezilwane ezahlukahlukene, kufaka phakathi ibhubezi, i-civet, igundane kanye nenja ye-raccoon, okuvumela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Empeleni, kwakubonwa ukuthi kunezinsalela eziyisithupha kuphela zama-amino acid ezahlukile kuma-virus isolate womuntu nawomphakathi ku-RBD futhi ezine zazo zitholakala kumugqa wokubopha we-receptor wokusebenzisana ne-ACE2.
ICivet SARS-CoV ine-K479N ne-S487T izinguquko ku-RBD yayo, okungase kukhulise ukuhlobana kokusebenzisana kwamaprotheni we-spike ne-human ACE2 receptor.
Ngamanye amazwi, lezi zinhlobo ezimbili zokubhinca ama-amino acid zingase zibe ezibalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni namagciwane nabantu.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yabelana ngomamukeli ofanayo wamangqamuzana ne-SARS-CoV.
Umehluko ongama-30% phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV eqenjini le-S1 le-protein S usho ukuthi ukuhlobana okuhlangene kwe-S protein yayo ne-ACE2 yomuntu kungenzeka ukuthi kuguqukile.
Ngempela, ucwaningo lwe-crio-EM lukhombisa ukuthi lokhu kubopha kuhlobene ngokuphindwe izikhathi eziyi-10 kuya kwezi-20 kunalokho phakathi kwe-ACE2 yomuntu ne-SARS-CoV S protein.
Kuzoba nentshisekelo futhi ukunquma ukuthi ngabe kukhona yini okunye okufunekayo ukuze kudluliselwe i-SARS-CoV-2.
Okuhlaba umxhwele ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 nayo ibopha ku-ACE2 kodwa inengxenye ehlukile ye-S.
Kunamanye ama-HCoV receptors amaningi, njenge-aminopeptidase N ye-HCoV-229E, ne-9-O-acetylated sialic acid ye-HCoV-OC43.
Bangase futhi baba necala lokuzivumelanisa ngokuphumelelayo nalezi zifo ezibangelwa ama-COV kubantu ngemva kokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo eziphakathi kwezilwane ezibanjwe yizilwane.
Ngaphezu kwama-receptor eselula, umphumela wokudluliselwa kwe-HCoVs phakathi kwezinhlobo ulawulwa nezinye izici zokuncika kanye nokunciphisa.
Ukuhluka kwalezi zinhlayiya zamaprotheni phakathi kwabantu kanye namagciwane e-HCoVs asemthonjeni wemvelo njengamabhungane, amakamela angama-dromedary nezidudla kungase kube yisithiyo sokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo.
Ama-HCoVs kufanele athathe izici zokuncika kumgcini futhi agumbuqele izici zokunciphisa umgcini ukuze kudluliselwe ngempumelelo phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Kulokhu, kusadingeka ukucacisa nokukhombisa izakhi ezibangela ama-molecule kule ndawo ebalulekile yokuxhumana kwegciwane nomninikhaya.
Ukuhlolwa okungabandlululi kwe-genome-wide kokuncika kwe-host kanye nezakhi zokuvimbela i-SARS-CoV-2 kusetshenziswa ubuchwepheshe besimanje be-CRISPR kungaba nemiphumela emihle.
Ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha: kubuyela endaweni engenacala
Ukuhlukahluka kwama-CoV embathe kunikeza amathuba amaningi okuvela kwama-HCoV amasha.
Ngale ndlela, ama-Covs ombathe asebenza njengeziqu ze-HCoVs.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuguquka okusheshayo nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwezakhi zofuzo nakho kuholela ekuziphendukeleni kwe-HCoV futhi kusebenza njengezinyathelo ezimbili ezibalulekile kule nqubo.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukuthola noma ukulahlekelwa kwezakhi zofuzo ezintsha ezifaka amaprotheni kunamandla okuguqula kakhulu ama-phenotypes omkhuhlane we-virus.
Phakathi kwamaprotheni okuhambisana ne-SARS-CoV, i-ORF8 ibilokhu ibonwa njengokubalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni nabantu, njengoba amagciwane ombathe ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV ahlukaniswa kodwa atholakala ukuthi abhekisela kumaprotheni ahlukene e-ORF8.
Isici sokususwa kwe-nucleotide engama-29 se-SARS-CoVs sitholakale ezinhlotsheni ezihlukaniswe ekuqaleni kobhadane lomuntu.
Lokhu kuhlukana kwe-ORF8 kuhlukanisa i-ORF8a ne-ORF8b futhi kucatshangwa ukuthi kuyisinambuzane esivumelanayo esikhuthaza ukushintshaniswa kwabamukeli.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-SARS-CoV inomlando wokubumbana kabusha okungenzeka nemindeni yama-alpha- kanye nama-gamma-CoVs, lapho kutholakala khona inqwaba yezifunda ezincane ezihlanganisiwe ku-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Izindawo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha zabuye zahlolwa ku-nsp9, iningi le-nsp10, nasezingxenyeni ze-nsp14.
Ngokufanayo, kuye kwaboniswa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-MERS-CoV lwabhekana nemicimbi yokuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwezinhlanga ezahlukene, okwenzeka kumakamela angama-dromedary eSaudi Arabia.
Ngaphandle kwe-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, kuye kwabonwa nemicimbi yokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwamanye ama-HCoVs, lapho ama-HCoVs ehlanganiswa kabusha namanye ama-Covs ezilwane kumagciwane awo angekho ezakhiweni.
Kufanele futhi kuxwayiswe ukuthi ukukhethwa okufakelwayo kungasiza ekushintsheni okungahloselwe kwezakhi zofuzo ze-virus, okungenzeka kakhulu ukuthi kubangelwa ukukhulula amagciwane ekucindezelweni kokukhetha, njengokusetshenziswa kohlelo lokugwema ukungenwa izifo.
Isibonelo sale miphumela ukulahlekelwa kwe-ORF4 yobude obuphelele ku-HCoV-229E prototype strain, ngenxa yokuqedwa kwama-nucleotide amabili.
Ngenkathi i-ORF4 engalinyazwa ingabonwa kumagciwane ombhubhane nakwamakamela ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ibonisa ukufakwa okukodwa kwe-nucleotide, okuholela ekushintsheni kwesakhelo.
Okokugcina, ukuvela kwama-HCoVs amasha kuhlobene nokucindezela kokukhetha emagcekeni awo.
Izimpawu ezingabonakalisi noma ezincane kuphela zatholakala lapho izimpungushe zithe zahlushwa ama-COV, okubonisa ukuvumelanisa phakathi kwama-COV nezimpungushe.
Kwabonakala ukuthi izimpungushe zilungele kahle ama-COV ngokomzimba nangokwenyama.
Ngokwesibonelo, amaphutha ekusebenziseni impendulo evikela ukuvuvukala emagundane anciphisa ngokuphumelelayo isifo esibangelwa ama-COV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, umsebenzi wamangqamuzana ombulali wemvelo emagundane uvinjelwe ngenxa yokulawula okuphezulu kwe-inhibitory killer cell receptor NKG2/CD94 kanye nezinga eliphansi lokuveza izinhlayiya ezinkulu ze-histocompatibility complex class I.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga eliphakeme lezinhlobo ze-oxygen ezisebenza kahle (i-ROS) ezenziwa umsebenzi ophakeme we-metabolic wezinambuzane zingaqeda ukuphindaphinda kwe-COV futhi zithinte ukufundwa okuphambene ne-exoribonuclease, ngaleyo ndlela zinikeze ingcindezi yokukhetha ekwakheni izinhlobo zegciwane ezibangela izifo kakhulu lapho zingeniswa kumgcini omusha.
Izinhlobo eziningi ze-COV ezibangela izifo nazo zingavela ngokuhlanganiswa kabusha, okuholela ekutholeni amaprotheni amasha noma izici zamaprotheni ukuze zivumelane nezimo zomgcini.
Ngakho-ke, akuyona into eyenzeka ngengozi ukuthi ama-HCoV amathathu amasha avele eminyakeni engamashumi amabili edlule.
Ama-COV awenzi lutho noma abangela izimpawu ezincane kumagumbi awo okuhlala njengamabhungane namakamela.
Zenza izinqubo zokuphindaphinda ngendlela enamandla ngaphandle kokwenza ukuba amasosha omzimba amelane nezimo ezibucayi.
Lapha kukhona izimfihlo zokuthi kungani kuthathwa abathwali abangenayo imizwa nokuthi yini ebangela izifo ezinzima kubantu.
Izimpawu ezinzima zibangelwa ukuphazamiseka okukhulu kwempendulo yomzimba kanye nesiphepho se- cytokine lapho impendulo yomzimba yomzimba inamandla kakhulu, ukulimala kwempunga kuba nzima kakhulu.
Ngokuphambene, ezithwaleni ezingenakubonakaliswa, impendulo yomzimba ye-immune iye yahlukaniswa nokwenziwa kwe-COV.
Isitayela esifanayo sokususa ukuxhumana kwempendulo yomzimba singaba nemiphumela ezuzisayo ekwelapheni kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuphendula kwe-interferon kunamandla kakhulu emagundane.
Ngakho-ke, ukuphathwa kwe-interferon yohlobo I okungenani esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu kufanele kube yinzuzo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuvuselelwa kwe- NLRP3 inflammasome kumagundane akulungile.
Ngalesi sizathu, ukuvimbela i-NLRP3 inflammasome nge-MCC950 kungase kube wusizo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kulandela isihloko esivamile lapho i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV zavela khona.
Ngenkathi kutholakale ukuthi i-bat beta-CoV yabelana ngama-95% e-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV, kukhona futhi i-bat-CoV eyabelana ngama-96% e-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngenkathi izilwane ezifuywayo nezinye izilwane ezimakethe zitholakale ukuthi ziqukethe amagciwane afana ne-SARS-CoV, azitholakalanga izindlu eziphakathi ezisheshayo ze-SARS-CoV-2.
Kutholakale ama-pangolin beta-CoVs ahambelana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2, okukhombisa ukuthi ama-pangolin angase abe ngomunye wabathengi abaphakathi noma ama-pangolin beta-CoVs angasiza izingcezu zofuzo kunguqulo yokugcina ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kunemibuzo, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yenziwe umuntu ngamabomu noma ngephutha.
Ama-COV abuyele ekukhanyeni ngenxa yokuqubuka kwakamuva kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Ucwaningo lwe-COV emagundane nakwezinye izilwane lushintshe kakhulu umbono wethu ngokubaluleka kwemvelaphi ye-zoonotic kanye nezitshalo zezilwane ze-HCoVs ekudlulisweni kwabantu.
Ubufakazi obubanzi bukhombisile ukuthi i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zinomsuka wezinambuzane futhi zidluliselwa kubantu ngokusebenzisa ababungazi abaphakathi.
Njengoba ukutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV kuvela ekuxhumaneni kwabantu nezilwane ezimakethe, ukuvala izimakethe ezimanzi nokubulala izilwane ezifuywayo kuzobe sekuphelile ngempumelelo ubhadane lwe-SARS.
Ngesizathu esifanayo, ama-pangolin kufanele asuswe ezimakethe ezimanzi ukuvimbela ukudluliselwa kwe-zoonotic, ngenxa yokuthola izizukulwane eziningi zama-pangolin beta-CoVs ahlobene eduze ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Kodwa-ke, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwa kanjani kubantu ngama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusamele kucaciswe ekucwaningweni kwesikhathi esizayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV ibilokhu ikhona kumakamela angama-dromedary isikhathi eside.
Lezi zingamela zisebenza njengethuluzi elibalulekile lokuhamba futhi ziwumthombo oyinhloko wenyama, ubisi, isikhumba nemikhiqizo yeboya kubantu bendawo.
Zisakazeka kabanzi eMpumalanga Ephakathi nase-Afrika.
Ngakho-ke akunakwenzeka ukuhlabela wonke amakamela ukuze kulawulwe i-MERS, njengoba kwakwenziwe ezimakethe zezilwane zasendle eChina ukuvimbela ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuze kuvinjelwe ukuqubuka okuphindaphindiwe kwe-MERS, kufanele kuthathwe indlela ebanzi yokuthuthukisa izidakamizwa ezisebenzayo zokulwa ne-MERS-CoV zamakamela, ngokuhlanganiswa nezinye izindlela zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Njengoba singakwazi ukuwaqeda la magciwane, kungavela izinhlobo ezintsha zofuzo ezibangela ukuqubuka.
Izinhlobo ezihlukahlukene ze-COV ezibangelwa yizilwane ziyasakazeka emvelweni.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-COV ezimpukane anezinhlobo eziningi zezinambuzane ahlukahlukene.
Kunamathuba amaningi okuthi lezi zifo ezibangelwa ukulimala kwabantu ziguquke futhi ziphinde zihlanganiswe, okuholela ekubukeni kwezifo ezintsha ezizothinteka kakhulu futhi/noma ezibulalayo kubantu esikhathini esizayo.
Isiko lokudla izilwane zasendle kwezinye izindawo zaseChina kufanele liyekwe ukuze kuncishiswe ukuxhumana okungadingekile phakathi kwabantu nezilwane.
Ngenxa ye-SARS, i-MERS ne-COVID-19, kufanele kube khona uhlelo olungcono lokulungiselela nokuphendula.
Empeleni, amagciwane amaningi abelokhu ekhona emhlabeni isikhathi eside kakhulu.
Zihlale eziqongweni zazo zemvelo kuze kube yilapho kunethuba lokuchitheka.
Nakuba izintuthwane zinezici eziningi ezenza kube lula ukusakaza amagciwane, amathuba okuba abantu babe nokuxhumana nezintuthwane nezinye izinhlobo zezilwane zasendle angancishiswa uma abantu befundiswa ukuba bahlale kude nazo.
Ukuqapha okuqhubekayo kwezilwane ezincelisayo kuyadingeka ukuze siqonde kangcono imvelo ye-COVs kanye namagumbi ayo emvelo, okuyobonakala kuwusizo ekuvimbeleni ukudluliselwa kwezilwane kubantu nokuqubuka kwesikhathi esizayo.
Ukuze siphethe, indlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokuvimbela ukuhlaselwa kwabantu yi-zoonosis yabantu ukuhlala kude nezindawo zemvelo ezihlala izilwane eziphila ngaphansi kwamanzi.
Izingcezu eziningana ze-puzzle yemvelaphi ye-SARS-CoV-2 zisaphuthelwa.
Okokuqala, uma izintuthwane zidlulisela igciwane lokhokho be-SARS-CoV-2 kuma-pangolins, kuyoba nentshisekelo ukubona ukuthi ngaphansi kwaziphi izimo izintuthwane nama-pangolins angahlanganyela i-niche efanayo yezemvelo.
Okwesibili, uma izintuthwane zidlala indima eqondile ekudluliseleni kwabantu, kufanele kunqunywe ukuthi abantu bahlangana kanjani nezintuthwane.
Okwesithathu, uma kunesilwane sesithathu esisebenza njengesilwane esiphakathi ngempela, kufanele kucaciswe ukuthi sisebenzelana kanjani nezinhlobo ezahlukene kuhlanganise nabantu, izintethe nama-pangolin.
Ekugcineni, njengoba izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane zasekhaya zingaba nezinkinga ze-SARS-CoV-2, kufanele kwenziwe ukuqapha nokutheleleka kokuhlola.
Uma ngabe kungumshaya, i-pangolin noma esinye isilwane esincelisayo, kulindeleke ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 noma amagciwane ayo abuzali afana kakhulu azotholakala kumagumbi ayo emvelo ngokuzayo.
Ucwaningo oluqhubekayo kule ndawo luzokhanyisa indlela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-SARS-CoV-2 ezilwaneni, olunemithelela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni nasekulawuleni i-COVID-19 kubantu.
Kuyadingeka ukuvuselela izindlela zokuxilonga ze-COVID-19 isimo esolisayo kanye ne-isimo esiqinisekisiwe
NgoFebhuwari 6, 2020, iqembu lethu lakhipha isiqondiso esisheshayo sokuthola nokwelapha isifo se-coronavirus entsha (2019-nCoV) sika-2019, futhi lesi siqondiso sanikeza ulwazi lwethu futhi senza inkomba enhle yokulwa nalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Kodwa-ke, isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) siyisimo esibucayi, ulwazi lwethu luyanda kancane kancane ngokuya ngemiphumela yocwaningo eqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho komkhuba wezokwelapha; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilongwa nokwelashwa nawo ayavuselelwa njalo.
Kule ncwadi, siphendule ukuphawula okukodwa mayelana nesiqondiso sethu futhi sanikeza izinga lokutholwa kwamagciwane lamagciwane asolwayo kanye namacala aqinisekisiwe ngokusho kwezikhombisi zakamuva zokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kwe-COVID-19 (inguqulo yesikhombisa) ezikhishwe yiKomiti Yezempilo Kazwelonke ye-People's Republic of China.
NgoDisemba 2019, i-2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ibangele ukuqubuka, manje okubizwa ngokusemthethweni ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) futhi leli gciwane selibizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
NgoMashi 11, 2020, i-WHO yachaza i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Ukuze silwe nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2, iqembu lethu lithuthukise isiqondiso esisheshayo sokweluleka futhi sishicilelwe ku-inthanethi ku-Military Medical Research ngoFebhuwari 06, 2020.
Kusukela yanyatheliswa, iye yaheha abantu abaningi.
Qaphela ukuthi i-COVID-19 yisifo esisha, ulwazi lwethu nokwazi kwethu kuyanda kancane kancane ngokuya ngokutholakala kocwaningo olujwayelekile kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho komkhuba wezokwelapha; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilongwa nokwelashwa nawo ayavuselelwa njalo.
Isibonelo, iziqondiso zokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kwe-COVID-19 ezikhishwe yiKomiti Yezempilo Kazwelonke ye-People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), phakathi kuka-16 Januwari 2020 no-3 Mashi 2020, zikhiphe izichibiyelo eziyisikhombisa, ezinye izizinda ziguquke kakhulu.
Manje isiqondiso sethu sathola ukuphawula kukaZhou et al., baletha isiphakamiso esilula sokuphumelela ngokusekelwe kokuhlangenwe nakho kwabo kwezokwelapha.
Umsebenzi wabo ungeze ubufakazi obusha emhlahlandlela wethu futhi futhi wenza inkomba ebalulekile yalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Siyayisekela umsebenzi wabo obalulekile futhi siyabonga.
Kodwa-ke, umsebenzi wabo udinga nokuvuselelwa ngokusho kwezikhombisi zakamuva zokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kwe-COVID-19 (i-Trial version yesikhombisa) kanye nezifundo zakamuva.
Ngokwedivayisi yesikhombisa (3 Mashi 2020), ukuqinisekisa icala elicatshangwayo kudinga ukuhlanganisa noma iyiphi into eyodwa yezici zomlando wezifo nezimpawu ezimbili zemibono yezokwelapha ukwenza ukuhlaziywa okuphelele, noma kudinga ukuhlangabezana nezinto ezintathu zemibono yezokwelapha uma kungekho mlando ocacile wezifo:
Umlando wezifo: (1) umlando wokuhamba noma wokuhlala edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma kweminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona amacala e-COVID-19 ezinsukwini eziyi-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (2) umlando wokuxhumana namacala atheleleka e-SARS-CoV-2 (ngokuhlolwa kwe-nucleic acid okuhle); (3) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli ezinomkhuhlane noma izimpawu zokuphefumula ezivela edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona i-COVID-19 ezinsukwini eziyi-14 ezedlule ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (4) umlando wokuxhumana neqembu lamacala aqinisekisiwe (≥ 2 amacala anomkhuhlane kanye/noma izimpawu zokuphefumula azenzeka kungakapheli amasonto ama-2 ezindaweni ezincane, njengekhaya, ehhovisi, ekilasini lesikole, njll.).
Ukubonakala kwemitholampilo: (1) umkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula; (2) ngezimpawu zokuqopha ukutheleleka kwe-COVID-19; (3) inani eliphelele lamangqamuzana amhlophe egazi abonisa ukuthi inani lama-lymphocyte livamile, liyancipha noma linciphe esigabeni sokuqala.
Ukuxilongwa kwecala eliqinisekisiwe kufanele kususelwe ekutheni kunesizathu esisodwa sobufakazi obutheleleka noma obutheleleka ngokulandelayo: (1) ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR ngesikhathi sangempela okubonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inemiphumela emihle; (2) ukulandelana kwe-genome yonke ye-virus ebonisa ukufana okuphezulu nama-coronavirus amasha aziwayo; (3) ukuhlolwa kwe-serum okubonisa ukuthi i- IgM antibody kanye ne- IgG antibody ye-SARS-CoV-2 iyinhle; noma ukushintsha kwe- IgG antibody ye-SARS-CoV-2 kusuka kokungemuhle kuya kokungemuhle, noma ukwanda kwe- titer ≥4 izikhathi esigabeni sokululama ngaphezu kwalokho esigabeni esibucayi.
Singabona ukuthi ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR yesikhathi sangempela kwe-nucleic acid emigwaqweni yokuphefumula noma amasampula egazi kwengezwe ohlwini lwesibili (18 Januwari 2020) nolwesithathu (22 Januwari 2020).
Ukuthola i-pathogenic of blood sample kwanezelwa kumagazini wesine (27 January 2020) nowesihlanu (8 February 2020); bese kuthi ubufakazi be-serological bengezwe kumagazini wesikhombisa.
Lezi zinguquko ezisekelwe kubacwaningi zaqhubeka nomsebenzi wokufuna i-kit enhle yokuthola i-nucleic acid yokutholwa kwe-acid yokutholwa okusheshayo, kanye namasampula avela ezindleleni zokuphefumula kuhlanganise nokutholwa kwegazi, okwandisa ukutholakala kwezibonelo ezahlukene, futhi kwaxhasa ukuletha umphumela omuhle we-antibody ethile kumakhredithi aqinisekisiwe.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, kunobufakazi obandayo obusikhumbuza ukuba siqaphele iziguli ezingavamile ezibonisa izimpawu nezingabonisi izimpawu.
Ngakho-ke, ishadi lokuhamba kukaZhou et al. kufanele libuyekezwe, njengoba babeka umuntu ongenazo izimpawu zokwelashwa njenge-  low risk.
Uhlelo lokulinganisa kufanele luqinisekiswe naseminye imikhuba nezifundo zemitholampilo.
Ukuze siphethe, siyethemba ukuthi kuyoba nobufakazi obuqondile obengeziwe futhi sicele abafundi ukuba banikeze imibono yabo.
Ukuze kutholakale ukuthi kunabantu abasolwayo noma abaqinisekisiwe, siphakamisa ukuba balandele futhi balandele iziqondiso zakamuva zamazwe abo.
Ithimba lethu lizobuyekeza futhi umhlahlandlela wethu ngesikhathi esifanele ukuze linikeze usizo.
IBangladesh ibika izisulu ezintsha ezinhlanu ezifa ngenxa ye-COVID-19, okuyisilinganiso esiphakeme kakhulu nsuku zonke
Izolo, iBangladesh iqinisekise izisulu ezintsha ezinhlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ngalolo suku.
Lesi yisibalo esiphakeme kunazo zonke sabantu abafa ngosuku ngenxa yaleli gciwane.
Kusukela izolo, i-Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) yaseBangladesh ibike ukuthi inani lamacala atholwe atholakala ukuthi afaka iziguli ezisebenzayo eziyi-114 kanye neziguli ezingama-33 eziye zatholakele ezihlala ekhaya.
Kuye kwafa abangu-17.
Emhlanganweni wezindaba online, umqondisi we-IEDCR, uDkt Meerjady Sabrina Flora, uthe abafile babehlanganisa abesilisa abane nowesifazane oyedwa.
NgokukaDkt Meerjady, iziguli ezimbili zazineminyaka engaphezu kwengu-60, ezimbili zaphakathi kuka-51 no-60, kanti enye yayineminyaka engu-41-50 ubudala.
Uphinde wathi ababili babahlukunyezwa baseDhaka.
Inhlangano Yezwe Yezempilo (i-WHO) yamemezela i-COVID-19 njengobhadane ngoMashi 11.
Isikhulu sesibhedlela sathela i-Anatolu Agency, okuyinkundla yezindaba yendawo, ukuthi omunye walabo abashonile kwakunguJalal Saifur Rahman, umqondisi weBengali Anti-Corruption Commission, owayekhathalelwa esibhedlela saseKuwait Maitree.
NgoMgqibelo, esitatimendeni se-video esiku-inthanethi, uNgqongqoshe Wezokuhamba Ngezindlela kanye Nezibhuloho waseBangladesh u-Obaidul Quader uthe izitimela zomphakathi zizovalwa isikhathi eside kunalokho okwakuhlelwe ekuqaleni, kuze kube ngoMgqibelo ozayo.
Lokhu kuvalwa kwezithuthi zomphakathi ekuqaleni kwaqala ngoMashi 26 futhi kwakuhlelwe ukuba kuphele ngoMgqibelo, ngo-April 4.
Ukuhamba kwezimpahla eziyisisekelo - ezokwelapha, uphethiloli nokudla - kwakusavunyelwe.
Izigameko zokuqala zokutheleleka nge-COVID-19 eBangladesh zaqoshwa ngoMashi 8, kubantu ababili ababuya e-Italy kanye nomfazi womunye wabo.
Ngo-March 19, laba abathathu base sebephulukisiwe.
I-SARS-CoV-2 idlula izigidi eziyishumi zokutheleleka emhlabeni jikelele
NgoLwesine, inani eliphelele lamacala e-SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus izifo lidlule isigidi emhlabeni wonke, idatha yaseJohn Hopkins University yabonisa.
