Lesi sigameko senzeke ngosuku olufanayo lapho iMalawi iqinisekisa khona ukuthi ithole izifo zokuqala ze-coronavirus kanti neZambia ithole ukufa kwayo kokuqala okuhlobene ne-coronavirus.
