Izitolo e-Australia zinciphisa imikhawulo ephepheni lokugezela ngokuthengiselana
NgoSonto noMgqibelo kusihlwa, izitolo zase-Australia iWoolworths neColes zehlise imikhawulo yazo yokuthenga iphepha lokugezela yaba ngamaphakethe amabili kanye nelilodwa ngokuthengiselana kuzo zonke izitolo ezingeni likazwelonke, ngokulandelana.
I-ALDI yafaka umkhawulo wephakethe elilodwa, ngoMsombuluko.
Lezi zingqinamba zabhalwa njengemiyalezo emabhange, nasemakhasini e-Facebook eziteshi.
Kubikwa ukuthi abathengi babethenga ngenxa yokwesaba i-COVID-19 uma abantu bedinga ukuzihlukanisa.
NgoLwesithathu, iWoolworths yanciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha elisetshenziselwa ukulethwa ekhaya libe yiphakethe elilodwa nge-oda ngalinye.
Lezi zinguquko zilandela ukuvinjelwa kwangaphambilini kwepakethe ezine ngokuthengiselana okwaqalwa yiWoolworths neColes ngoMashi 4 no-5 ngokulandelana.
"UCole, ekukhululweni kwayo kwabezindaba ngoMashi 8, wabika ukuthi ngesinqumo samaphakethe amane, ""izitolo eziningi zisathengisa ngaphakathi kwehora lokulethwa"", futhi wabiza lesi sidingo ngokuthi "esingenakuqhathaniswa"", kanti i-ALDI, kokuthunyelwe kwe-Facebook ngoLwesibili, yakusho ukuthi "akulindwanga".
"Ukuthengiswa kwenyuka kakhulu ngesonto eledlule, ngokusho kwesikhulumi seWoolworths".
Isitolo sikaCostco eCanberra naso sakhawulela inani elivunyelwe ukuba libe ngamaphakethe amabili ngesonto eledlule.
Ukuze kuncishiswe ukushoda, uColes wayala amaphakheji amakhulu kubahlinzeki futhi kwandisa imvamisa yokulethwa, uWoolworths wayala isitokwe esingeziwe, kanti i-ALDI yenza izitoko ze-Special Wednesday ezazilindelwe zitholakale ekuseni.
URussell Zimmerman, umqondisi ophethe we-Australian Retailers Association, wathi abathengisi bazama ukukhulisa amasheya, kodwa imikhawulo yomkhandlu wendawo ngesikhathi sokulethwa kwamaloli yenza kube nzima.
Ulindele ukukhuphuka kwezindleko zokukhiqiza, njengoba abahlinzeki bezama ukuhlangabezana nesidingo, futhi kuncane okhethekile.
NgoLwesibili, i-ALDI yamemezela ukuthi ngemva kokukhululwa kwamasheya kusenesikhathi, ezinye izitolo azikwazi ukuqhuba umcimbi okhethekile wangoLwesithathu.
Embikweni weNews.com.au, uDkt Gary Mortimer, onguchwepheshe wezokuthengisa eQueensland University of Technology, wathi izitolo zigcwalisa isitokwe njalo ebusuku.
