UColes noWoolworths banombono wokuthi uma bekunokuningi eshalofini, uma imikhiqizo efana namaphepha okugeza kanye ne-sanitizer [ingathengwa] futhi ikhona ngobuningi, cishe ubunganciphisa ukwethuka, kusho uRussell Zimmerman nge-ABC News.
Umkhiqizi wephepha langasese elibuyekeziwe i-Who Gives a Crap uthe ngoLwesithathu odlule babephelelwe isitokwe.
