I-Domain.com, indawo yezezakhiwo, ibike ukuthi abanye abathengisi bezindlu babenikeza iphepha lokugezela lamahhala kumthengisi wokuqala kuma-auction eMelbourne, lapho kwakubanjwa ama-auction ambalwa ngenxa yokuthi abathengi babe nesikhathi sokuphumula ngempelasonto ende yoSuku Lwezabasebenzi.
Uhlelo lwangoLwesine lwe-NT News, iphephandaba lanyatheliswa nsuku zonke eDarwin, lwafaka isihloko samakhasi angu-8 esasimelwe sinqunywe futhi sisetshenziswe njengephepha langasese.
Izitolo ekuqaleni zazinqikaza ukubeka imikhawulo, ngokusho kombiko we-ABC Australia ngoMashi 3 lapho zathi azinayo inhloso yokufaka imikhawulo ekuthengeni.
URussell Zimmerman wanezela ukuthi neminye imikhiqizo iyadingeka kakhulu, kuhlanganise nemaski, izinto zokuhlanza amanzi, imikhiqizo eyomisiwe, ukugeza izandla nomgubo.
