I-World Health Organization imemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esiwumqedazwe
NgoLwesithathu, i-World Health Organization (WHO) yamemezela ukuqubuka okuqhubekayo kwe-COVID-19  isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  njengobhadane.
"Nakuba igama elithi ""ubhadane"" libhekisela kuphela ekutheni isifo sesisakazeke kangakanani, hhayi ukuthi amacala athile ayingozi kangakanani, i-WHO yaqaphela isidingo sokushayela ohulumeni ukuba bathathe isinyathelo:"
Wonke amazwe angashintsha inkambo yalolu bhubhane.
Uma amazwe ethola, ehlola, elapha, ehlukanisa, elandela futhi ehlanganisa abantu bawo ukuze baphendule, kusho uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
Sikhathazeke kakhulu ngamazinga ashaqisayo okuhlakazeka nobunzima kanye namazinga ashaqisayo okungasebenzi.
"Ngokusho kukaDkt Tom Frieden, owayengumqondisi weZikhungo Zokulawulwa Nokuvikelwa Kwezifo zase-United States, lolu bhubhane "aluzange lube khona ngaphambili".
"Wathi, ezitatimendeni ezashicilelwa yi-CNN ngoFebhuwari, ""ngaphandle komkhuhlane, akukho okunye ukugula komoya okuye kwalandelwa kusukela ekuqhamukeni kuya ekusakazekeni okuqhubekayo emhlabeni wonke". ""
"UGhebreyesus uveze umbono ofanayo, ethi ""asikaze sibone ubhadane olubangelwa i-coronavirus ngaphambili".""
Waqhubeka, ""futhi asikaze sibone ubhadane olungalawulwa ngasikhathi sinye".""
Isimo esisha njengobhadane silandela isinqumo se-WHO ngoJanuwari sokumemezela ukuqubuka njengesifo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi esikhathaza umhlaba wonke.
"Umqondisi we-United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease, uDkt Anthony Fauci, uthe mayelana nokuqubuka, ""umgqa owodwa, kuzoba kubi kakhulu. """
Kusukela ngoLwesine, i-Associated Press ibike ukuthi kunamacala okungenani ayi-126 000 e-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke, okuholele ekufeni okungaphezu kuka-4 600.
Ubhadane lwe-coronavirus 201920 luwumqedazwe oqhubekayo wesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19), obangelwa yi-coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ye-acute respiratory syndrome.
Ukuqubuka kwahlolwa eWuhan, eChina, ngoDisemba 2019, kwabhengezwa njengesiFundazwe sezempilo yomphakathi esinomthelela omkhulu emhlabeni wonke ngoJanuwari 30, 2020, kwabhekwa njengobhadane ngoMashi 11, 2020.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 10, 2020, kubikwe ukuthi kunabantu abangaba yizigidi eziyi-1.61 abane-COVID-19 emazweni nezindawo ezingama-210 okuholele ekufeni kwabantu abangaba ngu-97,000.
Cishe abantu abangu-364 000 sebephulukisiwe.
Izinga lokufa kwabantu lilinganiswa ne-4% eChina, kuyilapho emhlabeni wonke livela ku-13.04% e-Algeria kuya ku-0.08% eNew Zealand.
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa umkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela nokuphefumula okusheshayo.
Izinkinga zingahlanganisa ukuvuvukala kwamakhala kanye nesifo sokuphefumula esibucayi.
Isikhathi esivela ekuvezeni kuze kuqale izimpawu ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu, kodwa singaba yizinsuku ezimbili kuya kwezingu-14.
Akukho mgomo noma ukwelashwa okuqondile kwe- antiviral okwaziwayo.
Ukwelashwa okuyinhloko kuwukwelashwa okubonisa izimpawu nokwesekela.Izinyathelo zokuvimbela ezinconywayo zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukumboza umlomo lapho ukhwehlela, ukugcina ibanga nabanye abantu, nokuqapha nokuzihlukanisa kubantu abasola ukuthi bayangenwa yilesi sifo.
Iziphathimandla emhlabeni wonke ziye zaphendula ngokumisa imikhawulo yokuhamba, ukuhlukaniswa kwabantu, ukuvala amakhaya, ukulawula izingozi emsebenzini nokuvala izikhungo.
Lolu bhubhane luholele ekuphazamisekeni okukhulu kwezenhlalo nezomnotho emhlabeni wonke, ukubambezeleka noma ukukhanselwa kwemicimbi yezemidlalo, yenkolo, yezepolitiki neyesiko, kanye nokushoda okubanzi kwezimpahla okwanda ngenxa yokuthenga kokwethuka.
Izikole namanyuvesi ziye zavalwa ezweni lonke noma endaweni emazweni angu-193, kuthinta cishe amaphesenti angu-99.4 abantu abafunda emhlabeni.
Ukwaziswa okungalungile mayelana naleli gciwane kuye kwasakazeka ku-intanethi, futhi kuye kwaba nezigameko zokugwema abantu bamazwe angaphandle nokucwaswa kwabantu baseChina, abanye abantu abavela naseMpumalanga naseNingizimu-mpumalanga ye-Asia, nabanye abavela ezindaweni ezinabantu abaningi abanegciwane.
Ngenxa yokunciphisa ukuhamba nokuvalwa kwezimboni ezindindindayo, kube nokwehla kokungcola komoya nokukhishwa kwekhabhoni.
Iziphathimandla zezempilo eWuhan, eChina (inhloko-dolobha yesifundazwe saseHubei) zabika ngeqembu lamacala omfutho omzimba ongabangeli lutho ngoDisemba 31, 2019, futhi kwaqalwa uphenyo ekuqaleni kukaJanuwari 2020.
Izigameko eziningi zazinokuxhumana neHuanan Seafood Wholesale Market ngakho-ke kucatshangwa ukuthi leli gciwane livela emithonjeni yezilwane.
Igciwane elibangele ukuqubuka kwalesi sifo laziwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, igciwane elisanda kutholakala elihlobene kakhulu nama-coronavirus ezimpukane, ama-pangolin coronaviruses, ne-SARS-CoV. Umuntu wokuqala owaziwayo onezimpawu kamuva watholakala ukuthi wagula ngoDisemba 1, 2019, futhi lowo muntu wayengenalo ukuxhumana okubonakalayo neqembu lezimakethe ezimanzi kamuva.
Kulolu cluster lokuqala lwezinkinga olubikwe ngoDisemba 2019, izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zatholakala ukuthi zihlobene nemakethe.
NgoMashi 13, 2020, umbiko ongaqinisekisiwe weSouth China Morning Post waveza ukuthi icala elivela emuva ngoNovemba 17, 2019, kumuntu oneminyaka engama-55 ubudala ovela esifundazweni saseHubei, kungenzeka ukuthi lalingeyokuqala. NgoFebhuwari 26, 2020, i-WHO yabika ukuthi, njengoba amacala amasha abikwa ukuthi ancipha eChina kepha akhuphuka ngokuzumayo e-Italy, e-Iran naseNingizimu Korea, inani lamacala amasha ngaphandle kweChina lidlule inani lamacala amasha ngaphakathi kweChina okokuqala ngqa.
Kungenzeka ukuthi kunezimo ezingabikelwa kahle, ikakhulukazi kulabo abanezimpawu ezincane.
NgoFebhuwari 26, kwakubikezelwe amacala ambalwa kakhulu phakathi kwentsha, kanti lawo angu-19 nangaphansi kwakungu-2,4% wamacala emhlabeni wonke. Umeluleki omkhulu wezesayensi wase-United Kingdom, uPatrick Vallance, walinganisela ukuthi abantu abangama-60% baseBrithani kwakuzodingeka bagule ngaphambi kokuba kutholakale ukungasebenzi kahle kwemihlambi.
Amacala abhekisela enanini labantu abahlolwe nge-COVID-19, futhi okuhlolwa kwabo kuqinisekiswe ukuthi kunemiphumela emihle ngokwemigomo esemthethweni.
Kusukela ngo-March 23, alikho izwe elalihlolwe ngaphezu kuka-3% wabantu balo, futhi amazwe amaningi aye enza izinqubomgomo ezisemthethweni zokungahlolwa kulabo abanezimpawu ezilula kuphela, njenge-Italy, iNetherlands, iSpain neSwitzerland.
Ucwaningo olwanyatheliswa ngoMashi 16 luthole ukuthi eChina, kuze kube nguJanuwari 23, kulinganiselwa ukuthi ama-86% ezigciwane le-COVID-19 ayengakabonakali, nokuthi lezi zigciwane ezingekho emthethweni zaziyimbangela yokutheleleka kwama-79% amacala abhalwe phansi.
Ukuhlaziywa kwezibalo okwenziwa ngoMashi 30 kwabonisa ukuthi inani lokutheleleka e-Italy lalingaphezu kakhulu lelo elalibhalwe.
Isilinganiso sokuqala senombolo yokuzala eyisisekelo (R0) ye-COVID-19 sasingu-1.4 kuya ku-2.4.
Ucwaningo olwenziwe i-US Center for Disease Control and Prevention luphethe ngokuthi kungaba ngu-5.7.
Iningi labantu abane-COVID-19 liyaphila.
Kulabo abangenayo, isikhathi esivela ekubonakalisweni kwezimpawu kuze kube sekufeni siphakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-6 nezingu-41, kanti esivame kakhulu izinsuku ezingu-14.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 10, 2020, cishe abantu abangu-97,000 base befile ngenxa ye-COVID-19.
EChina, ngoFebhuwari 5, cishe ama-80% ezishonile ayengabantu abangaphezu kweminyaka engama-60, kanti ama-75% ayenesifo senhliziyo nesifo sikashukela. Izibalo ezisemthethweni zokufa ngenxa yobhadane lwe-COVID-19 ngokuvamile zibhekisela kubantu abafile abahlolwe be-COVID ngokwezinqubo ezisemthethweni.
Inani lamafa eqiniso ngenxa ye-COVID-19 lingaba likhulu kakhulu, njengoba lingabandakanyi abantu abafa ngaphandle kokuhlolwa - ngokwesibonelo ekhaya, emakhaya asebekhulile, njll.
Idatha eyingxenye evela e-Italy ithole ukuthi inani labantu abafa ngokweqile ngesikhathi sobhadane lidlule inani eliyisisekelo lokufa nge-COVID ngezikhathi ezingama-4-5x.
"Owakhulumela izikhungo zase-US zokulawula nokugwema izifo (CDC) wavuma ukuthi "Siyazi ukuthi [inani elichazwe lokufa] lilinganiselwe", isitatimende esiqinisekiswe imibiko ye-anecdotal yokungabalwa kwezinto e-US Ukuqhathaniswa okunjalo kuvame ukwenzeka ezifweni eziwumshayabhuqe, njengobhadane lwe-H1N1 swine flu luka-2009. Ukufa kokuqala okuqinisekisiwe kwakuseWuhan ngoJanuwari 9, 2020. "
Ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kweChina ezwekazini kwenzeka ngoFebhuwari 1 ePhilippines, futhi ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kwe-Asia kwaba eFrance ngoFebhuwari 14.
NgoFebhuwari 28, ngaphandle kweChina, kwaba nokufa okungaphezu kweshumi nambili e-Iran, eNingizimu Korea nase-Italy.
NgoMashi 13, amazwe nezindawo ezingaphezu kwamashumi amane babike izimpilo, kuwo wonke amazwekazi ngaphandle kwe-Antarctica. Izinyathelo eziningana zivame ukusetshenziswa ukuze kukalwe inani lokufa.
Lezi zinombolo ziyahlukahluka ngokwendawo nangesikhathi, futhi zithonywa umthamo wokuhlolwa, ikhwalithi yohlelo lwezokunakekelwa kwempilo, izinketho zokwelashwa, isikhathi selokhu kwaqubuka ukuqubuka, kanye nezici zabantu ezifana nobudala, ubulili nempilo jikelele. Isilinganiso sokufa nesibalo sibonisa inani lokufa lihlukaniswe ngenani lamacala atholakala ngesikhathi esithile.
Ngokusekelwe ezibalo zaseJohn Hopkins University, isilinganiso somhlaba wonke sokufa nesibalo singama-6.0% (97.039/1.617.204) kusukela ngo-Ephreli 10, 2020.
Inani liyahlukahluka kuye ngezindawo.
EChina, ukulinganiselwa kwesilinganiso sokufa kwabantu kuye kwehla kusuka ku-17.3% (kwalabo abanezifo eziqala ngo-110 Januwari 2020) kuya ku-0.7% (kwalabo abanezifo eziqala ngemuva kuka-1 Februwari 2020).Ezinye izinyathelo zihlanganisa izinga lokufa kwabantu (CFR), elibonisa amaphesenti abantu abaxilongwayo abafa ngenxa yesifo, kanye nezinga lokufa kwabantu ababulawa ukutheleleka (IFR), elibonisa amaphesenti abantu abathelelekile (abaxilongwayo nabangakaxilongwa) abafa ngenxa yesifo.
Lezi zibalo azikho isikhathi esinqunyelwe futhi zilandela inani elithile labantu kusukela ekutheleleni kuya ekuxazululeni amacala.
Izazi eziningi ziye zazama ukubala lezi zinombolo zabantu abathile.
Isikhungo Sezokwelapha Esisekelwe Ebufakazini se-University of Oxford silinganisela ukuthi izinga lokufa kwabantu ababulawa ubhadane liphakathi kuka-0.1% no-0.39%.
Isilinganiso esiphezulu salolu hlu sihambisana nemiphumela yokuhlolwa kokuqala okungahleliwe kwe-COVID-19 eJalimane, kanye nocwaningo lwezibalo oluhlaziya umthelela wokuhlolwa kuzibalo ze-CFR.
I-WHO ithi lesi sifo singakwazi ukulawulwa.
Isiqongo nesikhathi sokuphela sokuqubuka akuqinisekile futhi kungahluka kuye ngokuthi indawo.
"UMaciej Boni wasePenn State University wathi, ""Uma kungalawulwa, ukuqubuka kwezifo ezithathelwanayo ngokuvamile kuyaqhubeka futhi kuqale ukwehla lapho lesi sifo siphela ezitolo ezitholakalayo".
"Kodwa cishe akunakwenzeka ukwenza noma isiphi isiphakamiso esihlakaniphile manje mayelana nokuthi lokho kuyoba nini".
"Umeluleki wezokwelapha omkhulu kahulumeni waseChina uZhong Nanshan wathi ""kungase kuphele ngoJuni"" uma wonke amazwe engakwazi ukuhambisana ukuze alandele iseluleko se-WHO ngezinyathelo zokumisa ukusabalala kwaleli gciwane".
"Ngomhlaka 17 Mashi, u-Adam Kucharski waseLondon School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine wathi i-SARS-CoV-2 ""izohamba, mhlawumbe unyaka noma amabili". "
"Ngokusho kocwaningo lwe-Imperial College olwenziwa nguNeil Ferguson, kuzodingeka ukuhlukaniswa ngokomzimba nezinye izinyathelo ""kuze kube yilapho umuthi wokugoma utholakala (ngokuzayo izinyanga eziyi-18 noma ngaphezulu)".
"UWilliam Schaffner waseVanderbilt University uthe, ""Ngicabanga ukuthi akunakwenzeka ukuthi le coronavirus ngoba ithunyelwe kalula izonyamalala ngokuphelele"" futhi "ingaba yisifo sesizini, sibuye njalo ngonyaka". "
Ukuthi ukubuya komzimba kuyingozi kangakanani kuyodingeka kuncike emthonjeni wokugoma kanye nasesilinganisweni sokuguquka.
Izimpawu ze-COVID-19 zingaba ezingaqondile futhi abantu abathelelekile bangaba nezimpawu ezingenalutho.
Izimpawu ezimbili ezivame kakhulu ukushisa (88%) nokukhwehlela okomile (68%).
Izimpawu ezingavamile zihlanganisa ukukhathala, ukukhiqizwa kwe-sputum yokuphefumula (i-phlegm), ukulahlekelwa ukuzwa iphunga, ukuphefumula okusheshayo, ubuhlungu bemisipha kanye nemihlathi, ubuhlungu bekhala, ikhanda, ukuqaleka, ukuhlanza, i-hemoptysis, isifo sohudo noma i-cyanosis. I-WHO ithi cishe umuntu oyedwa kwayisithupha uyagula kakhulu futhi kunzima ukuphefumula.
Izikhungo Zokulawula Nokuvimbela Izifo zase-U.S. (CDC) zibhala izimpawu eziphuthumayo njengokukhungatheka kokuphefumula, ubuhlungu obuqhubekayo esifubeni noma ingcindezi, ukudideka okungazelelwe, ubunzima bokuvuka, nobuso obuluhlaza noma izindebe; kunconywa ukunakekelwa kwezokwelapha ngokushesha uma kunezimpawu ezinjalo.Ukuqhubeka kwesifo kungaholela ekutholeni isifo samaphaphu esinamandla, isifo sokuphefumula esibucayi, i-sepsis, ukushaywa yisisu kanye nokufa.
Abanye balabo abahluphekayo bangase bangabi nezimpawu, abangenazo izimpawu zokwelashwa kodwa babe nemiphumela yokuhlolwa eqinisekisa ukutheleleka, ngakho abacwaningi banikeze iseluleko sokuthi labo abaxhumana eduze nabantu abahluphekayo kufanele babhekwe eduze futhi bahlolwe ukuze kuvinjelwe ukutheleleka.
Izilinganiso zaseChina zesilinganiso sokungabi nazimpawu zivela kuma-44% kuya kuma-45%.
Isikhathi esivamile sokufudumala (isikhathi esiphakathi kokutheleleka nokuqala kwezimpawu) sisukela ezinsukwini eziyodwa kuya kwezingu-14; ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu.Njengesibonelo sokungaqiniseki, ukulinganiselwa kwengxenye yabantu abane-COVID-19 abalahlekelwa umuzwa wabo wokuhogela kwaba ngama-30% ekuqaleni futhi kamuva kwehla yaya ku-15%.
Kunemininingwane ethile yokuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kanjani.
Kukholakala ukuthi lesi sifo sidluliselwa ngokuyinhloko lapho sithintana eduze nangamaconsi amancane akhiqizwa lapho ukhwehlela, ukhwehlela noma ukhuluma; lapho sithintana eduze ngaphakathi kwamamitha angu-1 kuya kwangu-2 (3 kuya ku-6 izinyawo).
Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukukhwehlela okungabonakali kungaholela emaconsi ahamba amamitha angu - 4,5 (amamitha angu - 15) kuya kumamitha angu - 8,2.
Abanye baye baphakamisa ukuthi leli gciwane lingadluliselwa ngamathontsi amancane ahlala isikhathi eside emoyeni, okungase akhiqizwe ngesikhathi sokukhuluma. Amathontsi okuphefumula nawo angakhiqizwa ngesikhathi sokuphefumula, kuhlanganise nalapho ukhuluma, nakuba leli gciwane ngokuvamile lingadluliswa emoyeni.
Amathonsi angafika emlonyeni noma emakhaleni abantu abaseduze noma mhlawumbe angene emaphashini.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha ezifana nokufakwa kwe-intubation nokuvuselelwa kwengqondo (CPR) zingabangela ukuba uketshezi lokuphefumula luvele emoyeni futhi ngaleyo ndlela luvele emoyeni.
Lingasakazeka nalapho umuntu ethinta indawo engcolisiwe, kuhlanganise nesikhumba, bese ethinta amehlo, impumulo noma umlomo.
Nakuba kunezinsolo zokuthi ingase isakazeke ngemithi, kulinganiselwa ukuthi ingozi incane.
Uhulumeni waseChina uphike ukuthi kungenzeka ukudluliselwa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngomlomo wezinso. Leli gciwane liyatheleleka kakhulu ezinsukwini ezintathu zokuqala ngemuva kokuqala kwezimpawu, yize ukusabalala kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuba kuvele izimpawu nasezigabeni ezalandela zesifo.
Abantu baye bahlaziywa benesifo kuze kube yizinsuku ezintathu ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu okusikisela ukuthi ukudluliselwa kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuba kutholakale izimpawu ezibalulekile.
Zimbalwa kuphela izindaba zamacala angenasibonakaliso aqinisekiswe ngelabhorethri, kodwa ukutheleleka okungenazibonakaliso kuye kwahlolwa kwamanye amazwe ngesikhathi kwenziwa ucwaningo lokulandelela ukuxhumana.
Isikhungo saseYurophu Sokuvimbela Nokulawula Izifo (ECDC) sithi nakuba kungakacaci kahle ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kalula kangakanani, umuntu oyedwa ngokuvamile utheleleka abanye ababili kuya kwabathathu. Leli gciwane lihlala amahora noma izinsuku ezindaweni eziphakeme.
Ngokuqondile, kwabonwa ukuthi leli gciwane lalingatholakala kuze kube yizinsuku ezintathu epulasitiki (i-polypropylene) nensimbi engagqwali engu-304, usuku olulodwa epulasitini, futhi kuze kube amahora amane epulasitiki.
Kodwa-ke, lokhu kuyahlukahluka ngokuya ngobumanzi nokushisa. Izilwane ezifuywayo nezinye izilwane ziye zathola i-COVID-19.
Abukho ubufakazi bokuthi izilwane zingadlulisela leli gciwane kubantu, nakuba iziphathimandla zaseBrithani zeluleka ukuba umuntu ageze izandla ngemva kokuxhumana nezilwane, njengokungathi ngemva kokuxhumana nezinye izindawo abantu abangase bathinte kuzo.
I-coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2) ye-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2) iyi-virus entsha, eyahlukaniswa okokuqala kubantu abathathu abane-pneumonia exhunywe ku-cluster yeziguli ezibucayi zokuphefumula eWuhan.
Zonke izici ze-virus entsha ye-SARS-CoV-2 zenzeka kuma-coronavirus ahlobene emvelweni.Ngaphandle komzimba womuntu, leli gciwane libulawa yinsipho yasendlini, echitha imvilophu yalo yokuvikela.I-SARS-CoV-2 ihlobene eduze ne-SARS-CoV yokuqala.
Kucatshangwa ukuthi ivela emithonjeni yezilwane.
Ukuhlaziywa kwezakhi zofuzo kuveze ukuthi i-coronavirus ihlangana ngobuningi nohlobo lwe-Betacoronavirus, ku-subgenus Sarbecovirus (inzalo B) kanye nezinhlobo ezimbili ezivezwe yizimfudu.
Kufana ngama-96% ezingeni lonke le-genome namanye amasampula e-bat coronavirus (BatCov RaTG13).
NgoFebhuwari 2020, abacwaningi baseChina bathola ukuthi kunomehluko owodwa kuphela we-amino acid ezingxenyeni ezithile zemigqa ye-genome phakathi kwama-virus avela kuma-pangolin nalabo abavela kubantu.
Ukuqhathaniswa kwe-genome yonke kuze kube manje kutholile ukuthi okungenani ama-92% omkhiqizo wezakhi zofuzo owabiwe phakathi kwe-pangolin coronavirus ne-SARS-CoV-2, okunganele ukufakazela ukuthi ama-pangolin angumbungazi ophakathi.
Ukutheleleka yileli gciwane kungatholakala okwesikhashana ngesisekelo sezimpawu, nakuba ukuqinisekiswa ekugcineni kungenziwa ukusabela kweketane kwe-transcription polymerase chain (rRT-PCR) kwe-secretions egqoke ukutheleleka noma ukubonwa nge-CT.
Ucwaningo oluqhathanisa i-PCR ne-CT eWuhan lubonise ukuthi i-CT iyathinteka kakhulu kune-PCR, nakuba ingacacisiwe, futhi izici zayo eziningi zokuqopha izithombe zixubene nezinye izifo zamaphaphu nezinqubo zesifo.
"NgoMashi 2020, i-American College of Radiology incoma ukuthi ""i-CT akufanele isetshenziselwe ukuhlolwa noma njengokuhlolwa komugqa wokuqala ukuthola i-COVID-19"."
I-WHO ishicilele izinqubo eziningana zokuhlola i-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2, okokuqala kukhiphe ngoJanuwari 17.
Ukuhlolwa kusebenzisa i-reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) yesikhathi sangempela.
Ukuhlolwa kungenziwa kumasampula okuphefumula noma egazi.
Imiphumela ngokuvamile itholakala ngemva kwamahora ambalwa noma izinsuku.
Ngokuvamile lolu cwaningo lwenziwa nge-swab ye-nasopharyngeal nakuba ingasetshenziswa ne-swab yomphimbo.Izilabhorethri eziningi nezinkampani zikhiqiza izivivinyo ze-serological, ezithola ama-antibodies.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 6, 2020, akukho neyodwa yalezi zinto eye yafakazelwa ukuthi inembile ngokwanele ukuba ivunyelwe ukusetshenziswa kabanzi.
E-US, ukuhlolwa kwe-serological okuthuthukiswe yi-Cellex kuvunyelwe ukusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo kuphela ngamalebhu aqinisekisiwe.
Izici ezivelele zokuqopha izithombe ku- radiographs naku- computed tomography (CT) zabantu abanezimpawu zihlanganisa ukungafihli kwe- asymmetrical peripheral ground glass kanye nokungabikho kokukhishwa kwe- pleural.
I-Italian Radiological Society ihlanganisa i-database yomhlaba wonke eku-inthanethi yemiphumela yokuthwebula izithombe yezigameko eziqinisekisiwe.
Ngenxa yokuhlangana nezinye izifo ezifana ne-adenovirus, ukuthathwa kwezithombe ngaphandle kokuqinisekiswa yi-PCR kunobuciko obuncane ekutholeni i-COVID-19.
Ucwaningo olukhulu eChina lwaqhathanisa imiphumela ye-CT yesifuba ne-PCR futhi lwabonisa ukuthi nakuba ukubonwa kwemifanekiso kungakhethekile kangako ekutheleleni, kuyashesha futhi kuyathinteka, okusikisela ukuthi kufanele kubhekwe njengethuluzi lokuhlola ezindaweni ezibandakanyekile.
Kuye kwakhiwa amanethiwekhi e-neural convolutional asekelwe ebuhlakani bokufakelwa ukuze kutholakale izici zokubonisa igciwane nge-radiograph kanye ne-CT.
Amasu okuvimbela ukudluliselwa kwalesi sifo ahlanganisa ukugcina inhlanzeko yomuntu siqu, ukugeza izandla, ukugwema ukuthinta amehlo, impumulo noma umlomo ngezandla ezingakugezi, nokukhwehlela noma ukuqhuma ezintanjeni nokufaka izicubu ngqo esitsheni semfucuza.
Labo okungenzeka sebevele banesifo baye banconywa ukuba bagqoke imaski yokuhlinza obala.
Kunconywa nezinyathelo zokuhlukanisa abantu emzimbeni ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa. Ohulumeni abaningi baye banciphisa noma banikeza iseluleko mayelana nokuhamba okungabalulekile okuya nokubuya emazweni nasezindaweni ezithintekile.
Nokho, leli gciwane selifinyelele esigabeni sokusakazeka komphakathi ezingxenyeni ezinkulu zomhlaba.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi leli gciwane lisakazeka emphakathini, futhi amanye amalungu omphakathi awazi ukuthi atheleleke kuphi noma kanjani. Abahlinzeki bezempilo abanakekela umuntu ongase abe notheleleke batuswa ukuthi basebenzise izindlela ezijwayelekile zokuqapha, izindlela zokuqapha zokuxhumana nokuvikela amehlo.Ukulandelela ukuxhumana kuyindlela ebalulekile ezikhungweni zezempilo ukuthola umthombo wokutheleleka nokuvimbela ukudluliselwa okwengeziwe.
Ukusetshenziswa kwedatha yendawo evela kumakhalekhukhwini ohulumeni ngale njongo kuye kwabangela ukukhathazeka ngobumfihlo, ne-Amnesty International kanye nezinye izinhlangano ezingaphezu kwekhulu zikhiphe isitatimende esicela imikhawulo kulolu hlobo lokuqapha.
Izinhlelo zokusebenza ezahlukahlukene zeselula ziye zasetshenziswa noma zaphakanyiswa ukusetshenziswa ngokuzithandela, futhi kusukela ngo-Ephreli 7, 2020, amaqembu ochwepheshe angaphezu kweshumi ayesebenza ngezixazululo ezihambisana nobumfihlo, njengokusebenzisa iBluetooth ukubhalisa ukusondelana komsebenzisi namanye amafoni eselula.
Abasebenzisi bayothola umyalezo uma bexhumana eduze nomuntu othole ukuthi une-COVID-19. Kuzungeza imibono eyiphutha mayelana nokuthi ungayivimbela kanjani igciwane; ngokwesibonelo, ukugeza ikhala nokuxubha ngamanzi omlomo akuphumeleli.
Akukho umuthi wokugoma i-COVID-19, yize izinhlangano eziningi zisebenza ekuthuthukiseni omunye.
Kunconywa ukugeza izandla ukuze kugwenywe ukusabalala kwesifo.
I-CDC incoma ukuba abantu bageze izandla njalo ngensipho namanzi okungenani imizuzwana engamashumi amabili, ikakhulukazi ngemva kokuya endlini yangasese noma lapho izandla zingcolile ngokusobala; ngaphambi kokudla; nangemva kokuphefumula ekhaleni, ekhwehlela noma ekhwehlela.
Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi ngaphandle komzimba womuntu, leli gciwane libulawa isepha lasekhaya, eliqhumisa ibhola lalo elivikelayo.
