IJapan inikele ngemaski obuso ayisigidi eWuhan, iTurkey ithumele imishini yezokwelapha, iRussia ithumele izimpahla zokwelapha ezingaphezu kwamathani ayi-13 eWuhan, iMalaysia imemezele ukunikela ngezigqoko zokwelapha eziyizigidi eziyi-18 eChina, iJalimane inikeze izimpahla ezahlukahlukene zezokwelapha ezibandakanya amasudi ayi-10,000 eHazmat, kanti i-United States inikele ngamathani ayi-17.8 ezimpahla zokwelapha eChina futhi yathembisa ukusekelwa kwezimali okungeziwe okungu- $ 100 million emazweni athintekile. Ngemuva kokuthi amacala eChina abonakale esezinzile, izwe lithumela usizo emazweni ahlukahlukene athintwe yilesi sifo.
NgoMashi, iChina, iCuba neRussia yathumela izimpahla zezokwelapha kanye nochwepheshe ukusiza i-Italy ukubhekana nokuqubuka kwayo kwe-coronavirus.
UJack Ma usomabhizinisi wathumela amakhithi okuhlola angu-1.1 million, amaski obuso ayizigidi eziyisithupha, nezingubo zokuzivikela ezingu-60.000 e-Addis Ababa, e-Ethiopia ukuze zisakazwe yi-African Union.
Kamuva wathumela amakhithi okuhlola angu-5 000, amaski obuso angu-100 000 namathuluzi okuphefumula ama-5 ePanama.
UMa wanikela nangezinto zokwelapha eCanada. INetherlands, iSpain, iTurkey, iGeorgia neCzech Republic zikhombise ukukhathazeka kwazo ngemaski nezikhwama zokuhlola ezenziwe eChina.
Isibonelo, iSpain ikhiphe amakhithi okuhlola ama-coronavirus angama-58,000 enziwe eChina ngesilinganiso sokunemba esingu-30% nje kuphela, kuyilapho iNetherlands ikhiphe amaski obuso angama-600,000 aseChina ayenephutha.
IBelgium yacela ukuhoxisa izifihla-buso ezingu-100 000 ezingasetshenziswanga, okwakuthiwa zivela eChina, kodwa empeleni zazivela eColombia.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, usizo lwaseChina luye lwazamukelwa kahle ezingxenyeni ezithile zaseLatin America nase-Afrika. Ngo-April 2, iWorld Bank yaqala imisebenzi yokusiza amazwe asathuthuka.
I-WHO iye yazisa imizamo yezithunywa zevangeli zaseChina ekulawuleni nasekugcineni lolu bhubhane.
"I-WHO yaqaphela umehluko phakathi kokugqashuka kwe-SARS kuka-2002 kuya ku-2004, lapho iziphathimandla zaseChina zabesolwa khona ngokufihla okuvimbela imizamo yokuvimbela nokuvimbela, kanye nenkinga yamanje lapho uhulumeni ophakathi "ehlinzeke khona izibuyekezo ezijwayelekile ukugwema ukwethuka ngaphambi kwamaholide oNyaka Omusha Wenyanga".
"NgoJanuwari 23, ekuphenduleni isinqumo seziphathimandla eziphakathi sokusebenzisa ukuvinjelwa kwezithuthi eWuhan, ummeleli we-WHO uGauden Galea waphawula ukuthi yize "ngokuqinisekile kwakungeyona isincomo esenziwe yi-WHO", futhi "kuyisibonakaliso esibaluleke kakhulu sokuzibophezela ukuvimbela lolu bhubhane endaweni lapho lugxile kakhulu khona" futhi wakubiza ngokuthi "okungazange kube khona emlandweni wezempilo yomphakathi".NgoJanuwari 30, ngemuva kokuqinisekiswa kokudluliselwa komuntu kumuntu ngaphandle kweChina nokwanda kwenani lamacala kwamanye amazwe, i-WHO yamemezela ukuqubuka njengesifo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi sokukhathazeka kwamazwe omhlaba (PHEIC), i-PHEIC yesithupha selokhu kwaqala ukusetshenziswa lesi sinyathelo ngesikhathi sobhadane lomkhuhlane wezingulube ngo-2009".
"UMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom uthe i-PHEIC ibangelwa "ngengozi yokusabalala emhlabeni wonke, ikakhulukazi emazweni anemali ephansi naphakathi ngaphandle kwezinhlelo zezempilo eziqinile".
"Ephendula ekusetshenzisweni kwemikhawulo yokuhamba, uTedros wathi ""akukho sizathu sezinyathelo eziphazamisa ngokungadingekile ukuhamba nokuhweba kwamazwe omhlaba"" nokuthi ""i-WHO ayincomi ukulinganisela ukuhweba nokuhamba""".
"Ngosuku luka-5 kuFebhuwari, i-WHO yacela umphakathi womhlaba wonke ukuthi unikeze umnikelo wama- $ 675 million ukuze usekele ukulungela amasu emazweni anemali encane, isho ukuphuthuma kokusekela lawo mazwe "angenazo izinhlelo zokuthola abantu abathole leli gciwane, noma ngabe livela".
"UTedros waqhubeka esho ukuthi ""siqinile njengesixhumanisi sethu esibuthakathaka kakhulu"" futhi wanxusa umphakathi wamazwe omhlaba ukuba "utshale imali namuhla noma ukhokhe kamuva". NgoFebhuwari 11, i-WHO engqungqutheleni yabezindaba yasungula i-COVID-19 njengegama lesifo".
"Ngalo lolo suku, uTedros wathi uNobhala-Jikelele we-UN u-Antonio Guterres wayevumile ukunikeza ""amandla esistimu yonke ye-UN ekuphenduleni"."
"Ithimba le-UN Crisis Management lavuselelwa ngenxa yalokho, okuvumela ukuxhumanisa impendulo yonke yeZizwe Ezihlangene, okuyinto i-WHO ithi izovumela ukuba "igxile ekuphenduleni kwezempilo ngenkathi ezinye izinhlaka zingaletha ubuchwepheshe bazo ukuze zibhekane nemithelela ebanzi yezenhlalo, ezomnotho nentuthuko yokuqubuka".
"Ngosuku luka-14 kuFebhuwari, kwaqaliswa iqembu le-WHO eliholwa yi-Joint Mission Team neChina ukuhlinzeka ngochwepheshe bamazwe omhlaba kanye ne-WHO emhlabathini eChina ukusiza ekuphathweni kwasekhaya nokuhlola ""ububuthakathaka nokudluliselwa kwesifo"" ngokusingatha imihlangano yokusebenzela nemihlangano enezikhungo eziyinhloko ezingeni likazwelonke nokwenza ukuvakashelwa kwendawo ukuze kuhlolwe ""umeke imisebenzi yokuphendula ezingeni lezifundazwe nezesifunda, kufaka phakathi izindawo zasemadolobheni nezasemaphandleni"".Ngosuku luka-25 kuFebhuwari, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi ""umhlaba kufanele wenze okuningi ukuze ulungiselele ubhadane lwe-coronavirus olungaba khona,"" ithi nakuba kusesekusenesikhathi ukuwubiza ngokuthi ubhadane, amazwe kufanele "asesezingeni lokulungela".
"Njengoba kuphendulwa ukuqubuka okuthuthukayo e-Iran, i-WHO yathumela i-Joint Mission Team lapho ukuhlola isimo. NgoFebhuwari 28, izikhulu ze-WHO zithi ukuhlolwa kosongo lwe-coronavirus ezingeni lomhlaba kuzokwenyuswa kusuka "ekuphakeme" kuye "ekuphakeme kakhulu", izinga eliphakeme kakhulu lokuqapha nokuhlolwa kwengozi".
"UMike Ryan, ongumphathi ophethe wohlelo lwe-WHO lwezimo eziphuthumayo zezempilo, waxwayisa esitatimendeni esithi ""Lokhu kuyisivivinyo seqiniso kuwo wonke uhulumeni emhlabeni: Vuka".
"Le virus ingase ibe endleleni yayo futhi udinga ukuba ulungele, "" enxusa ukuthi izinyathelo ezifanele zokuphendula zingasiza umhlaba ugweme ""okubi kakhulu". "
"U-Ryan waveza ukuthi idatha yamanje ayiqinisekisi ukuthi izikhulu zezempilo zomphakathi zimemezele ubhadane lomhlaba wonke, wathi isimemezelo esinjalo sasiyosho ukuthi ""simukela ukuthi wonke umuntu emhlabeni uzovezwa yileso gciwane". ""
NgoMashi 11, i-WHO yamemezela ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus njengobhadane.
"UMqondisi-Jikelele uthe i-WHO "ikhathazeke kakhulu ngezinga elikhathazayo lokusabalala nobunzima, nangamazinga okukhathazeka ngokungazi". "I-WHO ibhekane nokugxekwa okukhulu ngalokho okubhekwa njengokuphathwa okunganele kwesifo, kufaka phakathi ukumenyezelwa okuphuzile kwesimo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi nokuhlukaniswa kwegciwane njengesifo esiwumqedazwe".
Ukuphikisana kwafaka isicelo sokuba uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom enze isexwayiso sakhe, esayinwe abantu abangu-733,000 kusukela ngo-Ephreli 6.
NgoMashi 26, 2020, ochwepheshe abaningi bezomthetho bamazwe omhlaba be-UN bagcizelela ukuhlonishwa kwamalungelo abo bonke abantu phakathi nobhubhane lwe-COVID-19.
Iqembu lochwepheshe lachaza ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokunikeza usizo lokusindisa ukuphila futhi uhulumeni unesibopho salokhu.
Iqembu laphakamisa ukuthi ukuntuleka kwemithombo noma umshwalense wezempilo akufanele kube yisisekelo sokubandlulula iqembu elithile.
Ochwepheshe bagcizelela ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokuthola impilo, kuhlanganise nabantu abakhubazekile, abangamalungu amaqembu amancane, abantu asebekhulile, abantu abahlakazekile, abangenamakhaya, abahlala ezimweni ezimbi kakhulu, abantu abavalelwe ejele, kanye nababaleki namanye amaqembu angakahlelwa ayedinga usizo lukahulumeni.
Izinhlangano zikahulumeni zamazwe omhlaba zixoxa ngemiphumela yezomnotho nezenhlalo yenhlekelele ye-COVID-19.
I-Organisation for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD) iye yasungula ipulatifomu yokunikeza ulwazi olufanele nolunzulu mayelana nezimpendulo zenqubomgomo emazweni emhlabeni wonke, kanye nemibono nezeluleko.
Kusukela ezinqubeni zokuqinisa izinhlelo zezempilo kanye nomnotho womhlaba kuya ekubhekaneni nemiphumela yokuvalwa kwemikhumbi kanye nemikhawulo yokuhamba, i-hub edijithali ifaka i-Country Policy Tracker, futhi ihlose ukusiza amazwe afunde komunye nomunye futhi ahambisane ngokuphumelelayo nezinselelo ze-coronavirus emhlabeni jikelele.
Uhulumeni waseChina uye wagxekwa yi-United States, uNgqongqoshe wase-UK weHhovisi leKhabhinethi uMichael Gove, nendodana kaMongameli waseBrazil uJaiir Bolsonaro u-Eduardo Bolsonaro ngokusingatha ubhadane, olwaqala esifundazweni saseChina iHubei.
Abaphathi abaningi bezingxenye zesifundazwe zeCPC baxoshwa ngenxa yokuziphatha kwabo ngemizamo yokuhlukaniswa kwabantu eCentral China, okuyisibonakaliso sokungajabuli ngendlela izikhundla zezombusazwe eziphendule ngayo ukuqubuka kulezi zindawo.
Abanye abahlaziyi bakholelwa ukuthi lesi sinyathelo sasihloselwe ukuvikela unobhala jikelele weCPC uXi Jinping ekucasukeni komphakathi ngokuqubuka kwe-coronavirus.
Ezinye izikhulu zaseChina, ngokwesibonelo uZhao Lijian, zalahla ukuvuma kwangaphambilini ukuthi ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus kwaqala eWuhan, ngokuxhasa imibono yokuzungulela mayelana ne-COVID-19 evela e-US noma e-Italy.
"Uhulumeni wase-US kaDonald Trump ubhekise ku-coronavirus ngokuthi "i-virus yaseChina" noma "i-virus yaseWuhan" ethi "ukucwaningwa kwabantu eChina kucindezele igciwane manje eliye laba yisibetho somqedazwe womhlaba wonke", okuye kwagxekwa abanye abagxeki ngokuthi ubuhlanga futhi "kuphazamisa ukwehluleka kokuphatha kwakhe ukuvimbela lesi sifo".
"I-Daily Beast yathola ikhebula likahulumeni wase-US elichaza isu lokuxhumana elinomsuka ocacile eMkhandlwini Wezokuphepha Kazwelonke, necebo elicashunwe ngokuthi ""Konke mayelana neChina".
"Sitshelwa ukuthi sizame ukufinyelela kulo myalezo nganoma iyiphi indlela, kuhlanganise nezingqungquthela zabezindaba kanye nokuvela kwethelevishini. ""Izikhungo ezifana nePolitico, Foreign Policy, neBloomberg zithi imizamo yaseChina yokuthumela usizo emazweni athintwe yileli gciwane iyingxenye yomzamo wokuphromotha wokuthonya umhlaba wonke".
"Inhloko yezepolitiki zangaphandle ye-EU uJosep Borrell waxwayisa ngokuthi kukhona ""isici se-geopolitical esihlanganisa ukulwa nethonya ngokusebenzisa ukujikeleza kanye 'nezepolitiki zokupha.'"
"UBorrell waphinde wathi ""iChina isekela ngokuqinile umyalezo wokuthi, ngokungafani ne-US, iyingxenye yomlingani ophethe kahle futhi onokwethenjelwa".""
I-China iphinde yacela i-US ukuthi isuse izibopho zayo eSyria, eVenezuela nase-Iran, kanti ngokusho kwemibiko ithumela usizo kula mazwe amabili okugcina.
Umnikelo kaJack Ma wamamaski angu-100 000 eCuba wavinjelwa yizijeziso zase-US ngo-Ephreli 3.
Izikhulu zase-US ziye zabuye zaqanjwa ngecala lokuqondisa kabusha usizo olwenzelwe ezinye izizwe ezweni lazo.
Futhi kuye kwabikwa ukuthi kunezingxabano ezihlobene nemaski phakathi kwamanye amazwe, njengeJalimane, i-Austria neSwitzerland; neCzech Republic ne-Italy.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, iTurkey yathatha amakhulu ama-ventilator ayebhekiswe eSpain.
Ekuqaleni kukaMashi, uhulumeni wase-Italy wagxeka ukungabi khona kobudlelwane kwe-European Union ne-Italy ethintwe yi-coronavirus.
"UMaurizio Massari, ummeli wase-Italy e-EU, uthe ""IChina kuphela ephendule kabili".
