"Iphephandaba lase-Italy iLa Stampa lacaphuna "umthombo wezepolitiki ophakeme" ongaziwa ukuthi amaphesenti angu-80 ensizakalo yaseRussia "ayingenamsebenzi noma ayisizi ngalutho e-Italy".
"Umthombo usola iRussia ngokuqala "ukuhlaselwa kwe-geopolitical and diplomatic" okuthakazelisayo".
UMongameli waseLombardy, u-Attilio Fontana, kanye noNgqongqoshe Wezangaphandle wase-Italy uLuigi Di Maio bakwenqaba ukubikwa kwabezindaba futhi babonga.
IRussia yathumela indiza yezimpahla neyokusiza kwezokwelapha e-United States.
"Isikhulumi seKremlin uDmitry Peskov sathi ""lapho sinikeza usizo kozakwabo baseMelika, [uPutin] ucabanga ukuthi lapho abakhiqizi baseMelika bemishini yezokwelapha nezinto zokwakha bethola amandla, bazokwazi ukuphendula uma kudingeka".""
"Ukuvivinya impi ye-NATO "Defender 2020" ehleliwe eJalimane, ePoland, naseBalt, ukuvivinya okukhulu kwe-NATO kusukela ekupheleni kweMpi Yomshoshaphansi, kuzobanjelwa ngezinga elincane".
"Umangabhala Jikelele we-Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament uKate Hudson ugxeke ukuzivocavoca kweDefender 2020: ""Ekuphikisweni kwamanje kwezempilo yomphakathi, akufaki kuphela izimpilo zamabutho avela e-US nakwamanye amazwe amaningi aseYurophu abamba iqhaza kodwa nezakhamizi zamazwe asebenza kuwo. ""Uhulumeni wase-Iran uthinteke kakhulu yileli gciwane, amalungu ephalamende angaba nguzinkulungwane ezimbili athelelekile kanye nezinye izibalo zezombusazwe eziyishumi nanhlanu ezikhona noma ezake zaba khona".
UMongameli wase-Iran uHasan Rouhani wabhala incwadi yomphakathi eya kubaholi bomhlaba becela usizo ngo-14 Mashi 2020, ethi izwe lakhe liyakhathazeka ngokulwa nalolu bhubhane ngenxa yokuntuleka kokufinyelela ezimakethe zomhlaba wonke ngenxa yezibopho zase-United States ngokumelene ne-Iran.Ubhubhane luholele ekuceleni kwe-United States ukuthi yamukele izinqubomgomo zenhlalo ezivamile kwamanye amazwe acebile, kufaka phakathi ukunakekelwa kwezempilo jikelele, ukunakekelwa kwezingane okuvamile, ikhefu lomndeni elikhokhelwayo, nezinga eliphakeme lemali yezempilo yomphakathi.
Abahlaziyi bezombusazwe balindele ukuthi lokhu kungathinta kabi amathuba kaDonald Trump okuphinda akhethwe okhethweni lukaMengameli ka-2020.
