Ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus kuye kwabangela izimo eziningana zokushoda kokunikezwa, okubangelwa ukusetshenziswa okwandayo kwemishini yokulwa nokuqubuka, ukuthenga ukwethuka, nokuphazamiseka kwemisebenzi yezimboni neyokuthutha.
I-United States Food and Drug Administration ikhiphe izixwayiso mayelana nokushoda kwezidakamizwa nemishini yezokwelapha ngenxa yokwanda kwesidingo sabathengi nokuphazamiseka kwabahlinzeki.
Izindawo eziningana nazo zabona ukuthenga okuphazamisayo okwaholela ekutheni izitolo zikhishwe izimpahla eziyisisekelo ezifana nokudla, iphepha lokuwasha namanzi agcwele amabhodlela, okwenza kube nokushoda kokuphakelwa.
Umkhakha wezobuchwepheshe uye waxwayisa ngokulibaziseka kokuthumela izimpahla zobuchwepheshe.
NgokukaMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO uTedros Adhanom, isidingo semishini yokuzivikela siye sakhuphuka ngokuphindwe kayikhulu.
Lokhu kucela kuye kwaholela ekunyukeni kwamanani okufika izikhathi ezingamashumi amabili kunamanani avamile futhi kwabangela ukubambezeleka kokunikezwa kwezinto zokwelapha izinyanga ezine kuya kweziyisithupha.
Kuye kwabangela nokushoda kwemishini yokuzivikela emhlabeni wonke, futhi i-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi lokhu kuyingozi kubasebenzi bezempilo.
