Umsebenzi udale ukuntuleka kwefomula yezingane kwezinye izimakethe ezinkulu futhi kamuva wavinjelwa nguhulumeni wase-Australia. Naphezu kokwanda okuphezulu kwamacala e-COVID-19 enyakatho ye-Italy naseWuhan, kanye nesidingo esiphezulu semikhiqizo yokudla, zombili lezi zindawo ziye zagcinwa zingenalutho lokudla.
