Amashalofu okudla angenalutho ayevela okwesikhashana, ngisho nasedolobheni laseWuhan, kuyilapho izikhulu zikahulumeni waseChina zikhipha izimpahla zenyama yengulube ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukudla okwanele kubantu.
