Ukuhlolwa kwelebhu kwesifo sokuphefumula se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) kanye negciwane elihambisana ne-SARS-CoV-2 kufaka phakathi izindlela ezithola ubukhona begciwane nalabo abathola ama-antibodies akhiqizwa ngokuphendula ukutheleleka.
Ukuba khona kwegciwane kumasampula kuqinisekiswa yi-RT-PCR, ethola i-RNA ye-coronavirus.
Lolu hlelo lokuhlola luqondile futhi lwenzelwe ukuthola i-RNA ye-SARS-CoV-2 kuphela.
Isetshenziselwa ukuqinisekisa ukutheleleka okusha kakhulu noma okusebenzayo.
Ukuthola ama-antibody (serology) kungasetshenziswa kokubili ekuxilongweni nasekugadweni kwabantu.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-antibody kubonisa ukuthi bangaki abantu abaye baba nalesi sifo, kuhlanganise nalabo abanezimpawu ezincane kakhulu ukuba babike noma ababengazange babe nazo.
Izinga lokufa lesifo kanye nezinga lokuzivikela emhlambini emphakathini linganqunywa ngemiphumela yalesi sihlolwa.
Ngenxa yokuhlolwa okulinganiselwe, kusukela ngoMashi 2020 akukho mazwe ayenemininingwane ethembekile ngokwanda kwaleli gciwane kubantu bawo.
Ngo-March 23, alikho izwe elalihlolwe ngaphezu kuka-3% wabantu balo, futhi kunezinguquko ezinkulu ekutheni kwenziwa izivivinyo ezingakanani emazweni ngamazwe.
Lokhu kuguquguquka kungenzeka futhi kuthinte kakhulu izinga lokufa kwabantu ababulewe, okungenzeka ukuthi lilinganiswe kakhulu kwamanye amazwe.
Ukusebenzisa i-reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) yesikhathi sangempela, ukuhlolwa kungenziwa kumasampula okuphefumula atholakala ngezindlela ezihlukahlukene, kuhlanganise nesampula le-nasopharyngeal swab noma isampula le-sputum.
Imiphumela ngokuvamile itholakala kungakapheli amahora ambalwa kuya ezinsukwini ezimbili.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-RT-PCR okwenziwe nge-swabs yentamo kunokwethenjelwa kuphela ngesonto lokuqala lesifo.
Kamuva leli gciwane lingaphela emqaleni kanti liyaqhubeka liphindaphindeka emaphashini.
Kubantu abatheleleke abahlolwe ngesonto lesibili, esikhundleni salokho, kungathathwa amasampula emigwaqweni yomoya ejulile nge-suction catheter noma kusetshenziswe izinto zokukhwehlela (i-sputum).
Olunye lwezivivinyo zokuqala ze-PCR lwakhiwa eCharité eBerlin ngoJanuwari 2020 kusetshenziswa i-reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), futhi lwakha isisekelo samakhithi angama-250,000 wokusabalalisa yi-World Health Organization (WHO).
I-United Kingdom nayo yayithuthukise ukuhlolwa ngoJanuwari 23, 2020. Inkampani yaseNingizimu Korea i-Kogenebiotech yathuthukisa ikhithi yokuxilonga ye-SARS-CoV-2 esezingeni lomtholampilo, esekelwe ku-PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ngoJanuwari 28, 2020.
