Lezi zisetshenziselwa ukuthola ukutheleleka kubantu abaqala ngezinsuku ezingu-7 noma ngaphezulu ngemuva kokuqala kwezimpawu, ukunquma ukutheleleka, nokubhekwa kwabantu.Ukuhlolwa kungenziwa emalebhu amakhulu (CLT) noma ngokuhlolwa okuvela endaweni yokunakekela (PoCT).
Izinhlelo ezizenzakalelayo ezinamandla amakhulu ezise laboratories eziningi zomtholampilo zizokwazi ukwenza lezi zivivinyo kodwa ukutholakala kwazo kuzoncika esimisweni sokukhiqiza sohlelo ngalunye.
I-CLT ngokuvamile isebenzisa isampula elilodwa legazi elisezingeni eliphansi, nakuba isampula elilandelayo lingasetshenziswa ukulandela impendulo yomzimba.
Ku- PoCT isampula elilodwa legazi ngokuvamile litholakala ngokushaya isikhumba.
Ngokungafani nezindlela ze-PCR, isinyathelo sokukhipha asidingeki ngaphambi kokuhlolwa. NgoMashi 26, 2020, i-FDA yabala izinhlangano ezingama-29 ezazinikeze isaziso esifundweni njengoba kudingeka futhi manje manje sezikwazi ukusabalalisa izivivinyo zazo ze-antibody.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 7, 2020, ukuhlolwa okukodwa kuphela okuvunyelwe yi-FDA ngaphansi kwegunya lokusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo. Ekupheleni kukaMashi 2020, i-Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics ne-Epitope Diagnostics ithole ukuvunywa kweYurophu kwamakhithi ayo okuhlola, angabona ama-antibody we-IgG ne-IgA ngokumelene negciwane kumasampula egazi.
Amandla okuhlola angamakhulu amaningana amasampula kungakapheli amahora futhi ngenxa yalokho ashesha kakhulu kunokuhlolwa okujwayelekile kwe-PCR kwe-RNA ye-virus.
Amaphilisi ngokuvamile atholakala ngemva kwezinsuku ezingu-14 ukuqala kwesifo. Ekuqaleni kuka-April, i-UK yathola ukuthi ayikho neyodwa yamakhithi okuhlola amaphilisi athengiwe ayilungile ngokwanele ukuba isetshenziswe.
"IHong Kong isungule uhlelo lapho iziguli ezisolwayo zingahlala khona ekhaya, ""umnyango wezimo eziphuthumayo uzonikeza isiguli isampula", bayakutshela, bayithumele emuva futhi bathole umphumela wokuhlolwa isikhashana ngemuva kwalokho.I-British NHS imemezele ukuthi ihlose uhlelo lokuhlola iziguli ezisolwayo ekhaya, okususa ingozi yokuthi isiguli sibulale abanye uma sifika esibhedlela noma sidinga ukubulala amagciwane i-ambulensi uma isetshenziswa.Ekuhlolweni okuqhutshwa nge-driving ye-COVID-19 yamacala asolwayo, uchwepheshe wezokunakekelwa kwezempilo uthatha isampula esebenzisa izinyathelo ezifanele zokuphepha".
