Izindlela zokubhekana ezahlukene zokuhlola ezihlose izingxenye ezahlukene zephrofayili yezakhi zofuzo ze-coronavirus zathuthukiswa eChina, eFrance, eJalimane, eHong Kong, eJapane nase-United States.
