NgoMashi 16, iWorld Health Organization yacela ukuthi kuqiniswe izinhlelo zokuhlola njengendlela engcono yokunciphisa ukuqhubeka kobhadane lwe-COVID-19. Isidingo esiphakeme sokuhlola ngenxa yokusabalala okukhulu kwegciwane sabangela ukubuyela emuva kokuhlolwa ngamakhulu ezinkulungwane zamalebhu aseMelika, futhi izimpahla zama-swabs kanye nama-reagents amakhemikhali zaqala ukucindezeleka.
