"UNdunankulu uMatovič uphakamisa ukuthi lezi zisetshenziswe eMfuleni iDanube. U-Ateş Kara woMnyango Wezempilo waseTurkey uthe amakhithi okuhlola athengwe yiTurkey eChina "anezinga eliphezulu lokuxhumana" futhi akazange "awafake ekusetshenzisweni. ""I-UK ithenge amakhithi okuhlola ayizigidi ezingama-3.5 eChina kodwa ekuqaleni kuka-Ephreli 2020 yamemezela ukuthi awawusebenziseki".
Ukuhlolwa, okulandelwa ukuhlukaniswa kwalabo abahlolwe bephumelela kanye nokulandelela labo abantu ababenesifo se-SARS-CoV-2 ababenokuxhumana nabo, kwaholela emiphumeleni emihle.
Abacwaningi abasebenza edolobheni lase-Italy iVò, indawo lapho kwafa khona abantu bokuqala nge-COVID-19 e-Italy, baqhuba imijikelezo emibili yokuhlola kubantu abacishe babe ngu-3 400, ngezinsuku eziyishumi.
Cishe uhhafu wabantu abahlolwa benemiphumela emihle abazange babe nezimpawu, futhi bonke abantu ababekhona babehlukaniswe.
Njengoba ukuhamba komphakathi kwakunqunyelwe, lokhu kwaqeda ngokuphelele izifo ezintsha.
Ngokulandelela okuqinile kokuxhumana, imikhawulo yokuhamba engenayo, ukuhlolwa, nokuhlukaniswa kwabantu, ubhadane lwe-coronavirus luka-2020 eSingapore luye lwaqhubeka kancane kakhulu kunamanye amazwe athuthukile, kodwa ngaphandle kwemikhawulo eqinile njengokuvalwa okuphoqelelwe kwamakhefu nezindawo zokuthengisa.
Imicimbi eminingi ikhanselwe, futhi iSingapore yaqala ukweluleka izakhamuzi ukuba zihlale ekhaya ngoMashi 28, kodwa izikole zavula kabusha ngesikhathi ngemuva kweholide ngoMashi 23.
Amanye amazwe amaningi aphinde aphatha ubhadane ngokulandelwa kokuxhumana okunamandla, imikhawulo yokuhamba engenayo, ukuhlolwa, nokuhlukaniswa kwabantu, kepha ngokuvalwa okuqinile, njenge-Iceland neNingizimu Korea.
Ucwaningo lwezibalo luthole ukuthi amazwe aye ahlolwe kakhulu, maqondana nenani labantu abafa, anezinga eliphansi kakhulu lokufa, mhlawumbe ngoba la mazwe akwazi kangcono ukuthola labo abanezimpawu ezilula kuphela noma ezingenayo.
I-WHO incoma ukuthi amazwe angenakho ukuhlolwa kanye namalebhu kazwelonke anolwazi oluncane nge-COVID-19 athumele amasampula awo okuqala amahlanu amahle kanye namashumi ayishumi amabi e-COVID-19 kwelinye lamalebhu ayi-16 okuhlolwa kwe-WHO ukuze kuqinisekiswe.
Kula mabhethri angu-16 okucwaninga, angu-7 ase-Asia, angu-5 eYurophu, amabili e-Afrika, owodwa eNyakatho Melika nowodwa e-Australia.
Esithombeni esilandelayo, ikholomu Ehle njenge-% yokuhlolwa ithonywa inqubomgomo yokuhlola yezwe.
Izwe elihlola kuphela abantu abangene ezibhedlela liyoba nephesenti eliphakeme lokuhlola elifanele kunelizwe elihlola bonke abantu, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi babonisa izimpawu noma cha, ezinye izinto zifana.
Ukugeza izandla, okubizwa nangokuthi ukuhlanzeka kwezandla, kuwukuhlanza izandla ngenjongo yokususa inhlabathi, amafutha, izinambuzane noma ezinye izinto ezingadingeki.
"Ukugeza izandla ngensipho njalo ngesikhathi esithile "sezikhathi ezibucayi" emini kuvimbela ukusabalala kwezifo eziningi, isibonelo isifo sohudo kanye ne-cholera, ezithathelwana ngomlomo".
Abantu bangagula nezifo zokuphefumula ezifana nomkhuhlane noma umkhuhlane, ngokwesibonelo, uma bengazihlambi izandla ngaphambi kokuthinta amehlo, impumulo noma umlomo (okungukuthi, izembozo zomzimba).
Izikhathi ezinhlanu ezibalulekile zosuku lapho kubalulekile khona ukugeza izandla ngensipho zihlanganisa: ngaphambi nangemva kokukhishwa kwesisu, ngemva kokuhlanza phansi kwengane noma ukushintsha izinsimbi, ngaphambi kokondla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi nangemva kokulungiselela ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama, inhlanzi noma izinyoni ezingasetshenziswa.
Uma kungekho manzi nensipho, izandla zingase zihlanzwe ngomlotha. I-World Health Organization incoma ukugeza izandla:
Ngaphambi, ngesikhathi nangemva kokulungiselela ukudla.
Ngaphambi nangemva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ngemva kokushintsha amademoni noma ukuhlanza ingane eseyisebenzise indlu yangasese.
Ngemva kokuphefumula, ukukhwehlela noma ukuqhuma.
Ngemva kokuthinta izilwane, ukudla kwezilwane noma imfucuza yezilwane.
Ukuhlanzeka kwezandla kwezokwelapha kubhekisela emikhubeni yokuhlanzeka ehlobene nezinqubo zezokwelapha.
Ukugeza izandla ngaphambi kokunikeza imithi noma ukunakekelwa kwezokwelapha kungavimbela noma kunciphise ukusabalala kwesifo.
Injongo eyinhloko yezokwelapha yokuwasha izandla ukuhlanza izandla ezigulini eziwubhadane (amabhaktheriya, amagciwane, noma ezinye izidalwa ezincane ezingabangela izifo) namakhemikhali angabangela ukulimala noma izifo.
Lokhu kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abaphatha ukudla noma abasebenza emkhakheni wezokwelapha, kodwa futhi kuyinkambo ebalulekile emphakathini jikelele.
Ukugeza izandla kunezinzuzo eziningi empilweni, kuhlanganise nokunciphisa ukusakazeka komkhuhlane, i-coronavirus nezinye izifo ezithathelwanayo; ukuvimbela izimbangela ezithathelwanayo zesifo sohudo; ukunciphisa ukutheleleka komoya;
nokunciphisa izinga lokufa kwezingane lapho kuzalwa ekhaya.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-2013 lwabonisa ukuthi ukuthuthukisa imikhuba yokuwasha izandla kungaholela ekuthuthukisweni okuncane kokukhula kobude bezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu ubudala.
Emazweni asathuthuka, izinga lokufa kwezingane ezihlobene nezifo zokuphefumula nezomathambo lingancipha ngokuletha izinguquko eziqondile zokuziphatha, njengokuwasha izandla ngensipho.
Lesi senzo esilula singanciphisa izinga lokufa ngenxa yalezi zifo cishe ngo-50%.
Ukungenelela okukhuthaza ukugeza izandla kunganciphisa izenzakalo zokuhlanza ngesinye ingxenye yesithathu, futhi lokhu kufana nokuhlinzeka ngamanzi ahlanzekile ezindaweni ezinemali ephansi.
Ukwehliswa okungama-48% kwezigameko zokuquleka kungahlotshaniswa nokuwasha izandla ngensipho. Ukugeza izandla ngensipho kuyindlela eyodwa esebenza kahle futhi engabizi kakhulu yokuvimbela isifo sokuquleka nezifo ezibangelwa ukuphefumula (ARI), njengoba ukuziphatha okuzenzakalelayo kwenziwa emakhaya, ezikoleni nasemiphakathi emhlabeni wonke.
Isifo samaphaphu, okuyi-ARI enkulu, siyimbangela eyinhloko yokufa kwezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu ubudala, kubulala izingane ezicishe zibe yizigidi ezingu - 1,8 ngonyaka.
Ukudla umlomo kanye nesifo samaphaphu ndawonye kuholela ekufeni kwezingane okucishe kube izigidi ezingu-3.5 unyaka ngamunye.
Ngokusho kwe-UNICEF, ukugeza izandla ngensipho ngaphambi kokudla nangemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese kuyisiko elisemthonjeni kungasindisa ukuphila kwabantu abaningi kunanoma imuphi umuthi wokugoma noma ukungenelela kwezokwelapha, kunciphise ukufa ngenxa yesifo sohudo cishe ngesigamu nokufa ngenxa yezifo ezibangelwa imijikelezo yokuphefumula.
Ukugeza izandla ngokuvamile kuhlanganiswa nezinye izindlela zokungenela ezenzelwe ukunakekela inhlanzeko njengengxenye yohlelo lwamanzi, inhlanzeko nenhlanzeko (WASH).
Ukugeza izandla kuvikela futhi ekudlulisweni kwe-impetigo ngokuthintana nomzimba okuqondile.
Umphumela omncane omubi wokuwasha izandla ukuthi ukugeza izandla kaningi kungaholela ekulimaleni kwesikhumba ngenxa yokoma kwesikhumba.
Ucwaningo olwenziwe eDenmark ngo-2012 lwathola ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngokweqile kungaholela esimweni sesikhumba esibuhlungu nesinamabala esibizwa ngokuthi i-eczema yezandla noma i-dermatitis yezandla, okuyinto evamile kakhulu phakathi kwabasebenzi bezempilo.
Ukugeza izandla kaningi kakhulu kubonakala njengenye yezimpawu zokugula okungalindelekile.
Kunezikhathi ezinhlanu ezibalulekile ngosuku lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile ukuze kuncishiswe ukudluliselwa kwesifo ngomlomo: ngemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese (ukukhishwa komchamo, ukuhlanza izicubu), ngemva kokuhlanza phansi kwengane (ukuguqula izinsimbi), ngaphambi kokudla, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi/emva kokulungiselela ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi noma inyoni.
Ezinye izikhathi lapho kufanele kusetshenziswe khona indlela efanele yokuwasha izandla ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa kwesifo zihlanganisa ngaphambi nangemva kokwelapha isicupho noma isilonda; ngemva kokukhwehlela, ukukhwehlela noma ukuphefumula; ngemva kokuthinta imfucuza yezilwane noma ukuphathwa kwezilwane; nangemva kokuthinta udoti.
Emazweni amaningi, abantu abavamile ukugeza izandla ngensipho.
Ucwaningo lokuwasha izandla emazweni angu-54 ngo-2015 luthole ukuthi ngokwesilinganiso, amaphesenti angu-38.7% emakhaya ayegeza izandla ngensipho. Ucwaningo lwango-2014 lwabonisa ukuthi i-Saudi Arabia yayinamazinga aphezulu angama-97%, i-United States eduze naphakathi ngama-77%, neChina enamazinga aphansi kakhulu angama-23%.
"Uhlelo Lokunakekelwa Kwezempilo Okubalulekile" olusetshenziswa uMnyango Wezemfundo ePhilippines luyisibonelo sesenzo esisemkhakheni wokuthuthukisa impilo nemfundo yezingane".
Ukubulala izinambuzane kabili ngonyaka, kanye nokugeza izandla nsuku zonke ngensipho, ukugeza amazinyo nsuku zonke nge-fluoride, kuyisihluthulelo sale nqubo kazwelonke.
Kuye kwaqaliswa ngempumelelo nase-Indonesia.
Ukususwa kwezinambuzane esikhumbeni kuthuthukiswa ngokungezwa kwensipho noma izidakamizwa zokuwasha emanzini.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko wensipho nezinto zokuwasha ukuqedela izithiyo zokunciphisa isisombululo nokwandisa ukuncibilika.
Amanzi wona awusebenzi kahle ekuhlanzeni isikhumba ngoba amafutha namaprotheni, okuyizinto ezihlanganiswa nenhlabathi ehlukahlukene, awacinywanga kalula emanzini.
Nokho, ukuhlanza kusizwa ukugeleza kwamanzi okunengqondo.
Isabha eqinile, ngenxa yokuthi ingasetshenziswa kabusha, ingaqukatha amabhaktheriya atholakala ekusetshenzisweni kwangaphambilini.
Ucwaningo oluncane olwenziwe ngokudluliselwa kwamagciwane kusuka esabelweni esinamandla esonakele luye lwaphetha ngokuthi ukudluliselwa akunakwenzeka njengoba amagciwane egeza nge-foam.
"I-CDC isathi ""isabuni esinochungechunge esinokulawula okungekho izandla zokuphatha kuyathandwa kakhulu"."
Izinsipho zokulwa namagciwane ziye zathuthukiswa kakhulu ukuze zikhuthaze abantu ukuba bazi ukuthi bayaphila kanjani.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi ukusebenzisa izidakamizwa zokulwa nezifo noma izinto zokubulala amagciwane ezinconywayo kukhetha izinambuzane eziphikisana nama-antibiotic emvelweni.
Nokho, insipho elwa namagciwane iqukethe izidakamizwa ezivamile ezilwa namagciwane ezifana ne-triclosan, enohlu oluningi lwezinhlobo eziphikisayo zezinto eziphilayo.
Ngakho, ngisho noma izinhlobo eziphikisana nama-antibiotic zingakhethwa ngensipho elwa namagciwane, zingase zingabi nempumelelo njengoba zikhishwa emakethe.
Ngaphandle kwe-surfactant ne-agent yokuvikela isikhumba, ama-formula ahlanzekile angahlanganisa ama-acids (i-acetic acid, i-ascorbic acid, i-lactic acid) njenge-pH regulator, i-benzoic acid esebenzayo ngokumelene namagciwane kanye nezinye izithasiselo zesikhumba (i-aloe vera, amavithamini, i-menthol, izithasiselo zezitshalo).Ukuhlaziywa okuphelele okuvela e-University of Oregon School of Public Health kwabonisa ukuthi amasephu alulayo asebenza kahle njengamasephu alulayo aqukethe ama-antibacterial aqukethe i-triclosan ekuvimbeleni izifo nasekususeni amabhaktheriya ezandleni.
Amanzi ashisayo akulungele ukugeza izandla awashisi ngokwanele ukuba abulale amabhaktheriya.
Amabhaktheriya akhula ngokushesha okukhulu ekushiseni komzimba (37 °C).
Nokho, amanzi afudumele anensipho ayasebenza kangcono kunamanzi abandayo anensipho ekususeni amafutha emvelo agcina inhlabathi namagciwane.
Nokho, ngokuphambene nenkolelo evamile, izifundo zesayensi ziye zabonisa ukuthi ukusebenzisa amanzi afudumele akunamphumela ekunciphiseni umthwalo wamagciwane ezandleni.
Isisusa-gazi sezandla noma i-antiseptic yezandla iyinsiza yokuhlanzeka kwezandla engekho emanzini.
Ngasekupheleni kwawo-1990 nasekuqaleni kwekhulu lama-21, utshwala obuthambisa izandla obungaxhunyiwe emanzini (owaziwa nangokuthi ama-hand rubs, ama-anti-septic hand rubs, noma ama-hand sanitizer) baqala ukuthandwa.
Iningi lawo lisuselwa ku-isopropyl alcohol noma ethanol elenziwe ndawonye ne-agent yokuqina njenge-Carbomer (i-polymer ye-acrylic acid) ibe yigeli, noma i-humictant efana ne-glycerin ibe uketshezi, noma i-foam ukuze kube lula ukuyisebenzisa futhi kunciphise umphumela wokomisa wotshwala.
Ukwengeza i-hydrogen-peroxide eyancibilika kukhulisa ngokwengeziwe umsebenzi wokulwa namagciwane. Izithambisi zokuhlanza izandla eziqukethe okungenani u-60 kuya ku-95% wotshwala ziyi-germkillers esebenza kahle.
Izithambisi zokugeza utshwala zibulala amabhaktheriya, amabhaktheriya angakwazi ukugwema izidakamizwa eziningi (i-MRSA ne-VRE), isifo sofuba, namanye amagciwane (kuhlanganise ne-HIV, i-herpes, i-RSV, i-rhinovirus, imithi yokugoma, umkhuhlane, ne-hepatitis) kanye namakhowe.
Ama-drop sanitizer aqukethe utshwala angama-70% abulala ama-99.97% (ukunciphisa i-log ka-3.5, okufana nokunciphisa i-decibel ka-35) wamagciwane ezandleni ngemva kwemizuzwana engama-30 ngemuva kokufakwa kanye nama-99.99% kuya ku-99.999% (ukunciphisa i-log ka-4 kuya kwengu-5) wamagciwane ezandleni ngemva kwemizuzu engu-1 ngemuva kokufakwa.Ama-drop sanitizer asezandleni asebenza kakhulu ngokumelene namagciwane futhi asebenza kancane ngokumelene namagciwane athile.
Izidakamizwa zokuhlanza izandla ezisekelwe kotshwala cishe azisebenzi ngokuphelele ngokumelene namagciwane ohlobo lwe-norovirus (noma i-Norwalk), imbangela evame kakhulu yokutheleleka kwe-gastroenteritis. Kumelwe kusetshenziswe izidakamizwa ezanele zokulwa nokubulala izinambuzane noma ukucwiliswa kotshwala ezandleni ukuze kuthungwe kahle noma kuhlanganiswe izandla zombili.
Izandla zangaphambili nezingemuva, phakathi nezingxenye zeminwe zonke ziyahlanzwa cishe imizuzwana engama-30 kuze kube yilapho uketshezi, i-foam noma i-gel isomile.
Izingalo kufanele zihlanzwe kahle, zixhunywe ezandleni zombili. Isikhungo Sase-US Sokulawula Nokuvimbela Izifo sincoma ukugeza izandla ngaphezu kwezingalo ezikhishwayo, ikakhulukazi lapho izandla zingcolile.
Ukusetshenziswa okwandayo kwalezi zinto kusekelwe ekusebenziseni kwazo kalula nasekusebenzeni kwazo ngokushesha ekubulaleni ama-microorganisms; kodwa akufanele kusebenze njengendawo yokuwasha izandla ngendlela efanele ngaphandle kokuthi kutholakale isephu namanzi.
Ukusetshenziswa okuvamile kwama-hand sanitizer anotshwala kungabangela isikhumba esomile ngaphandle kokuthi kufakwe izithasiselo zokuthambisa kanye/noma ama-humidifiers esikhumba.
Umphumela wokomisa kotshwala ungancishiswa noma uqedwe ngokungeza i-glycerin kanye/noma ezinye izithako zokuthambisa kumanyathelo.
Ezikhathini zokuhlolwa komtholampilo, izidakamizwa zokuhlanza izandla ezisekelwe otshwaleni eziqukethe izinto ezenza kube mnandi zabangela ukucasuka kwesikhumba nokoma kancane kunama-soap noma izidakamizwa zokuhlanza amagciwane.
Ukugqwala okuphathelene nokuxhumana, i- contact urticaria syndrome noma ukuzwela ngokweqile kotshwala noma izithasiselo ezitholakala kuma-rubs ezandla ezidakayo akuvamile ukuba khona.
Ukuthambekela okuphansi ekubangeleni i-dermatitis yokuxhumana ecasulayo kwaba yinto ekhangayo uma kuqhathaniswa nokugeza izandla ngensipho namanzi.
Naphezu kokusebenza kwawo, izinto ezingekho emanzini azihlanzi izandla ngezinto eziphilayo, kodwa zivele zizibulale.
Yingakho izidakamizwa zokuhlanza izandla zingasebenzi kahle njengensipho namanzi ekuvimbeleni ukusabalala kwezifo eziningi, ngoba lezi zifo zisahlala ezandleni.
Ukusebenza kwe-drug-free hand sanitizer kuncike kakhulu ezakhiweni nasekwakhiweni kwayo, futhi ngokomlando kunomsebenzi omncane kakhulu kotshwala nokuthambisa utshwala.
Muva nje, ama-formulas asebenzisa i-benzalkonium chloride aboniswe ukuthi anomsebenzi oqhubekayo futhi ohlanganisiwe wokulwa namagciwane ngemuva kokufakwa, ngokungafani notshwala, okuye kwaboniswa ukuthi kunciphisa ukusebenza kwayo ngemuva kokusetshenziswa okuphindaphindiwe, cishe ngenxa yemiphumela emibi yesikhumba ehamba phambili.
Abantu abaningi abahlala emphakathini onezimali ezincane abakwazi ukukhokhela insipho futhi esikhundleni salokho basebenzisa umlotha noma inhlabathi.
Umlotha noma inhlabathi kungase kusebenze kangcono kunamanzi wodwa, kodwa kungase kungasebenzi kangako kunensipho.
Esinye isizathu sokukhathazeka ukuthi uma inhlabathi noma umlotha ungcoliswe amagciwane, kungase kwandise ukusabalala kwezifo kunokuba kunciphise.
Njengensipho, umlotha nawo uyisibulala-magciwane ngoba uma uthinta amanzi, uveza isixazululo esishisayo.
I-WHO yancoma umlotha noma isihlabathi njengendawo yesephu uma isephu ingekho.
Indlela efanele yokuwasha izandla enconyiwe yi-US Centers for Disease Control ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa kwesifo ifaka phakathi lezi zinyathelo ezilandelayo:
Izandla ezimanzi ngamanzi afudumele noma abandayo.
Kunconywa ukuba kube namanzi agelezayo ngoba izikhwama eziphakama zingaba zingcolile, kuyilapho izinga lokushisa lamanzi kubonakala lingenzi umehluko.
Ukugcoba izandla ngokuzihlunga ngensipho eningi, kuhlanganise nomhlane wezandla, phakathi kweminwe, nangaphansi kwezipikili.
Isabha ivimbela amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ucwaningo lubonisa ukuthi abantu bavame ukugeza izandla zabo ngokucophelela lapho kusetshenziswa isephu kunamanzi kuphela.
Hlanza okungenani imizuzwana engu-20.
Ukugcoba kudala ukuhlangana, okusiza ekususeni amagciwane esikhumbeni, futhi ukugcoba isikhathi eside kuletha amagciwane amaningi.
Hlanza kahle ngaphansi kwamanzi agelezayo.
Ukugeza emgodini kungangcolisa izandla.
Yomisa ngethuluzi elihlanzekile noma uvumele umoya ukuba womise.
Izandla ezimanzi nezimanzi zingase zingcoliswe kalula. Izindawo ezivame kakhulu ukulahleka yizinyonga, izinsimbi, izindawo eziphakathi kweminwe, nezingaphansi kwezipikili.
Izikhonkwane ezenziwe ngomshini kanye ne-chip nail polish zingaba nezingqimba ezincane.
Ngokuvamile kunconywa i-lotion enomswakama ukuze izandla zingagqwali; isikhumba esomile singabangela ukulimala kwesikhumba okungase kwandise ingozi yokudluliselwa kwesifo.
