Livela embhalweni weBhayibheli kaMathewu lapho uPontiyu Pilatu ahlanza khona izandla zakhe kunqume ukubethela uJesu Kristu esiphambanweni, kodwa seliye laba yigama elisetshenziswa kabanzi kakhulu kwamanye amphakathi esiNgisi.
ENcwadini kaShakespeare iMacbeth, uLady Macbeth uqala ukugeza izandla zakhe ngenkani emzamweni wokuhlanza ibala elicatshangelwe, emelela unembeza wakhe onecala maqondana nobugebengu ayebenzile futhi wabangela umyeni wakhe ukuba enze.
Kuye kwatholakala nokuthi abantu, ngemva kokukhumbula noma ukucabanga ngezenzo ezingenabuKristu, bavame ukugeza izandla kaningi kunabanye, futhi bavame ukubheka imishini yokuwasha izandla njengento eyigugu kakhulu.
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, labo abavunyelwe ukugeza izandla zabo ngemva kokubheka okunjalo mancane amathuba okuba bahlanganyele kwezinye izenzo zokubuyisela "ukuhlanza", njengokuzithandela".
