Ukulawulwa kwengozi emsebenzini ngenxa ye-COVID-19
Ukulawulwa kwengozi emsebenzini ye-COVID-19 ukufaka isicelo semethodoloji yokuphepha kwezempilo nokusebenza kwezingozi zokuvikela isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ukulawulwa okufanele kwengozi emsebenzini kuxhomeke emsebenzini kanye nomsebenzi, ngokusekelwe ekuhloleni ubungozi bemithombo yokuchayeka, ubukhulu besifo emphakathini, kanye nezimbangela zobungozi zabasebenzi ngabanye abangase babe sengozini yokungenwa yi-COVID-19.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane bokuchayeka emsebenzini inokuxhumana okuncane emsebenzini nomphakathi nabanye osebenza nabo, okuyinto enconyelwayo ukuthi yenziwe ukuze kuvinjelwe ukutheleleka, kuhlanganise nokuwasha izandla, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, isimilo sokuphefumula, nokugcina indawo yokusebenza ihlanzekile futhi igcwele izifo.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi ihlanganisa leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa nge-COVID-19, kodwa abangase batheleleke ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo noma ukuhamba kwamanye amazwe.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengasesikoleni, ezindaweni zokusebenza ezinobuningi obukhulu babantu, kanye nezinye izindawo zokuthengisa ezinobukhulu obukhulu.
Ukulawulwa kwengozi yaleli qembu, ngaphezu kwezinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, kufaka phakathi ukuphefumula usebenzisa izihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle, iziqaphi zokuqhuma, kanye nokuba nemishini yokuzivikela yomuntu siqu etholakalayo uma umuntu one-COVID-19 etholakala.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi bezempilo nabasebenza ezindaweni zokuhlinza abantu abachayeke kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo ukuthi une-COVID-19 njengobungozi obukhulu bokuthi bathole izinto ezibonakalayo, okuyinto eyandisa ibe yingozi enkulu kakhulu uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma bephatha amasampula kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo ukuthi une-COVID-19.
Ukulawulwa kwengozi okufanelekayo kwabasebenzi kuhlanganisa ukulawula kwezobunjiniyela njengamakamelo okuphefumula ngaphansi kwengcindezi engalungile, nemishini yokuzivikela yomuntu siqu efanele umsebenzi.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kungaba nemiphumela eminingi emsebenzini.
Izisebenzi zingase zingayi emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula, isidingo sokunakekela abanye, noma ngenxa yokwesaba ukuchayeka.
Amaphethini okuhweba angashintsha, kokubili ngokuya ngokuthi yiziphi izimpahla ezifunwa, nezindlela zokuthola lezi zinto (njengokuthenga ngaphandle kwehora eliphakeme noma ngezinsizakalo zokulethwa noma zokuhamba).
Ekugcineni, ukuthuthwa kwezinto ezivela ezindaweni ezihlushwa kakhulu yi-COVID-19 kungaphazanyiswa.Uhlelo lokulungela izifo ezithathelwanayo kanye nolwempendulo lungasetshenziswa ukuqondisa izenzo zokuvikela.
Izinhlelo zihlanganisa izinga lobungozi elihlobene nezindawo ezahlukene zokusebenza nemisebenzi yomsebenzi, kuhlanganise nemithombo yokuchayeka, izici zobungozi ezivela ekhaya nasemphakathini, kanye nezimbangela zobungozi zabasebenzi ngabanye ezifana nobudala noma izimo zempilo ezingapheli.
Zibonisa futhi ukulawula okudingekayo ukuze kuxazululwe lezo zingozi, kanye nezinhlelo eziphuthumayo zezenzakalo ezingaba khona ngenxa yokuqubuka.
Izinhlelo zokulungiselela izifo ezithathelwanayo kanye nezindlela zokuphendula zingaphansi kwezincomo zikazwelonke noma ezingaphansi kukazwelonke.
Izinhloso zokuphendula ekuqubukeni zihlanganisa ukunciphisa ukudluliselwa phakathi kwabasebenzi, ukuvikela abantu abasengozini enkulu yezinkinga zempilo ezingathandeki, ukugcina imisebenzi yebhizinisi, nokunciphisa imiphumela engathandeki kwamanye ama-entities kumaketanga abo okuhlinzeka.
Ububi besifo emphakathini lapho ibhizinisi likhona buthinta izimpendulo ezithathiwe.
I-hierarchy yokulawula izingozi yisikhungo esisetshenziswa kabanzi ekuphepheni nasempilweni emsebenzini ukuhlukanisa ukulawula izingozi ngokusebenza kahle.
Lapho ingozi ye-COVID-19 ingeke iqedwe khona, ukulawula okusebenzayo kakhulu ukulawula ubuchwepheshe, okulandelwa ukulawula kokuphatha, futhi ekugcineni imishini yokuzivikela yomuntu siqu.
Ukulawulwa kwezobunjiniyela kuhilela ukuhlukanisa abasebenzi ezingozini ezihlobene nomsebenzi ngaphandle kokuncika ekuziphatheni kwabasebenzi, futhi kungaba yisixazululo esingasetshenziswa kakhulu.
Ukulawulwa kokuphatha yizinguquko zenqubomgomo noma izinqubo zomsebenzi ezidinga isenzo somsebenzi noma somqashi.
Imishini yokuzivikela yomuntu siqu (PPE) ibhekwa njengengasebenzi kahle kunezindlela zokuphatha nezobuchwepheshe, kodwa ingasiza ekuvimbeleni ukuchayeka okuthile.
Zonke izinhlobo ze-PPE kufanele zikhethwe ngokuya ngengozi ezikuyo isisebenzi, zifakwe kahle njengoba kufanelekile (isb. iziphepho zokuphefumula), zigqoke kahle futhi ngendlela efanele, zihlolwe njalo, zigcinwe futhi zishintshwe, njengoba kudingeka, futhi zisuswe kahle, zihlanzwe futhi zigcinwe noma zilahlwe ukuze kugwenywe ukungcola.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane bokuchayeka emsebenzini inokuxhumana okuncane emsebenzini nomphakathi nabanye osebenza nabo.
Izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka ezinconywa kuzo zonke izindawo zokusebenza zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla njalo nokuzikhandla, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, isimilo sokuphefumula kuhlanganise nokukhwehlela nokudonsa, ukuhlinzeka ngezindwangu nemithombo yokulahla udoti, ukulungiselela ukusebenza kude noma ukusebenza ngamasheya uma kunesidingo, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bangasebenzisi amathuluzi nemishini yabanye, nokugcina ukuhlanzwa nokubulala amagciwane okujwayelekile kwemvelo yokusebenza.
Ukuhlonza ngokushesha nokuhlukanisa abantu abangase batheleleke kuyisinyathelo esibalulekile ekuvikeleni abasebenzi, amakhasimende, izivakashi nabanye emsebenzini.
Izikhungo Zokulawula Nokuvimbela Izifo Zase-U.S. (CDC) zincoma ukuthi abasebenzi abanezimpawu zesifo esibucayi sokuphefumula bahlale ekhaya baze bangabi nalutho, izimpawu zokushisa, nanoma yiziphi ezinye izimpawu okungenani amahora angu-24 ngaphandle kokusebenzisa imithi yokunciphisa umkhuhlane noma eminye imithi eguqula izimpawu, nokuthi izinqubomgomo zekhefu lokugula ziyanyuka, zivumele abasebenzi bahlale ekhaya ukuze banakekele ilungu lomkhaya ogulayo, nokuthi abasebenzi bayazazi lezi zinqubomgomo.
Ngokusho kwe-OSHA, imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi ihlanganisa leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma eduze ngaphakathi kwamamitha ayisithupha (1.8 m) nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ukuthi baneziguli ze-COVID-19, kodwa abangase babe nesifo se-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo endaweni yebhizinisi, noma ngoba umuntu usanda kuhamba emazweni angaphandle endaweni ene-COVID-19 edluliselwe kabanzi.
