Abasebenzi abakuleli qembu eliyingozi akuvamile ukuba badinge ukusebenzisa izinsimbi zokuphefumula.
Uma umuntu egula endizeni, ukulawula okufanele ukuvikela abasebenzi nabanye abagibeli kuhlanganisa ukuhlukanisa umuntu ogulayo nabanye ngamakhilomitha angu-6, ukhetha ilungu elilodwa lomsebenzi wokusiza umuntu ogulayo, nokunikeza umuntu ogulayo imaski yobuso noma ukucela umuntu ogulayo ukuba amboze umlomo wakhe nenhloko ngezindwangu lapho ekhwehlela noma eqhuma.
Abasebenzi base-cabin kufanele bagqoke amagilavu ezokwelapha alahlwayo lapho begcina umhambi ogulayo noma lapho bethinta uketshezi lomzimba noma izindawo ezingase zingcoliswe, futhi mhlawumbe babe nemishini eyengeziwe yokuzivikela uma umhambi ogulayo enokushisa, ekhwehlela njalo noma enenkinga yokuphefumula.
Amagilavu nezinye izinto ezilahlwayo kufanele zilahlwe esikhwameni sezingozi eziphilayo, futhi izindawo ezingcolisiwe kufanele zihlanzwe futhi zihlatshwe izifo ngemuva kwalokho. Ezokuhamba ngomkhumbi kwezohwebo, kuhlanganise nezikebhe zokukhwela nezinye izitsha, ukulawula izingozi kuhlanganisa ukuhlehlisa uhambo uma ugula, nokuzihlukanisa kanye nokuzisa isikhungo sezokwelapha esikebheni ngokushesha uma umuntu eba nomkhuhlane noma ezinye izimpawu ngenkathi ebhodini.
Ngokufanelekile, ukulandelela kwezokwelapha kufanele kwenzeke ekamelweni lomuntu ohlukanisiwe.Ezikoleni nasezikhungweni zokunakekela izingane, i-CDC incoma ukuvala okwesikhashana ukuze kuhlanzwe noma kubulawe uma umuntu onegciwane esezakhe isikole kungakhathalekile ukuthi umphakathi usakazeke kanjani.
Lapho kunokudluliselwa komphakathi okuncane kuya kokulinganisela, kungenziwa amasu okuhlukanisa abantu emphakathini njengokukhansela uhambo lwasensimini, imihlangano neminye imihlangano emikhulu efana nokuqeqeshwa ngokomzimba noma amakilasi ekwaya noma ukudla endaweni yokudlela, ukwandisa isikhala phakathi kwedeski, izikhathi eziphazamisayo zokufika nokuxoshwa, ukunciphisa izivakashi ezingadingekile, nokusebenzisa indawo ehlukile yehhovisi lezempilo yezingane ezinemiphumela efana nomkhuhlane.
Lapho kunokudluliselwa okukhulu emphakathini wasendaweni, ngaphezu kwamasu okuhlukanisa abantu, kungacatshangelwa ukudedelwa esikoleni isikhathi eside.Kubasebenzi bezomthetho abenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke, ubungozi bezempilo obusheshayo bubhekwa njengephansi yi-CDC.
Izikhulu zomthetho okufanele zithintane nabantu abaqinisekisiwe noma abasolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19 zinconywa ukuba zilandele iziqondiso ezifanayo nezobuchwepheshe bezokwelapha bezimo eziphuthumayo, kufaka phakathi imishini efanele yokuzivikela.
Uma kwenzeka kuhlangana eduze ngesikhathi sokuboshwa, abasebenzi kufanele bahlanze futhi babulale amagciwane amabhande nemishini yabo yomsebenzi ngaphambi kokuba baphinde basebenzise i-spray yokuhlanza yasendlini noma i-wipe, futhi balandele izindlela ezijwayelekile zokusebenza zokuvimbela nokulahla i-PPE esetshenzisiwe kanye nokuvimbela nokuhlanza izingubo.
I-OSHA ibheka abasebenzi abathile bezempilo nabasebenza ezindaweni zokuhlinza izidumbu njengezigaba eziphakeme noma eziphakeme kakhulu zobungozi bokugqashuka.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obukhulu ihlanganisa ukuhlinzekwa kwezempilo, ukwesekwa, abasebenzi baselebhu, kanye nabasebenzi bezokuthutha bezokwelapha abachayeka ezigulini ezaziwayo noma ezisola nge-COVID-19.
Lezi ziba ingozi enkulu kakhulu uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma baphathe amasampula ezigulini ze-COVID-19 ezaziwayo noma ezisolayo.
Izinqubo zokwenza i-aerosol zihlanganisa ukufakwa kwe-tube, izinqubo zokukhishwa kokukhwehlela, ama-bronchoscopes, ezinye izinqubo zokuxilonga amazinyo nokuhlolwa, noma ukuqoqwa kwesampula okuhlaselayo.
Imisebenzi yezindawo zokuhlinza izidumbu enesibopho esiphakeme ihlanganisa abasebenzi abahilelekile ekulungiseleleni izidumbu zabantu ababenamacala aziwayo noma asolisayo e-COVID-19 ngesikhathi sokushona kwabo; laba baba yingozi enkulu kakhulu uma benza ukuhlolwa.Ukulawulwa okungeziwe kobunjiniyela kwala maqembu obungozi kufaka phakathi amakamelo okuhlukanisa iziguli ezine-COVID-19 eyaziwayo noma esolisayo, kuhlanganise nalapho kwenziwa izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
Ukuphefumula okuqondile okuqondile kungase kube okufanele kwezinye izindawo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo nezingcwaba.
Amasampula kufanele aphathwe ngezinyathelo zokuqapha ze- Biosafety Level 3.
I-World Health Organization (WHO) incoma ukuthi iziguli ezizayo zihlukaniswe zibe izindawo ezihlukile zokulinda kuye ngokuthi ngabe zisolwa yini nge-COVID-19. Ngaphezu kwezinye izinto zokuphepha, i-OSHA incoma ukuthi kusetshenziswe iziphepho kulabo abasebenza ngaphakathi kwamamitha ayisithupha ezigulini ezaziwa ukuthi zine-SARS-CoV-2, nalabo abenza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
E-United States, izihlungi zokuphefumula ezihlunga ubuso ezihlunga i-N95 ezivunyelwe yi-NIOSH noma ezingcono kufanele zisetshenziswe kumongo wohlelo oluphelele, olubhaliwe lokuvikela ukuphefumula oluhlanganisa ukuhlolwa kokulingana, ukuqeqeshwa nokuhlolwa kwezokwelapha.
Ezinye izinhlobo zezinto zokuphefumula zingahlinzeka ngokuvikelwa okukhulu nokuthuthukisa induduzo yabasebenzi. I-WHO ayincomi izembozo, njengoba i-COVID-19 iyisifo sokuphefumula kunokuba idluliselwe ngamanzi omzimba.
I-WHO incoma kuphela imaski yokuhlolwa okuhlinzwayo kubasebenzi abahlolwayo lapho bengena khona.
Kulabo abaqoqa amasampula okuphefumula ezigulini ze-COVID-19 ngaphandle kokwenza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, abanakekelayo noma abahamba nazo, i-WHO incoma ukuthi kuhlolwe imaski yokuhlinzwa, izibuko, noma isivikelo sobuso, ingubo, namagilavu.
Uma kwenziwa inqubo yokwakha i-aerosol, imaski yokuhlinzwa iyashintshwa ngesiphefumuli se-N95 noma se-FFP2.
Njengoba ukunikezwa kwe-PPE emhlabeni wonke kunganele, i-WHO incoma ukuthi kuncishiswe isidingo se-PPE ngokusebenzisa imithi ye-telemedicine, izithiyo zomzimba ezinjengewindi elivulekile, ukuvumela kuphela labo ababandakanyekayo ekunakekelweni okuqondile ukungena egumbini nesiguli se-COVID-19, besebenzisa kuphela i-PPE edingekayo emsebenzini othile, beqhubeka nokusebenzisa i-respirator efanayo ngaphandle kokuyisusa ngenkathi bekhathalela iziguli eziningi ezinesifo esifanayo, beqapha futhi bexhumanisa uchungechunge lokuhlinzekwa kwe-PPE, futhi beqeda ukusetshenziswa kwemaski kubantu abangenazimpawu.
