b' I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) iyi-enzyme eboshwe endaweni yangaphandle (izingqimba zamaseli) zamaseli emaphashini, emithambo yegazi, enhliziyweni, ezinso nasemizimbeni.
I-ACE2 iphikisana nomsebenzi we-angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ehlobene nayo ngokunciphisa inani le-angiotensin-II nokwandisa i-Ang(1-7) okwenza kube umuthi othembisa kakhulu wokwelapha izifo zenhliziyo. I-ACE2 iphinde isebenze njengendawo yokungena kumaseli e-coronavirus athile.
Inguqulo yomuntu ye-enzyme ivame ukubizwa ngokuthi hACE2.
I-angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 iyinhlanganisela ye-zinc equkethe i-metalloenzyme etholakala ebusweni bamaseli ase-endothelial nakwezinye izakhi.
I-ACE2 protein iqukethe i-N-terminal peptidase M2 domain ne-C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
I-ACE2 iyiprotheni ye-membrane yohlobo I yokudlula okukodwa, ene-enzymatically active domain yayo evezwe ebusweni bamaseli emaphashini nakwezinye izicubu.
Isizinda se-ACE2 esingaphandle kweseli sihlukaniswa nesizinda se-transmembrane enye i-enzyme eyaziwa ngokuthi i-sheddase, futhi amaprotheni ancibilika akhiqizwa akhululwa emthonjeni wegazi futhi ekugcineni akhishwe emchameni.
I-ACE2 itholakala ezigabeni eziningi: I-ACE2 iboshwe emlonyeni wamangqamuzana ikakhulukazi wamangqamuzana omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omncane, ama-enterocytes emathunjini amancane, amangqamuzana omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omncane kanye nemisipha emincane yomzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omzimba omningi.
Ukuvezwa kwe-ACE2 mRNA kutholakala nase-cerebral cortex, i-striatum, i-hypothalamus, kanye nesiqu somqondo.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko we-ACE2 ukwenza umsebenzi wokulinganisa i-ACE.
I-ACE ihlukanisa i-angiotensin I hormone ibe yi-angiotensin II ecindezela imithambo.
I-ACE2 ngokwayo ihlukanisa i-carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine kusuka ku-angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) futhi iyidlulise ibe i-angiotensin ye-vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
I-ACE2 ingabuye ihlukanise ezinye ama-peptide amaningi kuhlanganise ne- [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, i-apelin, i-neurotensin, i-dynorphin A, ne-ghrelin.
I-ACE2 ibuye ilawulwe ukuhweba nge-membrane kwe-neutral amino acid transporter SLC6A19 futhi iye yabandakanyeka esifweni sikaHartnup.
Njengophrotheni we-transmembrane, i-ACE2 isebenza njengendawo eyinhloko yokungena kumaseli e-coronavirus athile, kufaka phakathi i-HCoV-NL63; i-SARS-CoV (i-virus ebangela i-SARS); ne-SARS-CoV-2 (i-virus ebangela i-COVID-19).
Ngokuqondile, ukubopha i-spike S1 protein ye-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV2 endaweni ye-enzymatic ye-ACE2 ebusweni bamaseli kubangela i-endocytosis kanye nokuguqulwa kokubili kwegciwane ne-enzyme ibe yi-endosomes etholakala ngaphakathi kwamaseli.
Le nqubo yokungena idinga futhi ukuqala kwe-protein S nge-serine protease host TMPRSS2, ukuvinjelwa kwayo okuhlolwa njengendlela yokwelapha. Lokhu kuye kwaholela abanye ekucabangeni ukuthi ukwehlisa amazinga e-ACE2 kumaseli, kungasiza ekulweni nesifo.
Kodwa-ke, izinhlangano eziningi zezolimo kanye nezikhungo zokulawula ziye zeluleka ukuqhubeka nokwelashwa okujwayelekile kwe-ACE inhibitor ne-ARB.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile kanye ne-meta-analysis eyanyatheliswa ngoJulayi 11, 2012, kutholakale ukuthi ""ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors kwakuhlobene nokunciphisa okuphawulekayo okungu-34% kwengozi yokuphefumula uma kuqhathaniswa nokulawula. """
Ngaphezu kwalokho, "ubungozi bokushaqeka kwamakhemikhali abuye banciphe ezigulini ezilashwa ngama-ACE inhibitors ezazisengozini enkulu yokushaqeka kwamakhemikhali, ikakhulukazi lezo ezinesifo somzimba esihlaselayo nesehluleka kwenhliziyo".
" Ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors kwaphinde kwahlotshaniswa nokunciphisa ukufa okuhlobene nomdlavuza wemiphunga, nakuba imiphumela yayingaqiniseki kangako kunengozi ephelele yomdlavuza wemiphunga. """
I- recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) kucatshangwa ukuthi iyindlela entsha yokwelapha ukulimala komaphaphu okubucayi, futhi kubonakala sengathi ithuthukisa i-hemodynamics yamaphaphu nokugcwala komoya-mpilo ezimbongolo ezine- lipopolysaccharide- induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Ukuphela kwesikhathi sokuphumula kwe-rhACE2 kubantu cishe kungamahora angu-10 futhi ukuqala kwesenzo kungamaminithi angu-30 ngaphezu kwesikhathi sokusebenza (ukuqhubeka) kwamahora angu-24.
