I-COVID-19 yabonwa ngoDisemba 2019.
Ukuqubuka okukhulu kwasakazeka emhlabeni wonke ngo-2020, okwaholela ekutheni kwenziwe izimali ezinkulu kanye nemisebenzi yocwaningo ekuthuthukiseni umuthi wokugoma.
Izinhlangano eziningi zisebenzisa ama-genome ashicilelwe ukuthuthukisa izidakamizwa ezingaba khona zokugoma i-SARS-CoV-2.
Kwaphawulwa ngo-Ephreli ukuthi izidingo zesinyathelo se-CEPI sokuthuthukiswa komuthi wokugoma yijubane, umthamo wokukhiqiza, ukuthunyelwa ngesilinganiso esikhulu, nokufinyelela emhlabeni jikelele.
Ngo-Ephreli, ososayensi be-CEPI babike ukuthi amapulatifomu obuchwepheshe ahlukene ayi-10 ayecwaningwa futhi athuthukiswa ekuqaleni kuka-2020 ukuze kwakhiwe umuthi wokugoma osebenzayo wokulwa ne-COVID-19.
Izinhloso ezinkulu zepulatifomu eziqhubekayo ezifundweni zokuphepha zesigaba I zihlanganisa:
i-nucleic acid (i-DNA ne-RNA) (umthuthukisi wesigaba I nomuntu ozobhapathizwa emithini yokugoma: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
i-vector ye-virus (umthuthukisi wesigaba I nomuntu ozokhethwa ukuba abe umuthi wokugoma: CanSino Biologics, i-adenovirus type 5 vector)
Njengoba kubikwe ososayensi be-CEPI ngo-Ephreli, izicelo zokugoma eziyi-115 zizonke zisesigabeni sokuqala sokuthuthukiswa, kanti eziyi-78 ziqinisekisiwe njengezinhlelo ezisebenzayo (79, ngokusho kweMilken Institute), kanti ezinye ezingama-37 zimenyezelwe, kodwa kunolwazi oluncane olutholakalayo emphakathini (okucatshangwa ukuthi luhlelwa noma lwakhiwa).
