Imithi yokugoma yokuhlola kunoma yiziphi zalezi zindlela kufanele ihlolwe ukuze iqinisekise ukuphepha nokusebenza kahle. NgoMashi 16, 2020, kwaqala ukuhlolwa kokuqala komuthi wokugoma ngamavolontiya amane eSeattle.
Umuthi wokugoma uqukethe ikhodi engenabungozi yezakhi zofuzo ekopishwe ku-virus ebangela lesi sifo. Ukuqiniswa okuxhomeke kumagciwane kuye kwaphakanyiswa njengenselelo engase ibe khona ekuthuthukiseni umuthi wokugoma we-SARS-COV-2, kodwa lokhu kuphikisana.
Kunokuhlolwa okungokomtholampilo okusebenzayo okungaphezu kuka-300 okuqhubekayo kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020.
Izivivinyo eziyisikhombisa zazihlola izindlela zokwelapha ezazisemthethweni zokwelapha umalaleveva, kuhlanganise nezifundo ezine eziphathelene ne-hydroxychloroquine noma i-chloroquine.
Izidakamizwa eziphinde zisetshenziswe njenge-antiviral zifaka ingxenye enkulu yocwaningo lwaseChina, kanti ucwaningo lwesizini yesithathu lwe-remdesivir emazweni amaningana luzobikwa ekupheleni kuka-Ephreli.
Ukubuyekezwa okunamandla kwentuthuko yomtholampilo yokugoma kwe-COVID-19 kanye nezidakamizwa ezifanele, kwasungulwa ngo-Ephreli 2020. Imithi eminingi elwa namagciwane ekhona iyahlolwa ekwelapheni i-COVID-19, kufaka phakathi i-remdesivir, i-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine, i-lopinavir/ritonavir ne-lopinavir/ritonavir kuhlangene ne-interferon beta.
Kunobufakazi obuthuthukisiwe bokusebenza kwe-remdesivir, kusukela ngoMashi 2020.
Ukuthuthuka komtholampilo kwabonwa ezigulini ezazithola ukwelashwa nge- remdesivir esebenzisweni enesihawu.
Izivivinyo zomtholampilo zesigaba III zenziwa e-US, eChina nase-Italy.I-Chloroquine, eyayisetshenziselwa ukwelapha umalaleveva, yahlolwa eChina ngoFebhuwari 2020, ngemiphumela yokuqala.
Nokho, kunesidingo sokubuyekezwa kocwaningo.
Iziphathimandla zezempilo zaseKorea nezaseChina zincoma ukusetshenziswa kwe-chloroquine.
Nokho, iWuhan Institute of Virology, nakuba incoma umthamo wansuku zonke wama-gram, iphawula ukuthi umthamo ophindwe kabili uyingozi kakhulu futhi ungabulala.
NgoMashi 28, 2020, i-FDA yakhipha imvume yokusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo kwe-hydroxychloroquine ne-chloroquine ngokubona kodokotela abaphatha abantu abane-COVID-19.
Idatha yokuqala ibonisa ukuthi kudingeka imithamo ephakeme ye-ribavirin ukuvimbela i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
INitazoxanide inconyelwe ukutadisha okwengeziwe ku-in vivo ngemuva kokukhombisa ukuvinjelwa kokulinganiselwa okuphansi kwe-SARS-CoV-2.Izifundo zibonise ukuthi ukuqala kwe-spike protein nge-transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kubalulekile ekungeneni kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokuxhumana ne-ACE2 receptor.
Ucwaningo lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine nge-azithromycin noma ngaphandle kwayo lunemikhawulo emikhulu eye yavimbela umphakathi wezokwelapha ekwamukeleni lezi zindlela zokwelapha ngaphandle kokuqhubeka nezifundo. I-Oseltamivir ayivimbeli i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro futhi ayinalo indima eyaziwayo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Isiphepho se-cytokine singaba yinkimbinkimbi ezigabeni zokugcina ze-COVID-19 ebucayi.
Kunobufakazi bokuthi i-hydroxychloroquine ingaba ne-anti-cytokine storm properties. I-Tocilizumab ifakwe emiyalweni yokwelashwa yiKhomishana Yezempilo Kazwelonke yaseChina ngemuva kokuqedwa kocwaningo oluncane.
I-Italy ihlola isigaba 2 sokuhlolwa okungahleliwe ezingeni likazwelonke ngemuva kokubonisa imiphumela emihle kubantu abanezifo ezinzima.
Uma kuhlanganiswa nokuhlolwa kwegazi le-serum ferritin ukuze kutholakale iziphepho zamakhemikhali, kuhloswe ukuba kuvinjelwe ukuthuthukiswa okunjalo, okucatshangwa ukuthi kuyimbangela yokufa kwabanye abantu abathintekayo.
I-interleukin-6 receptor antagonist ivunyelwe yi-FDA ngokusekelwe ezifundweni zamacala ezibuyekeziwe zokwelashwa kwe-steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome ebangelwa imbangela ehlukile, i-CAR T cell therapy, ngo-2017.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi obungenzeki, obulawulwayo bokuthi i- tocilizumab iyindlela ephumelelayo yokwelapha i- CRS.
Ukudlulisa ama-antibody ahlanzekile nahlanganisiwe akhiqizwa amasistimu omzimba alabo asebevuselele ku-COVID-19 kubantu abawadingayo kuhlolwa njengendlela yokugoma engekho emthethweni.
Leli qhinga lahlolwa ku-SARS kodwa lalinganqotshwa.
Ukwehliswa kwegciwane kuyindlela elindelekile yokusebenza lapho ukwelashwa kwamaphilisi okuzenzakalelayo kungaxazulula khona ukuzivikela kwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, kungenzeka ukuthi ezinye izindlela, njengobuthi bezinhlayiya ze-cyllular cytotoxicity kanye/noma i-phagocytosis, ezincike kumagciwane.
Ezinye izinhlobo zokwelashwa kwamaphilisi okuzibulala-zinambuzane, ngokwesibonelo, kusetshenziswa amaphilisi okuzibulala-zinambuzane ahlanzekile, zisekhona.
Ukukhiqizwa kwe-serum yokuvuselela, eyakhiwa yingxenye eqediwe yegazi yeziguli ezivuselelwe futhi equkethe ama-antibody akhethekile kuleli gciwane, kungandiswa ukuze kusetshenziswe ngokushesha.
